(23, 119, 94, 'Ndingowakho, ndisindise; kuba ndifuna izilumkiso zakho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 119, 95, 'Abangendawo bendilindele ukuba nditshabalale, Ke mna ndibambe isiluleko sakho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 119, 96, 'Yonke inzaliseko ndiyibonile apho iphela khona; Ke wona ucwangco lwakho lubanzi kakhulu.', 'XHO22'),
