(23, 129, 8, 'Abadlulayo bangathi, Intsikelelo kaYehova mayibe phezu kwenu; siyanisikelela egameni likaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 130, 1, 'Ndinqula wena, Yehova, ndisezihogweni;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 130, 2, 'Yehova, live ilizwi lam; iindlebe zakho mazilibekele indlebe ilizwi lomthandazo wam.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 130, 3, 'Yehova, ebugwenxeni ubugwenxa bakho, ngubani na onokuma, Yehova?', 'XHO22'),
(23, 130, 4, 'Kuwe ke ukuxolela, ukuze woyikwe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 130, 5, 'Ndithembele kuYehova, uthembile umphefumlo wam, Ndikholose ngelizwi lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 130, 6, 'Umphefumlo wam ulindele kuYehova ngaphezu kwabalindele ingomso; Ndithi, ngaphezu kwabo bajonge ingomso.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 130, 7, 'uSirayeli makakholose ngoYehova, ngokuba kuYehova kukho inceba, nosindiso lwakhe lukhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 130, 8, 'Yena uya kumkhulula uSirayeli ezonweni zakhe zonke.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 131, 1, 'iNgoma kaDavide. Kwaye andiziqeqesheli izinto ezinkulu okanye izinto eziphezulu kakhulu kum.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 131, 2, 'Ndazinqanda, ndathi tu, njengomntwana olunyulweyo kunina; umphefumlo wam unjengomntwana olunyulweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 131, 3, 'uSirayeli makakholose ngoYehova kususela ngoku kude kuse ephakadeni.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 1, 'Ingoma yeeleta. Yehova, mkhumbule uDavide neembandezelo zakhe zonke.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 2, 'Wafunga uYehova, wafunga imbalasane kaYakobi;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 3, 'Andiyi kungena ententeni yendlu yam, Andiyi kukhwela esililini sam;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 4, 'Andiyi kuwaphumza amehlo am, amehlo am awabi nabuthongo:', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 5, 'ndide ndimfumanele indawo uYehova, nendawo yeGorha likaYakobi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 6, 'Yabona, siyivile e-Efrata, siyifumene ezweni lehlathi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 7, 'Siya kungena ezintenteni zakhe; soguqa ezinyaweni zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 8, 'Vuka, Yehova, ekuphumleni kwakho; wena netyeya yamandla akho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 9, 'Ababingeleli bakho mabambathe ubulungisa; banoyolo abanyulwa bakho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 10, 'Ngenxa kaDavide umkhonzi wakho, musa ukutyeka ebusweni bomthanjiswa wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 11, 'uYehova umfungele uDavide inyaniso; akayi kuzohlwaya; Ndiya kuhlala etroneni yakho kunye neziqhamo zomzimba wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 12, 'Ukuba bathe oonyana bakho bawugcina umnqophiso wam, Nesingqiniso sam endibafundisayo: Oonyana babo bothi nabo bahlale Etroneni yakho nanini.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 13, 'Ngokuba uYehova uyinyule iZiyon; wayefuna ibe yindawo yakhe yokuhlala.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 14, 'Nantsi indawo yam yokuphumla kwam nanini; kuba ndandiyifuna.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 15, 'Ndiya kukusikelela kakhulu ukudla kwakhe, Ndibadlise isonka abasweleyo bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 16, 'Ndiya kubambesa usindiso ababingeleli balo, nabangcwele balo bavuye;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 17, 'Ndiya kumtyala khona uphondo uDavide; Ndimkhanyisele umthanjiswa wam.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 132, 18, 'Iintshaba zakhe ndiya kuzambesa udano; Ke sona isithsaba sakhe siya kuphuma igazi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 133, 1, 'Ingoma kaDavide. Yabonani, ukuba kuhle, ukuba mnandi, Bakuba oonyana babantu behleli bodwa!', 'XHO22'),
(23, 133, 2, 'Kunjengeoli elungileyo entloko, esihla iye ezindevini, ezindevini zika-Aron;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 133, 3, 'Kunjengombethe waseHermon, ohla phezu kweentaba zaseZiyon, kuba uYehova wayimisela khona intsikelelo, ubomi, kude kuse ephakadeni.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 134, 1, '(Ingoma yezinyuko.) Yabonani, mbongeni uYehova, nonke nina bakhonzi bakaYehova, bemiyo endlwini kaYehova ebusuku.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 134, 2, 'Phakamisani izandla zenu engcweleni, nimdumise uYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 134, 3, 'uYehova, owenza amazulu nehlabathi, akusikelele eZiyon.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 1, 'Dumisani uYehova. Dumisani Igama likaYehova; Mdumiseni, nina bakhonzi bakaYehova!', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 2, 'Nina nimiyo endlwini kaYehova, Ezintendelezweni zendlu yoThixo wethu;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 3, 'Dumisani uYehova; ngokuba uYehova ulungile; Libetheleni uhadi igama lakhe; kuba kumnandi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 4, 'Kuba uYehova unyule uYakobi noSirayeli ukuba babe sisityebi sakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 5, 'Kuba ndiyazi mna ukuba uYehova mkhulu nokuba iNkosi yethu ingaphezu koothixo bonke.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 6, 'Yonke into ayithandayo uYehova uyenzile emazulwini nasemhlabeni, kuzo zonke iilwandle nemilambo yehlabathi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 7, 'Ulonyusa amafu esiphelweni sehlabathi; imvula uyenzela imibane; ukhupha umoya ezintweni zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 8, 'Owabulala amazibulo aseYiputa, awabantu naweenkomo;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 9, 'owathumela imiqondiso nezimanga phakathi kwenu, Yiputa, kuFaro nakubakhonzi bakhe bonke;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 10, 'owanqoba iintlanga ezinkulu, wabulala ookumkani abanamandla;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 11, 'uSihon, ukumkani wama-Amori, no-Ogi, ukumkani waseBhashan, nezikumkani zonke zakwaKanan;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 12, 'Walinika ilizwe labo njengelifa, ilifa labantu bakhe amaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 13, 'Igama lakho, Yehova, lingunaphakade; nesikhumbuzo sakho, Yehova, kwizizukulwana ngezizukulwana.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 14, 'Ngokuba uYehova uya kubagweba abantu bakhe, abe nosizi ngabakhonzi bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 15, 'Izithixo zeentlanga yisilivere negolide, Umsebenzi wezandla zabantu.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 16, 'Zinemilebe yomlomo, kodwa azithethi; banamehlo, kodwa ababoni;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 17, 'Zineendlebe nje, aziva; kwaye akukho moya emlonyeni wawo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 18, 'Abenzayo bayafana nabo; banjalo bonke abazimela ngaye.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 19, 'Dumisani uYehova, nina ndlu kaSirayeli, mbongeni uYehova, nina ndlu ka-Aron;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 20, 'Nina bendlu kaLevi, mbongeni, nina nimoyikayo uYehova, mbongeni uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 135, 21, 'Makabongwe uYehova eZiyon, ulohlala eYerusalem. Dumisani uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 1, 'Mdumiseni uYehova; ngokuba elungile, ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 2, 'Mdumiseni uThixo woothixo, Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 3, 'Dumisani uYehova wookumkani, Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 4, 'Nguye yedwa owenza imisebenzi ebalulekileyo ebalulekileyo, Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 5, 'KuloMenzi wezulu ngobulumko: Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 6, 'KuloMtwabululi wehlabathi phezu kwamanzi: Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 7, 'KuMenzi wezikhanyiso ezikhulu, Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 8, 'Ilanga malilawule imini, Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 9, 'Inyanga neenkwenkwezi zilawula ebusuku: Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 10, 'Kulowabulala amazibulo abo eYiputa, Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 11, 'Wabasondeza oonyana bakaSirayeli phakathi kwabo, Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 12, 'Ngesandla esithe nkqi, nangesandla esolukileyo: Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 13, 'KuloMgabuli woLwandle oluBomvu, lwagabuka, ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 14, 'Makacande kulo uSirayeli: Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 15, 'uFaro nempi yakhe bajulwa eLwandle oluBomvu, ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 16, 'Kulohambisa abantu bakhe entlango: Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 17, 'Ukongamela kookumkani abakhulu, Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 18, 'Nookumkani abadumileyo ababulawayo, ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 19, 'uSihon, ukumkani wama-Amori, ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 20, 'no-Ogi, ukumkani waseBhashan, ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 21, 'Walinikela ilizwe labo laba lilifa, Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 22, 'Malibe lilifa likaSirayeli umkhonzi wakhe, Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 23, 'Usikhumbule ehlazweni lethu, Ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 24, 'Usihlangule ezonweni zethu, ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 25, 'Onika inyama yonke ukudla, ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 136, 26, 'Mdumiseni uThixo wamazulu, ngokuba ingunaphakade inceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 137, 1, 'Emilanjeni yaseBhabheli, sahlala khona, salila, sakuyikhumbula iZiyon.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 137, 2, 'Iintsika zethu sazixhoma emngcunubeni phakathi kwawo;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 137, 3, 'Ngokuba apho babesibambe khona, babiza kuthi ingoma; kwaye abo basitshabalalisayo bafuna ulonwabo lwethu, besithi: Siculele ingoma yaseZiyon.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 137, 4, 'Siya kuyivuma njani ingoma kaYehova kwilizwe lasemzini?', 'XHO22'),
(23, 137, 5, 'Ukuba ndithe ndakulibala, Yerusalem, Masizilibale iinkohliso zakhe isandla sam sokunene.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 137, 6, 'Ukuba andithanga ndikukhumbule, ulwimi lwam malunamathele ekhuhlangubeni lam; andisayi kuyinyula iYerusalem ngaphezu kovuyo lwam olukhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 137, 7, 'Bakhumbule, Yehova, oonyana bakaEdom, Ngemini yeYerusalem; abo bathi, Yidilizeni, yidilizeni, kuse elusekweni lwalo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 137, 8, 'Ntombi yaseBhabheli, wena ufanelwe kukutshatyalaliswa; unoyolo lowo usivuzayo njengoko usikhonze ngako kuthi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 137, 9, 'Hayi, uyolo lomtyumza ngamatye abantwana bakho!', 'XHO22'),
(23, 138, 1, 'Ndiya kubulela kuwe ngentliziyo yam yonke; Ndiya kuvuma phambi koothixo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 138, 2, 'Ndiya kuguqa etempileni yakho engcwele, ndibulele kwigama lakho, ngenxa yenceba yakho, nangenxa yenyaniso yakho, ngenxa enokuba ulikhulisile ilizwi lakho ngaphezu kwegama lakho lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 138, 3, 'Ngemini yokubiza kwam, wandiphendula, wandomeleza ngomoya wam;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 138, 4, 'Baya kubulela kuwe, Yehova, bonke ookumkani behlabathi, Bakuweva amazwi omlomo wakho;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 138, 5, 'Ewe, baya kumemelela ngeendlela zikaYehova, Ngokuba mkhulu ubuqaqawuli bukaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 138, 6, 'Nangona uYehova ephakamile, uyabanyamekela abathobekileyo, kodwa ubazi abakude le abanekratshi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 138, 7, 'Ukuba ndithe ndahamba ebunzimeni, uya kundiphilisa; Uya kusolula isandla sakho emsindweni weentshaba zam, undisindise esokunene sakho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 138, 8, 'uYehova makandenzele isicelo sam: Yehova, inceba yakho ingunaphakade; musa ukuyishiya imisebenzi yezandla zakho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 1, 'Umhobe kaDavide. Yehova, undigocagocile, wandazi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 2, 'Wena uyakwazi ukudandatheka kwam nokreqo lwam, Uyaziqonda izicamango zam nakude.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 3, 'Uhambahamba indlela yam nezilili zam, Uyazazi zonke iindlela zam.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 4, 'Ngokuba akukho lizwi elulwimini lwam Ongalaziyo ke, Yehova.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 5, 'Wandijikela ngasemva nasemva, Wasibeka phezu kwam isandla sakho;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 6, 'Kuyandimangalisa ukwazi oko; iphezulu, andikwazi ukufikelela kuyo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 7, 'Ndingahambela phi na ukumka emoyeni wakho? Ndingabalekela phi na ukumka ebusweni bakho?', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 8, 'Xa ndinyuke ndaya emazulwini, ulapho; ndawendlala umandlalo wam kwelabafileyo, nanko ukho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 9, 'Ukuba ndithe ndathabatha amaphiko esifingo, ndahlala ekupheleni kolwandle;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 10, 'Isandla sakho siya kundikhapha, Esokunene sakho siya kundibamba.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 11, 'Ukuba ndithe, Okunene, buya kundigubungela ubumnyama; ubusuku bube kukukhanya kum.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 12, 'Ewe, ubumnyama abuyi kukufihla; kodwa ubusuku bukhanya njengemini; kobakho ubumnyama nokukhanya.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 13, 'Ngokuba uzithabathe izintso zam, Wandambesa esizalweni sikama.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 14, 'Ndithanda ukudumisa; ngokuba ndenziwe ngokoyikekayo, ngokubalulekileyo; zibalulekile izenzo zakho; kwaye umphefumlo wam uyazi kakuhle.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 15, 'Izinto zam azizange zifihleke kuwe xa ndenziwayo emfihlekweni, yaye ndenziwa ngendlela emangalisayo kweyona mimandla isemazantsi omhlaba.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 16, 'Amehlo akho andibona ndigqibelele; kwaye encwadini yakho kubhaliwe konke ukhupho lwam oludalwe emva kwanolunye lwazo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 17, 'Hayi, ukuxabiseka kweengcinga zakho, Thixo! hayi indlela enkulu ngayo isibalo sayo!', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 18, 'Ndizibalile, zininzi ngaphezu kwentlabathi; xa ndivuka ndisenawe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 19, 'Inene, wena Thixo, uya kubabulala abangendawo;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 20, 'Ngokuba bathetha kakubi ngawe, zalingcikiva igama lakho iintshaba zakho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 21, 'Yehova, andinabo na abakuthiyayo? Andivi buhlungu na ngenxa yamadoda amakhulu?', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 22, 'Ndibathiya ngentiyo ephelelisileyo, Kum mna baziintshaba.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 23, 'Ndigocagoce, Thixo, uyazi intliziyo yam; ndicikide, uzazi iingcinga-ngcinga zam.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 139, 24, 'Kwaye ubone ukuba kukho indlela engalunganga kum, kwaye undikhokelele kumendo wanaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 140, 1, 'Ndihlangule, Yehova, kongendawo; Ndikhusele kumcudisi;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 140, 2, 'obubonakalisa ububi ezintliziyweni zabo; bahlala behlanganisene emfazweni.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 140, 3, 'Balola ulwimi lwabo njengenyoka; Ubuthi bezizwe buphantsi komlomo wabo. Sela.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 140, 4, 'Ndisindise, Yehova, esandleni songendawo; Ndikhusele kumcudisi; obeceba ukubhukuqa uhambo lwam.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 140, 5, 'Abakhukhumeleyo bandithiyele ngomgibe nezintya; Baneka umnatha endleleni; bandenze igin. Sela.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 140, 6, 'Ndithi kuYehova, UnguThixo wam; Yehova, live izwi lomthandazo wam;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 140, 7, 'uYehova, ligwiba losindiso lwam, Wayigqubuthela intloko yam ngemini yemfazwe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 140, 8, 'Yehova, musa ukumnika ongendawo iminqweno yakhe; aliyi kubuya libekho icebo lakhe elibi; ukuze bangaziphakamisi. Sela.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 140, 9, 'Ke zona iintloko zabandingqongileyo, Nobubi bomlomo wabo buya kubagubungela;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 140, 10, 'Makawele phezu kwabo amalahle avuthayo; mabaphoswe emlilweni; emhadini onzulu, ukuze bangabi savuka.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 140, 11, 'Makungabikho mhlebi ehlabathini; ububi buya kuzingela umbulali ukuze amtshabalalise.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 140, 12, 'Ndiyazi ukuba uYehova uya kulixhasa ityala lehlwempu nehlwempu.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 140, 13, 'Inene, amalungisa aya kulidumisa igama lakho; aya kuhlala kuwe amalungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 141, 1, '(Indumiso kaDavide.) Yehova, ndinqula wena; khawuleza undilandele; Phulaphula izwi lam xa ndikubiza.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 141, 2, 'Umthandazo wam mawube nesiqhumiso phambi kwakho; ndiziphakamise izandla zam njengombingelelo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 141, 3, 'Yehova, beka umbonisi phambi komlomo wam; ndivale umnyango emlonyeni.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 141, 4, 'Intliziyo yam musa ukuyithobela ebubini nasebubini, ekwenzeni ububi nakubantu abenza ububi; andiyi kudla ubumnandi babo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 141, 5, 'Malindibethe ilungisa; makube yinceba leyo, makandohlwaye; iya kuba yi-ole elungileyo, engayi kuqhekeza intloko yam;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 141, 6, 'Xa abagwebi bawo bekhahlelwa ezindaweni ezilulwalwa, baya kuwaphulaphula amazwi am; kuba zimnandi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 141, 7, 'Athe saa amathambo ethu emlonyeni wendlu yofileyo, njengomntu egawula imithi, ayigawule.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 141, 8, 'Kodwa amehlo am akuwe, Yehova; ndithembele kuwe; musa ukuwuyeka umphefumlo wam;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 141, 9, 'Ndisindise ezintabeni abandakhele zona, Ezintabeni zabenzi bobubi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 141, 10, 'Mabaguqe ngamadolo abangendawo, ndibaleke mna;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 142, 1, '(Imbali kaDavide: umthandazo wakhe waba semqolombeni.) Ndadanduluka kuYehova ngezwi lam; Ngelizwi lam ndithandaza kuYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 142, 2, 'Ndiphalaze kuye ukukhala kwam; Ndabonisa inzame zam phambi kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 142, 3, 'Ekutyhafeni komphefumlo wam phakathi kwam, wayeyazi yena indlela yam; Ndathi ndihamba nje, bandithiyela ngokufihlakeleyo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 142, 4, 'Ndabheka ngasekunene kwam, ndakhangela, akwabakho bani undazi; akukho uwukhathalele umphefumlo wam.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 142, 5, 'Ndabiza kuwe, Yehova, ndathi, Uyindawo yam yokusabela, nesabelo sam ezweni labaphulaphulayo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 142, 6, 'Kubekele indlebe ukuhlahlamba kwam; ngokuba ndithobeke kakhulu; Ndihlangule kwabandisukelayo; ngokuba bomelele kunam.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 142, 7, 'Wukhuphe entolongweni umphefumlo wam, Ndibulele kwigama lakho; Amalungisa aya kundirhawula; ngokuba uya kundenzela inceba.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 143, 1, '(Indumiso kaDavide.) Yehova, wubekele indlebe umthandazo wam, uwubekele indlebe umthandazo wam; ndiphendule ngokuthembeka kwakho nangobulungisa bakho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 143, 2, 'Musa ukumsa ematyaleni umkhonzi wakho, ngokuba akukho mntu uhleliyo uya kulilungisa emehlweni akho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 143, 3, 'Ngokuba utshaba luwusukele umphefumlo wam; Wabubethela phantsi ubomi bam; Undibeke ebumnyameni njengabo bafa kudala.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 143, 4, 'Ngenxa yoko umphefumlo wam ukhwankqisiwe; Ibibhibhile intliziyo yam phakathi kwam.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 143, 5, 'Ndikhumbula imihla yamandulo; Ndiyigqala yonke imisebenzi yakho; Ndicamngca ngomsebenzi wezandla zakho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 143, 6, 'Ndizolulela kuwe izandla zam; umphefumlo wam ukungxamele njengomhlaba owomileyo. Sela.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 143, 7, 'Khawuleza undiphendule, Yehova, umphefumlo wam udandathekile; musa ukubusithelisa kum ubuso bakho, hleze ndifane nabahla baye kwelabafileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 143, 8, 'Ndivise kwakusasa inceba yakho; ngokuba ndikholose ngawe; Ndazise indlela endiya kuhamba ngayo; kuba ndiwuphakamisela kuni umoya wam.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 143, 9, 'Yehova, ndihlangule ezintshabeni zam; Ndibalekela kuwe ukuze ndizimele.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 143, 10, 'Ndifundise ukwenza ukuthanda kwakho; ngokuba unguThixo wam. Umphefumlo wakho ulungile; Ndikhaphele ezweni lenyaniso.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 143, 11, 'Ngenxa yegama lakho, Yehova, ndiphilise;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 143, 12, 'Ngenceba yakho zibhangise iintshaba zam, Ubatshabalalise bonke abawusukelayo umphefumlo wam, Ngokuba ndingumkhonzi wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 1, '(Indumiso kaDavide.) Makabongwe uYehova, mandla am, Ulofundisa izandla zam ukulwa, Ozifundisayo ukulwa neminwe yam!', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 2, 'Ukulunga kwam nenqaba yam; inqaba yam ephakamileyo, umsindisi wam; Ingweletshetshe yam, ndikholose ngaye; owabathobayo abantu bam phantsi kwam.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 3, 'Yehova, uyintoni na umntu, ukuze umazi! okanye unyana womntu, ukuba uya kuphendula kuye!', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 4, 'Ufana nomphunga umntu, imihla yakhe injengethunzi elidlulayo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 5, 'Wathoba amazulu akho, Yehova, uhle; Zichukumise iintaba, ziqhume.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 6, 'Thumela imibane, ubaphangalalise; tola iintolo zakho, ubatshabalalisile.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 7, 'Khawusibeke phezulu isandla sakho; Ndihlangule, ndisindise emanzini amaninzi, esandleni soonyana beentlanga;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 8, 'abamlomo uthetha inkohlakalo, Abasandla sokunene sisesokunene sobuxoki.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 9, 'Ndiya kukubethela ingoma entsha, Thixo; Ndiya kukubethela umrhubhe ontambo zilishumi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 10, 'Ulonika ookumkani usindiso, Ohlangula umkhonzi wakhe uDavide kumkhonto oyingozi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 11, 'Ndihlangule, ndihlangule esandleni soonyana bolunye uhlanga, abamlomo uthetha inkohlakalo, abasandla sokunene sisesokunene sobuxoki;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 12, 'oonyana bethu babe njengezityalo ezikhule kwasebutsheni babo; iintombi zethu zibe njengeembombo ezikhazimliswe njengebhotwe;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 13, 'ahluthe oovimba bethu, kubekho kukudla ngeentlobo ngeentlobo, neegusha zethu zivelise amawaka angamashumi amawaka ezitratweni zethu.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 14, 'Ke iinkomo zethu zomelele emsebenzini; ukuba kungabikho kuphuma nokuphumayo; ukuba akukho sikhalazo ezitalatweni zethu.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 144, 15, 'Lunoyolo uhlanga olunjalo; Hayi, uyolo lwabantu abaThixo wabo unguYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 1, '(Umhobe kaDavide.) Ndiya kubulela kuwe, Thixo wam, kumkani; yaye ndiya kulidumisa igama lakho ngonaphakade kanaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 2, 'Ndiya kukubonga yonke imihla; yaye ndiya kulidumisa igama lakho ngonaphakade kanaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 3, 'uYehova mkhulu yaye ngowokudunyiswa kunene; nobukhulu bakhe abunakulinganiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 4, 'Izizukulwana ngezizukulwana ziya kuyincoma imisebenzi yakho, Zixelise ubugorha bakho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 5, 'Ndiya kukhankanya ubuqaqawuli bobungangamsha bakho, nezimanga zakho;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 6, 'Bathetha abantu ngamandla ezenzo zakho ezoyikekayo, ndibalise ngobukhulu bakho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 7, 'Baya kuvakalisa ngokuyintabalala ukukhumbula ukulunga kwakho okukhulu, nokudumisa ubulungisa bakho.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 8, 'uYehova unemfesane, unobubele; uzeka kade umsindo, mkhulu ngenceba.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 9, 'Ulungile uYehova kubo bonke, Imfesane yakhe ikuzo zonke izenzo zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 10, 'Zonke izenzo zakho ziya kukubonga, Yehova; Bakubonge abakho benceba.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 11, 'Uzuko lobukumkani bakho baluthethe, Bathethe ngamandla akho;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 12, 'Ukuba babazise oonyana babantu ubugorha bakhe, nobungangamela bobukumkani bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 13, 'Ubukumkani bakho bubukumkani bamaphakade onke, nolawulo lwakho lukwizizukulwana ezingunaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 14, 'uYehova ungumxhasi wabo bonke abawayo, Ngumphakamisi wabo bonke abagobileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 15, 'Onke amehlo akhangele kuwe; wabanika ukudla kwakho ngexesha elililo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 16, 'Uyasivula isandla sakho, uzihluthise iinto zonke eziphilileyo ngeento ezikholekileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 17, 'Ulilungisa uYehova ngeendlela zakhe zonke, Ungcwele ngezenzo zakhe zonke.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 18, 'Usondele uYehova kubo bonke abamnqulayo, bonke abamnqulayo ngenyaniso.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 19, 'Uya kwenza okukholekileyo kwabamoyikayo; Uya kukuva ukuzibika kwabo, abasindise.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 20, 'uYehova uyabakhusela bonke abo bamthandayo, kodwa bonke abangendawo uya kubatshabalalisa.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 145, 21, 'Umlomo wam uya kuzixela iingoma zikaYehova, Yonke inyama ilidumise igama lakhe elingcwele ngonaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 146, 1, 'Dumisani uYehova. Mbonge uYehova, mphefumlo wam!', 'XHO22'),
(23, 146, 2, 'Ndiya kumdumisa uYehova lo gama ndidla ubomi; Ndiyathanda ukuhlabelela uThixo wam lo gama ndidla ubomi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 146, 3, 'Musani ukukholosa ngamanene, Ngonyana womntu ongenanceba kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 146, 4, 'Uyaphuma umphefumlo wakhe, abuyele emhlabeni wakhe; Kwangaloo mini ingqondo yakhe yaphambana.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 146, 5, 'Hayi, uyolo lwalowo uluncedo lunguThixo kaYakobi, okholose ngoYehova uThixo wakhe!', 'XHO22'),
(23, 146, 6, 'Lowo wenza izulu nomhlaba, nolwandle, neento zonke ezikwezo zinto, lowo ugcina inyaniso ngonaphakade;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 146, 7, 'Umgwebayo otyumkileyo, Ngopha abalambileyo ukudla; uYehova uyabakhulula abathinjwa;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 146, 8, 'uYehova uvula amehlo eemfama; NguYehova ophakamisa abagobileyo; uYehova uyawathanda amalungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 146, 9, 'uYehova uyabakhusela abasemzini; unceda iinkedama nabahlolokazi, uyijike indlela yabangendawo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 146, 10, 'uYehova uya kulawula ngonaphakade njengeNkosi, uThixo wakho, iZiyon, kwizizukulwana ngezizukulwana. Dumisani uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 1, 'Mdumiseni uYehova, ngokuba kulungile ukuvuma uzuko loThixo wethu; ngokuba kumnandi oko; kwaye indumiso ithandekayo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 2, 'uYehova uyakha iYerusalem, ahlanganise abagxothiweyo bakwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 3, 'Ulophilisa abaphuke intliziyo, Abophe amanxeba abo;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 4, 'Ubala inani leenkwenkwezi; uzibiza zonke ngamagama azo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 5, 'iNkosi yethu inkulu, inamandla amakhulu, ingqondo yayo ayinasiphelo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 6, 'NguYehova ophakamisa abalulamileyo, uyabawisa abangendawo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 7, 'Vumani ngendumiso kuYehova; nivume indumiso yoThixo wethu ngomrhubhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 8, 'Ulogubungela izulu ngamafu, Ulungisela umhlaba imvula, Uloseza utyani ezintabeni;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 9, 'Unika ukudla kwakhe amarhamncwa, Nakumahlungulu akhalayo;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 10, 'Akakholiswa bubugorha behashe; akazithandi iinyawo zomntu.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 11, 'uYehova uyakholiswa ngabo bamoyikayo, abakholose ngenceba yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 12, 'Mbonge uYehova, wena Yerusalem! Mdumise uThixo wakho, Ziyon!', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 13, 'Ngokuba uyayomeleza imivalo yamasango akho; Abantwana bakho ubasikelele ngawe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 14, 'Nguye owenza uxolo ezweni lakho, Wakondla ngengqolowa etyebileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 15, 'Uthumela umyalelo wakhe ehlabathini; ilizwi lakhe libaleka kakhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 16, 'Unika ikhephu njengoboya; Unika ukubanda njengothuthu.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 17, 'Uchithachitha umkhenkce wakhe njengamaqhekeza; Ngubani na onokuma phambi kwengqele yakhe?', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 18, 'Uthumela ilizwi lakhe, azinyibilikise; Uvuthuza umoya wakhe kwaye amanzi aqukuqela.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 19, 'Wamazisa uYakobi ilizwi lakhe, Wamazisa uSirayeli izigwebo zakhe neziyalezo zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 147, 20, 'Akazange akwenze oko ebantwini, nabo babengawazi imigwebo yakhe. Dumisani uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 148, 1, 'Dumisani uYehova. Dumisani uYehova emazulwini, Mdumiseni ezindaweni eziphakamileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 148, 2, 'Mdumiseni, nonke zithunywa zakhe, Mdumiseni, nonke mikhosi yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 148, 3, 'Mdumiseni, nina langa, nani nyanga, mdumiseni, nonke zinkwenkwezi zinokukhanya.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 148, 4, 'Mdumiseni, nina mazulu amazulu, Namanzi angaphezu kwezulu.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 148, 5, 'Mazilidumise ezo nto igama likaYehova, ngokuba wawisa umthetho, zadalwa.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 148, 6, 'Waziqinisa ngonaphakade kanaphakade;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 148, 7, 'Dumisani uYehova ehlabathini, nonke nina zimpungutye namaqula.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 148, 8, 'Umlilo nesichotho; ikhephu kunye nomphunga; sisiphango esilenzayo ilizwi lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 148, 9, 'Zonke iintaba neenduli; yonke imithi yeziqhamo nemisedare;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 148, 10, 'neenkomo zonke; izinto ezirhubuluzayo neentaka eziphaphazelayo:', 'XHO22'),
(23, 148, 11, 'Ookumkani behlabathi, neentlanga zonke; abathetheli nabagwebi behlabathi lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 148, 12, 'Amakhwenkwe namantombazana; abantu abadala kunye nabantwana:', 'XHO22'),
(23, 148, 13, 'Mabalidumise igama likaYehova, ngokuba lilodwa igama lakhe; Ubuqaqawuli bakhe buphezu komhlaba namazulu.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 148, 14, 'Ubaphakamisele abantu bakhe uphondo, Indumiso yabakhe benceba bonke; koonyana bakaSirayeli, kubantu ababesondele kuye. Dumisani uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 149, 1, 'Dumisani uYehova. Vumani kuYehova ingoma entsha, Indumiso yakhe ebandleni labangcwele.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 149, 2, 'Makavuye uSirayeli ngoMenzi wakhe; Oonyana baseZiyon mabavuye eNkosini yabo!', 'XHO22'),
(23, 149, 3, 'Mabalidumise igama lakhe ngokungqungqa, Bavume kuye ngengqongqo nohadi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 149, 4, 'Ngokuba uYehova uyakholiswa ngabantu bakhe; Uya kubahombisa abalulamileyo ngosindiso.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 149, 5, 'Abathembekileyo mabavuye ngozuko; wabaculela ezingqengqelweni zabo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 149, 6, 'Inguquko kaThixo mayibe semilonyeni yabo nekrele elintlangothi-mbini ezandleni zabo;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 149, 7, 'ukuba baphindezele impindezelo kwiintlanga, zohlwaye;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 149, 8, 'babakhonkxe ookumkani bazo ngemixokelelwane, nabathetheli bazo ngemixokelelwane yesinyithi;', 'XHO22'),
(23, 149, 9, 'kwathiwa, Banembeko ngenxa yabo bonke abangcwele bakhe. Dumisani uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 150, 1, 'Dumisani uYehova. Mdumiseni uThixo engcweleni yakhe, Mdumiseni endaweni yamandla akhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 150, 2, 'Mdumiseni ngenxa yobugorha bakhe, Mdumiseni ngobukhulu bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 150, 3, 'Mdumiseni ngesandi sesigodlo, Mdumiseni ngohadi nangohadi.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 150, 4, 'Mdumiseni ngengqongqo nengqungqo, Mdumiseni ngeento ezineentambo neentambo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 150, 5, 'Mdumiseni ngamacangci akhenkcezayo, mdumiseni ngamacangci akhenkcezayo.', 'XHO22'),
(23, 150, 6, 'Yonke into ephefumlayo mayimdumise uYehova. Dumisani uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 1, 'Amazwi kaSolomon unyana kaDavide, ukumkani wakwaSirayeli;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 2, 'Ubazi ubulumko noqeqesho; ukunakana kwamagama engqiqo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 3, 'yokwamkela imfundiso yobulumko, nesiko, nesiko, nobulungisa;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 4, 'Ukunika abo bafuna amaqhinga, ulwazi kunye neengcebiso kwabaselula.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 5, 'Oweva osisilumko, aqokele afunde; Umntu onengqondo uya kucebisana nobulumko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 6, 'Ukuqonda izaci neenkcazelo; Amazwi ezilumko nezintsonkotha zazo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 7, 'Ukoyika uYehova kukuqala kokwazi; Ubulumko noqeqesho izimathane ziludelile.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 8, 'Nyana wam, yiva uqeqesho lukayihlo, Ungawushiyi umyalelo kanyoko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 9, 'Kuba iya kuba sisivatho sokuhomba entlokweni yakho, nemixokelelwane yentamo yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 10, 'Nyana wam, xa aboni bekulinga, awukholwa;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 11, 'Ukuba bathe, Hamba nathi, masilinde igazi, sifune abamsulwa emfihlekweni, simsulwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 12, 'Wathi abo badlayo usaphila njengengcwaba; nabo bangcathu, njengabo behla ngezinyuko;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 13, 'Sozifumana zonke izinto ezinqwenelekayo, sozizalisa izindlu zethu ngamaxhoba.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 14, 'Liphose phakathi kwethu iqashiso lakho; masibe nesipaji esinye sonke.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 15, 'Nyana wam, musa ukuhamba nabo endleleni; Lugcine unyawo lwakho endleleni yabo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 16, 'Kuba iinyawo zabo zigidimela ebubini, zigijimela kuphalaza igazi;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 17, 'Okunene umnatha owanekwayo phambi kwamehlo eentaka zonke ulilize.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 18, 'Balalela igazi labo; bafihla ubomi babo emfihlekweni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 19, 'Zizo ezo iindlela zabo bonke abalungileyo; ethatha ubomi babanikazi bayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 20, 'Ubulumko bumemeza; Uxela ilizwi lakhe ezitratweni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 21, 'Ubiza phambi kwebandla, ekungeneni kwamasango; Emzini ubalisa amabali akhe, esithi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 22, 'Ziyatha, kunini na ningàzi? Ngaba abagxeki bakunanzile ukugxeka; Izinyabi zithiya ukwazi?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 23, 'Buyelani ekukhalimeni kwam; niyabona, ndowugalela kuni uMoya wam, ndinazise amazwi am.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 24, 'Ngenxa enokuba ndanibiza, anavuma; Ndasolula isandla sam, akwabona mntu;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 25, 'Anilivumanga icebo lam lonke, anavuma ukundithethisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 26, 'Nam ndiya kukuhleka ububi benu; Ndiya kuhleka ekufikeni koloyiko lwenu;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 27, 'Ngokuba ekufikeni kwakho unxunguphalo, kuza njengembubhiso, ukutshabalala kwakho kuza njengomoya wesaqhwithi; xa kufike ilishwa namashwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 28, 'Bosuka bandibhenele, ndingaphenduli; baya kundifuna kamsinya, bangandifumani;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 29, 'Kuba bakuthiyile ukwazi yaye abanyulanga ukoyika uYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 30, 'Abaliphulaphula icebiso lam; Bakucekisile konke ukukhalima kwam.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 31, 'Ngoko baya kudla iziqhamo zendlela yabo baze baneliseke ngamacebo abo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 32, 'Ngokuba intiyo yezinyabi iya kuzibulala, Nokulunga kwezinyabi kuya kuzitshabalalisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 1, 33, 'Kodwa ondiphulaphulayo uya kuhlala ekhuselekile, ezolile, angoyiki ububi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 1, 'Nyana wam, ukuba uthe wawamkela amazwi am, Wayifihla imimiselo yam;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 2, 'ukuze uyithobele ubulumko indlebe yakho, uyiguqulele ekuqondeni intliziyo yakho;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 3, 'Ewe, ukuba uthe wabiza ukwazi, walisa ekuqondeni ilizwi lakho;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 4, 'Ukuba ubufuna njengesilivere, yaye ubufuna njengobuncwane obufihliweyo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 5, 'Uya kwandula ukukuqonda ukoyika uYehova, ukuqonde uThixo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 6, 'Ngokuba uYehova upha ubulumko; emlonyeni wakhe kuphuma ukwazi nokuqonda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 7, 'Uwagcinela amalungisa ubulumko; Ndiyingweletshetshe kwabahamba ngobulungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 8, 'Ugcina umendo wobulungisa, Ayigcine indlela yabakhe benceba.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 9, 'Apho uya kukuqonda okusesikweni, nesiko, nesidima; ewe, nayiphi na indlela ilungile.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 10, 'Ubulumko buya kungena entliziyweni yakho, ukwazi yikholise umphefumlo wakho;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 11, 'Iingcinga zokusindisa, ukuqonda kokusindisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 12, 'Ukuba kukuhlangule emendweni wobubi, nakumntu othetha okubi;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 13, 'abatyekayo emendweni wobulungisa, bahamba ngeendlela zobumnyama;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 14, 'abavuyela ukwenza ububi, bagcobe ngobuxoki bongendawo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 15, 'abandlela zigoso-goso, abo batyekayo ezindleleni zabo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 16, 'Ukuba uhlangulwe kumkamntu, Kowolunye uhlanga, ovakalisa ilizwi lakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 17, 'oshiya iqabane lobutsha bakhe aze awulibale umnqophiso kaThixo wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 18, 'Kuba indlu yakhe isingise ekufeni, Neendlela zakhe zisingise ekufeni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 19, 'Akukho namnye oya kuye angabuyi, kwaye akayi kuzibamba iindlela zobomi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 20, 'Ukuze uhambe ngomendo wamalungisa, Ugcine umendo wamalungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 21, 'Ngokuba amalungisa aya kuhlala emhlabeni, amalungisa aya kuhlala kuwo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 2, 22, 'Ke bona abangendawo baya kunqunyulwa emhlabeni, nabangendawo banqunyulwe kulo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 1, 'Nyana wam, musa ukuwulibala umyalelo wam; Intliziyo yakho mayiyibambe imithetho yam;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 2, 'ngokuba iya kubandisa ubude bemihla yakho, neminyaka yobomi, noxolo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 3, 'Musa ukuswela inceba nenyaniso; Zinxibe kuwe emqaleni; yibhale elucwecweni lwentliziyo yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 4, 'Wofumana ke ukwamkeleka, nokwamkeleka kakuhle emehlweni kaThixo nakubantu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 5, 'Kholosa ngoYehova ngentliziyo yakho yonke; kwaye ungayami ngokwakho ukuqonda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 6, 'Umazi kuzo zonke iindlela zakho, kwaye uya kuwenza uthi tye umendo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 7, 'Musa ukuba sisilumko; yoyika uYehova, usuke ebubini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 8, 'Kuya kuba sempilweni entle enkabeni yakho nomongo emathanjeni akho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 9, 'Mzukise uYehova ngempahla yakho, nangongeniselo lwakho lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 10, 'Ozala amaqonga akho yintabalala, ozalatha isixovulelo sakho ngewayini;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 11, 'Nyana wam, musa ukuwucekisa uqeqesho lukaYehova; ungadinwa kukukhalima kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 12, 'Ngokuba uYehova uyamohlwaya amthandayo; njengoyise wonyana akholiswayo nguye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 13, 'Hayi, uyolo lomntu ofumene ubulumko, Lomntu ozuze ingqondo!', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 14, 'Kuba ishishini labo liwugqithile urhwebo lwesilivere, nongeniselo lwabo ngaphezu kwegolide embiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 15, 'Uxabiseke ngaphezu kweeperile, yaye yonke into onokuyinqwenela ayinakulinganiswa naye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 16, 'Imihla emide isesandleni sabo sokunene; yaye esandleni sakhe sasekunene kukho ubutyebi nozuko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 17, 'Iindlela zabo ziindlela zolonwabo, neendlela zabo zonke ziluxolo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 18, 'Bungumthi wobomi kwabawubambayo, Banoyolo bonke obubambayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 19, 'uYehova walidala ngobulumko ihlabathi; ngokuba wadala amazulu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 20, 'Ngokwazi kwakhe agqabhuka amaqula, Kwavuthuza amafu umbethe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 21, 'Nyana wam, mayingawashiyi amehlo akho; Londoloza ubulumko nesiluleko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 22, 'Koba bubomi emphefumlweni wakho, Nenceba emqaleni wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 23, 'Uya kwandula uhambe indlela yakho unoxolo, aluyi kubetheka unyawo lwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 24, 'Xa uthe walala, musa ukoyika; ewe, uya kulala, bube mnandi ubuthongo bakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 25, 'Musa ukoyika lunkwantyiso luzayo ngesiquphe, Nokutshabalala kwabangendawo, kwakufika.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 26, 'Ngenxa yokuba uYehova uya kuba lithemba lakho, yaye uya kulugcina unyawo lwakho lungabanjiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 27, 'Musani ukwala ukwenza okulungileyo kwabafaneleyo, ukuba kusemandleni enu ukukwenza.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 28, 'Musa ukuthi kummelwane wakho, Hamba, ubuye, ndokunika ngomso; xa unayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 29, 'Uze ungacebi ububi ngommelwane wakho, ngokuba yena uhleli nawe enoxolo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 30, 'Musa ukubambana nomntu kungekho sizathu, ukuba akonanga;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 31, 'Musa ukuyimonela indoda egonyamelayo, Unganyuli nanye yeendlela zayo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 32, 'Kuba ongendawo ulisikizi kuYehova; Ke lunabathe tye ucweyo lwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 33, 'Ingqalekiso kaYehova isendlwini yongendawo; kodwa isakhiwo samalungisa uyayisikelela.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 34, 'Ewe, uyabagxeka abagxeki, kodwa unenceba kwabalulamileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 3, 35, 'Izilumko ziya kuludla ilifa uzuko;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 1, 'Nina bantwana, yivani imfundiso kayihlo, niyilumkele, ukuze nikwazi ukuqonda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 2, 'Ngenxa yokuba ndininika imfundiso elungileyo, musani ukuwutyeshela umthetho wam.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 3, 'Kuba bendingunyana kabawo, Ndithambile, ndiyintanda emehlweni kama.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 4, 'Wandiyala ke, wathi kum, Intliziyo yakho mayiwabambe amazwi am; Gcina imithetho yam, nobomi bam.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 5, 'Rhweba ubulumko, rhweba ingqiqo; musa ukuyilibala; kwaye ungaphambuki emazwini omlomo wam.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 6, 'Musa ukumshiya, wokugcina; mthande, wokugcina.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 7, 'Ubulumko yeyona nto ibalulekileyo; Rhweba ke ubulumko, urhwebe ingqondo nako konke ukuqonda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 8, 'Mphakamise, wokuphakamisa; uya kukuhlonipha xa umbuza.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 9, 'Buya kukunika isihombo sokuhomba entlokweni yakho; wokunika isithsaba sokuhomba.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 10, 'Phulaphula, ungunyana wam, uze uwamkele amazwi am; woba mininzi iminyaka yobomi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 11, 'Ndikuyalele indlela yobulumko; Ndikukhaphele ngeendlela ezithe tye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 12, 'Ekuhambeni kwakho akayi kuphazamiseka ukunyathela kwakho; nokuba uyabaleka, akuyi kukhubeka.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 13, 'Bamba ingqeqesho; musa ukumshiya; mgcine; ngokuba ububomi bakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 14, 'Musa ukungena emendweni wabangendawo, Ungahambi emendweni wabangendawo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 15, 'Yicezele, ungadluli kuyo; yijike, udlule.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 16, 'Kuba abalali, ababi benza ububi; Bomkelwa bubuthongo, ukuba abakhanga;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 17, 'Ngokuba badla isonka sokungendawo, Basele newayini yobutshijolo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 18, 'Kodwa umendo wamalungisa unjengokukhanya okuqaqambileyo okuqhubeka kukhanya de kube semini enkulu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 19, 'Indlela yabangendawo injengesithokothoko; abayazi into abakhubeka ngayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 20, 'Nyana wam, wabekele indlebe amazwi am; yiva amazwi endlebe yam.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 21, 'Musa ukuwashiya amehlo akho; zigcine entliziyweni yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 22, 'Kuba bubomi kwababufumanayo, usindiso enyameni yabo yonke.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 23, 'Yinike intliziyo yakho ngako konke ukunyameka; kuba ubutyebi bobomi buphuma kuyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 24, 'Shenxisa emlonyeni wobuxoki kuwe, mayibe kude kuwe emlonyeni womlomo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 25, 'Amehlo akho makakhangele kakuhle, neentshiyi zakho mazikhangeleke kakuhle.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 26, 'Qikelela umkhondo wonyawo lwakho, Uwumise wonke umendo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 4, 27, 'Musa ukutyekela ekunene nasekhohlo; Susa unyawo lwakho ebubini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 1, 'Nyana wam, buve ubulumko bam, Uyibazele indlebe ingqondo yam;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 2, 'Ukuze uqonde icebo, Nomlomo wakho ugcine ukwazi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 3, 'Kuba umlomo womfazi wasemzini uvuza njengenqatha lobusi, nemilebe yakhe ibuthelezi ngaphezu kweoli.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 4, 'Ke ukuphela kwakhe kukrakra njengomlambo, kubukhali njengekrele elintlangothi mbini;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 5, 'Iinyawo zakhe zehla zaya ekufeni; ukunyathela kwakhe ukuya emazantsi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 6, 'Musani ukuyicinga indlela yobomi, neendlela zabo, ukuze ningazazi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 7, '“Bantwana bam, ndiphulaphuleni ngoku, ningemki emazwini omlomo wam.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 8, 'Suka umke kuye, ungasondeli emnyango wendlu yakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 9, 'Ukuba ubungangamsha bakho ungabunikeli bambi, Iminyaka yakho uyinike isijorha;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 10, 'ukuze abasemzini banganeli bubutyebi benu; umsebenzi wakho usendlwini yolunye uhlanga;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 11, 'Ekugqibeleni uya kukhala, xa inyama yakho itshabalala kunye nomzimba wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 12, 'Ndathi, Ndikuthiyile uqeqesho, Hayi, ukuba bubi kwentliziyo yam!', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 13, 'Kwaye andizange ndiliphulaphule ilizwi labafundisi bam, kwaye andibaphulaphulanga abo bandifundisayo!', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 14, 'Ndaphantse ukuba sebubini bonke, Ophakathi kwebandla nebandla.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 15, 'Sela amanzi equleni lakho, namanzi aqukuqelayo equleni lakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 16, 'Makatwazeke amaqula akho, Yagaleleka imijelo yamanzi ezitratweni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 17, 'Mayibe yeyakho, ingabi yabasemzini kuni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 18, 'Malisikelelwe kakuhle, uvuye ngumfazi wobutsha bakho;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 19, 'Makabe njengenkunzi yebhokhwe ephilileyo, nentombi ethandekayo; Ngamana amabele akhe angakuhluthisa; yaye usoloko uchukunyiswa luthando lwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 20, 'Kutheni na wena, nyana wam, ufanele uthandwe ngumfazi wasemzini uze uqhwabe incanca yowasemzini?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 21, 'Kuba iindlela zomntu ziphambi kwamehlo kaYehova, yaye uyazazi zonke iindlela zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 22, 'Umenzi wobubi uya kuzithwala izono zakhe, abanjiswe yimixokelelwane yezono zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 5, 23, 'Uya kufa engenatyala; ebuninzini bokumatha kwakhe uya kulahleka.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 1, 'Nyana wam, xa uthe wammela ummelwane wakho, Naxa uthe wabambana nomnye ngesandla owasemzini,', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 2, 'Ubanjwe ngentetho yomlomo wakho, Ubanjwe ngamazwi omlomo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 3, 'Yenza ngoko, nyana wam, uzisindise, ukuba uthe wawa esandleni sommelwane wakho; hamba, zithobe kwaye uqinisekise umhlobo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 4, 'Musa ukuwayeka alale amehlo akho, namashiya akho makangalali;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 5, 'Zisindise njengexhama esandleni somzingeli, nanjengentaka esandleni somthiyeli.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 6, 'Yiya embovaneni, vilandini; Khangela iindlela zakhe, ulumke:', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 7, 'engenamkhokheli, namgcini, namlawuli;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 8, 'Siphe ukudla ehlotyeni; Yilungise ngexa lokuvuna;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 9, 'Kunini na ulala, vilandini? Uya kuvuka nini na ebuthongweni bakho?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 10, 'Ukulala kancinane, ukozela kancinane, ukusonga iingalo zikabani kancinane, ukulala.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 11, 'Bokuza ubuhlwempu bakho njengomhambi, Nentswelo yakho njengendoda exhobileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 12, 'Ongendawo, ongendawo uhamba ngomlomo wobubi;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 13, 'Utyanda ngoshiyi, uthetha ngeenyawo, Walatha ngeminwe yakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 14, 'Inkohliso isentliziyweni yakhe, uyila ububi ngamaxesha onke; uhlwayela iiyantlukwano.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 15, 'Ngako oko, intlekele yakhe iya kumfikela kube kanye; uya kwaphuka ngephanyazo, angaphili.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 16, 'Ezi ezintandathu uzithiyileyo uYehova, zasixhenxe zingamasikizi kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 17, 'Ngamehlo aqwayingayo, lulwimi lobuxoki; Zizandla eziphalaza igazi elimsulwa;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 18, 'Intliziyo eyila ububi, ziinyawo ezikhawulezayo ukubalekela ebubini;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 19, 'Lingqina elixokayo, elifutha amanga, Nongenisa ukungavisisani phakathi kwabazalwana.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 20, 'Nyana wam, gcina umthetho kayihlo, ungatyeki emyalelweni kanyoko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 21, 'Sibophe entliziyweni yakho ngamaxesha onke, Usinxibe emqaleni wakho;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 22, 'Ukuba uthe wahamba, uya kukukhokela; Ukuba ulala, buya kukugcina; yaye xa uvuka, iya kuthetha nawe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 23, 'Ngokuba ulukhanyiso umthetho; nomyalelo ulukhanyiso; Uqeqesho lwemfundo yindlela yobomi;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 24, 'Ukuba akukhwebuke kumfazi onobubi, Nolwimi olukhohlisayo lomkamntu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 25, 'Musa ukubukhanuka ubunzwakazi bakhe ngentliziyo yakho; makangayichukumisi ngamashiya.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 26, 'Kuba ngenxa yehenyukazi umntu udla iqhekeza lesonka; Umkamntu okrexezayo uzingela umphefumlo onqabileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 27, 'Umntu unokuwuthabatha na umlilo esifubeni sakhe, Zingatshi na iingubo zakhe?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 28, 'Unokuhamba na umntu phezu kwamalahle avuthayo, zingatshisi iinyawo zakhe?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 29, 'Lowo ungena nomfazi wommelwane wakhe; akasayi kuba msulwa lowo umchukumisayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 30, 'Alidelwa isela xa lisiba ukuze lihluthe, xa lithe lalamba;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 31, 'Ukuba uthe wafunyanwa, wobuya kasixhenxe; woyirhola yonke impahla yendlu yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 32, 'Okrexeza umfazi ke akanangqondo; owenjenjalo uyawonakalisa umphefumlo wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 33, 'Uya kufumana ububi nocukucezo; nongcikivo lwakhe alucimi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 34, 'Kuba ikhwele libubushushu bendoda; ke ngoko, akayi kuwuconga umhla wempindezelo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 6, 35, 'Ayiyi kulubeka ucamagusho; nokuba uthe wampha izipho ezininzi, akaneliswa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 1, 'Nyana wam, gcina intetho yam, uyigcine imithetho yam.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 2, 'Gcina imithetho yam, uphile; nomyalelo wam njengokhozo lweliso lakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 3, 'Sibophe eminweni yakho, sibhale elucwecweni lwentliziyo yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 4, 'Yithi, Ungudade wethu; uze ubize ukuqonda kwakho;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 5, 'Ukuze ugcinwe kumkamntu, Kowolunye uhlanga, okudumisa ngamazwi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 6, 'Kuba ngefestile yendlu yam, ndalunguza eluqayini lwam;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 7, 'Yabona, phakathi kwamadodana azizidenge, kukho umfana ongenangqondo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 8, 'Hamba esitratweni kufuphi nembombo yakhe; wagoduka.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 9, 'Ngokuhlwa, ngokuhlwa, kumnyama nakubumnyama;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 10, 'Wahlangatyezwa yinkazana ethiwe wambu ngehenyukazi, enentliziyo enobuqhokolo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 11, 'Ulukhuni, uyinjubaqa, Azihlali endlwini yakhe iinyawo zakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 12, 'Ngoku ungaphandle, ngoku usezitratweni, ulala eqongqotha iimbombo zonke.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 13, 'Ngoko wambamba waza wamanga waza wathi kuye ngobuso obuneentloni:', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 14, 'Ndinemibingelelo yombulelo ekum; namhlanje ndizifezile izibhambathiso zam.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 15, 'Ngenxa yoko ndiphume ndeza kukukhawulela, ndabufuna ubuso bakho ngenyameko, ndakufumana.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 16, 'Umandlalo wam ndawuhombisa ngelinen ecikizekileyo, ngemifanekiso eqingqiweyo, ngelinen ecikizekileyo yaseYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 17, 'Umandlalo wam ndiwuthambisa ngemore, nekhala, nesinamon.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 18, 'Yiza, sihluthe luthando kude kuse; sithuthuzele ngothando.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 19, 'Ekubeni indoda elungileyo ingekho ekhaya, ithabatha uhambo olude.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 20, 'Wayithabatha ingxowa yemali, waza wabuyela ekhaya ngomhla omisiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 21, 'Ngentetho yakhe emnandi kakhulu, wamenza waziva iimvakalelo zakhe, wamnyanzela ngokuphethula komlomo wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 22, 'Uyamsukela kamsinya njengenkunzi yenkomo isiya ekuxhelweni, nanjengesidenge xa ezolula iintonga zaso;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 23, 'Lwada utolo lwacanda esibindini sakhe; njengentaka esiwa emgibeni, ingazi ukuba isindiselwe umphefumlo wayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 24, 'Ke ngoko, bonyana, ndiveni, Niyibazele indlebe intetho yomlomo wam.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 25, 'Musa ukuyiyekela intliziyo yakho ixexezele ezindleleni zakhe, Ungatyeki ezindleleni zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 26, 'Kuba wawisa abaninzi abangxwelerhiweyo, kwabulawa naye abaninzi abanamandla.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 7, 27, 'Indlu yakhe iyindlela yendlu yofileyo, Ezihla ziye ezindlwini zokufa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 1, 'Abumemezi na ubulumko? Kwakutheni ukuze ilizwi lakhe livakale?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 2, 'Emantloko eendawo eziphezulu, ngasendleleni, emendweni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 3, 'Ubiza emasangweni, emasangweni omzi, emasangweni amasango;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 4, 'Ndibiza kuni, madoda; Ilizwi lam lisiya koonyana babantu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 5, 'Buqondeni ubulumko, zinyabi, zinyabi, yibani nentliziyo elumkileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 6, 'Yivani; kuba ndiya kuthetha izinto ezimangalisayo; nokuvula umlomo wam kuya kuba yinyaniso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 7, 'Ngokuba umlomo wam uxela inyaniso; Okungendawo kulisikizi emlonyeni wam.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 8, 'Yonke intetho yomlomo wam isebulungiseni; akukho nto igwenxa okanye itenxileyo kuzo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 9, 'Zonke izinto zisingise kwizilumko, zilungile kwabazuze ukwazi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 10, 'Yamkelani uqeqesho lwam, ningamkeli silivere; nolwazi ngaphezu kwegolide embiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 11, 'Kuba ubulumko bulungile ngaphezu kweeperile; nazo zonke izinto ezinqwenelekayo azinakulinganiswa nabo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 12, 'Mna, bulumko, ndihleli ngengqondo, Ndazuza ukwazi inzululwazi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 13, 'Ukoyika uYehova kukuthiya into embi; Ndikuthiyile ukuzidla, ukukratsha, indlela egwenxa, nomlomo ongendawo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 14, 'Inkumbulo yeyam, nobulumko bugqibelele; Yingqondo; Ndinamandla.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 15, 'Ookumkani balawula ngam, Nezidwangube ziceba ubulungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 16, 'Balawula ngam abathetheli, nabagwebi bonke belimiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 17, 'Abandithandayo ndiyabathanda nam; nabo bandifunayo baya kundifumana.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 18, 'Bunam ubutyebi nozuko; ewe, ubutyebi banaphakade nobulungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 19, 'Zilungile iziqhamo zam ngaphezu kwegolide embiweyo, nakwengcwengekileyo; umvuzo wam yisilivere esulungekileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 20, 'Ndihamba ngomendo wobulungisa, phakathi kweendlela ezisesikweni;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 21, 'Ukuze ndibenzele okulungileyo abandithandayo; ndibuzalise ubuncwane babo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 22, 'uYehova wandenza ndaba yintlahlela yendlela yakhe, Ndaba ngowamandulo emisebenzini yakhe yakudala.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 23, 'Mna ndasekwa kususela kumaxesha amandulo, kwasephakadeni, Kwasemaphakadeni elimiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 24, 'Ndazalwa kungekabikho bunzulu; kungekho maqula azele ngamanzi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 25, 'Iintaba azikasekwa, neenduli zingekaveli;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 26, 'Akenzanga hlabathi, namasimi, Nothuli lomhlaba.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 27, 'Ekulilungiseni kwakhe izulu, ndandikho apho;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 28, 'Ekuwatywineni kwakhe amafu phezulu, Ekutywineni kwakhe amaqula oonogumbe behlabathi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 29, 'uEnere waluwisela umthetho ulwandle, ukuba amanzi angawexuki umthetho wakhe, Ekuzimiseni kwakhe iziseko zehlabathi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 30, 'Ke kaloku ndandinaye, njengokungathi omnye esondlwe naye;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 31, 'Vuyani ngenxa yesahlulo sehlabathi; noyolo lwam lwalukoonyana babantu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 32, 'Bantwana bam, ndiveni kaloku, ngokuba hayi, uyolo lwabazigcinayo iindlela zam!', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 33, 'Yivani uqeqesho, nibe nobulumko, ningalushiyi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 34, 'Hayi, uyolo lomntu ondivayo, Ozigcinayo iingcango zam imihla yonke, Elondoloza iingcango zeminyango yam;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 35, 'Ngokuba ondifumeneyo mna ufumene ubomi, nenceba evela kuYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 8, 36, 'Ke yena ondingcatshayo utshabalalisa umphefumlo wakhe; bonke abandithiyileyo bathanda ukufa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 1, 'Ubulumko buyakhile indlu yabo, Zikroliwe iintsika zabo zosixhenxe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 2, 'Wazixhela iinkomo zakhe; Uyiphithikezile iwayini yakhe; walungisa netafile yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 3, 'Wathuma abakhonzazana bakhe; ubiza iindawo eziphakamileyo zesixeko;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 4, 'Masiphambukele apha isidenge;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 5, 'Yizani nidle isonka sam, nisele iwayini endiyiphithikezileyo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 6, 'Shiyani iziyatha, niphile; nihambe ngendlela yokuqonda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 7, 'Omthethisa umgxeki uzihlazisa ngokwakhe; ke yena omohlwayayo umenzi wobubi, umkela isiqalekiso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 8, 'Musa ukumthethisa umgxeki, hleze akuthiye; yohlwaya isilumko, sokuthanda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 9, 'Sifundise isilumko, solumka ngakumbi; fundisa indoda elungileyo, yoba nemfundo eninzi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 10, 'Ingqalo yobulumko kukoyika uYehova, nokwaziwa koyiNgcwele yingqiqo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 11, 'Ngenxa yam iya kuba mininzi imihla yakho, ibe mininzi iminyaka yobomi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 12, 'Ukuba uthe walumka, uya kuzifumanela ubulumko;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 13, 'Umfazi osisinyabi uyaxokozela, akazi nto, akazi nto;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 14, 'Ngokuba ehleli emnyango wendlu yakhe, Etroneni yakhe ezindaweni eziphakamileyo zesixeko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 15, 'Ndibize abakhweli abahamba kakuhle endleleni yabo:', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 16, 'Masiphambukele apha isidenge; wathi kuye lowo ubefuna ukuqonda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 17, 'Amanzi abiweyo anencasa, Nesonka esityiwa ngasese sinencasa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 9, 18, 'Akazi ukuba abafileyo bakhona; nokuba abamenywa bakhe basezinzulwini zelabafileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 1, 'Amazwi kaSolomon. Unyana osisilumko uyamvuyisa uyise; Ke unyana osisinyabi ngumthwalo kunina.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 2, 'Ubutyebi bokungendawo abuncedi lutho, Ke bona ubulungisa buhlangula ekufeni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 3, 'uYehova akawuyeki ufe yindlala umphefumlo welungisa, kodwa ubutyebi babangendawo uyayigxotha.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 4, 'Osebenza ngesandla esityhafileyo uba lihlwempu; Ke sona isandla sabakhutheleyo siyatyebisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 5, 'Obutha ehlotyeni uyinkwenkwe elumkileyo; Olalayo ngexa lokuvuna ngunyana olihlazo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 6, 'Ziintsikelelo entlokweni yelungisa; Ke wona umlomo wabangendawo ugubungela ugonyamelo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 7, 'Ukukhunjulwa kwelungisa kuhleli kunentsikelelo, Ke igama labangendawo liyabola.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 8, 'Intliziyo elumkileyo iyayamkela imiyalelo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 9, 'Ohamba ngobulungisa uhamba enyanisekile; Ke yena ojibilizayo ngeendlela zakhe uyaziwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 10, 'Oqhwanyazayo ubanga ububi, Ophaphazelayo uya kuwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 11, 'Lithende lobomi umlomo welungisa; Ke wona umlomo wabangendawo ugubungela ugonyamelo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 12, 'Intiyo ivelisa iqhenqa, kodwa uthando lugubungela zonke izono.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 13, 'Ubulumko bufumaneka emlonyeni wesilumko; Intonga isemhlana wesinyabi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 14, 'Isilumko siyalugcina ukwazi; Umlomo wesinyabi usondele kwintshabalalo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 15, 'Ubuncwane bobutyebi ngumzi wabo oliqele; intshabalalo yabasweleyo bubuhlwempu babo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 16, 'Umsebenzi welungisa usingisa ebomini; ke sona isiqhamo songendawo sisingisa esonweni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 17, 'Ogcina uqeqesho umendweni wobomi; Ophulukene noqeqesho uyandwendwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 18, 'Oyifihlayo intiyo ungumlomo wobuxoki; Othukayo usisidenge.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 19, 'Ukona kwamazwi amaninzi, akaswele nto; Owuvalayo umlomo sisilumko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 20, 'Yisilivere esulungekileyo ulwimi lwelungisa; Ke yona intliziyo yabangendawo yinto engento.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 21, 'Umlomo welungisa udlisa abaninzi; Izimathane zifa ngokuswela ubulumko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 22, 'Intsikelelo kaYehova iyatyebisa, kodwa ayibandisi ubuhlwempu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 23, 'Ngokuba kumnandi kwisidenge ukwenza ububi; Ubulumko bunobuqili kwindoda enengqondo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 24, 'Ukunxunguphala kongendawo kuya kuba phezu kwakhe; Ke akunqwenelayo amalungisa aya kunikwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 25, 'Njengoko udlula umoya wesaqhwithi, akabikho ongendawo; Ke lona ilungisa luseko lwaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 26, 'Njengeviniga emazinyweni, nanjengomsi emehlweni, kukwanjalo ukonakala kwabayithumileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 27, 'Ukoyika uYehova kongeza imihla; Ke yona iminyaka yabangendawo iyanqanyulwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 28, 'Ukulinda kwamalungisa luvuyo; Ukulinda kwabangendawo kuyadaka.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 29, 'Indlela kaYehova inamandla kumalungisa, kodwa abenzi bobubi baya kutshatyalaliswa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 30, 'Ilungisa alishukunyiswa naphakade; Ke bona abangendawo abayi kuphila emhlabeni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 31, 'Umlomo welungisa uxela ubulumko; Ulwimi olungendawo luyanqanyulwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 10, 32, 'Umlomo welungisa uyakwazi okwamkelekileyo; Ke yona imilebe yongendawo ithetha ubuxoki.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 1, 'Lisikizi kuYehova isikali esixokayo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 2, 'Kwafika ukukhukhumala, kofika ukucukucezwa; Ke bona abathobekileyo ubulumko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 3, 'Ubulungisa babalungileyo buyabakhapha; ke bona ububi babangendawo buyabatshabalalisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 4, 'Ubutyebi abuyincedi nganto ngemini yembandezelo; Ke bona ubulungisa buhlangula ekufeni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 5, 'Ubulungisa bogqibeleleyo bulungelelanisa indlela yakhe; Ongendawo ukhubeka ngokungendawo kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 6, 'Ubulungisa bamalungisa buyabasindisa, Ke bona abakreqi baya kubanjwa bubulukhuni babo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 7, 'Ekufeni kongendawo liyadaka ithemba lakhe; Ithemba labangendawo liyadaka.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 8, 'Ilungisa liyahlangulwa embandezelweni, Ongendawo afike endaweni yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 9, 'Intshembenxa iyamonakalisa ummelwane wayo ngomlomo; Ke wona amalungisa aya kusindiswa ngokwazi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 10, 'Ngokuhamba kakuhle kwamalungisa, umzi uyavuya; Ekutshabalaleni kongendawo kubakho uvuyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 11, 'Ngentsikelelo yelungisa siyaphaka nyiswa isixeko; Ngomlomo wabangendawo siyatshatyalaliswa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 12, 'Oswele ubulumko udela ummelwane wakhe; Ke indoda enengqondo izola.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 13, 'Umntu oshiyiweyo utyhila ucweyo; Ke yena ontliziyo inyanisekileyo uyayigubungela into.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 14, 'Ukuba akukho kucetyiswa, bayawa abantu; kodwa xa baninzi abacebisi lusindiso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 15, 'Okholosa ngowasemzini uya kuba sisilumko kuloo nto; Oyithiyileyo ibheyile uqinile.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 16, 'Umfazi olungileyo ugcina isidima; Amadoda anamandla agcina ubutyebi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 17, 'Uwuphethe kakuhle umphefumlo wakhe umntu onobubele; Ke yena osijorha uyawonakalisa umzimba wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 18, 'Ongendawo uyinkohliso; Ke yena ohlwayela ubulungisa unomvuzo oyinyaniso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 19, 'Ubulungisa busingisa ebomini; Ophuthuma ububi usukela ukufa kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 20, 'Balisikizi kuYehova abantliziyo ingendawo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 21, 'Noko ke, ukuba kuxhawula isandla, umntu ongendawo akafuni kohlwaywa, kodwa inzala yamalungisa iyasinda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 22, 'Njengegolide empumlweni yehagu, Uyinzwakazi eswele ukuqonda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 23, 'Umnqweno wamalungisa yinto elungileyo; Ke ithemba labangendawo kukuphuphuma komsindo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 24, 'Kukho ohlakazayo, eyanda; kwaye kukho uthintelo ngaphezu kokuyimfuneko, kodwa lutyekela ekusweleni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 25, 'Umoya onobubele uyatyeba;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 26, 'Olahla ingqolowa, uyamqalekiswa ngabantu; kodwa ithamsanqa liya kuba entlokweni yalowo uthengisayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 27, 'Ongxamele okulungileyo ufuna okwamkelekileyo; Ongxamele ububi, buya kumfikela.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 28, 'Okholosa ngobutyebi bakhe uya kuwa yena, Ke wona amalungisa ayavuka njengokhula.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 29, 'Oyivusayo indlu yakhe uya kuwudla ilifa umphefumlo wakhe; Isinyabi siya kukhonza izilumko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 30, 'Isiqhamo selungisa ngumthi wobomi; nalowo ubamba imiphefumlo elumkileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 11, 31, 'Qaphelani, ilungisa liya kuphindezelwa ehlabathini, ngakumbi abakhohlakeleyo nomoni!', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 1, 'Uthanda uqeqesho othanda ukwazi; Uthiya isohlwayo úthiyile.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 2, 'Olungileyo uyamkeleka kuYehova; Ke yena oyila ububi uphuma kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 3, 'Akuzimaseki mntu, enokungendawo; Ke yona ingcambu yamalungisa ayinakushukunyiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 4, 'Umfazi olungileyo sisithsaba endodeni yakhe; Ke yena ohlazileyo unjengokubola emathanjeni ayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 5, 'Iingcinga zamalungisa zinobulungisa; Iingcinga zabangendawo yinkohliso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 6, 'Amazwi abangendawo afuna igazi; Ke wona umlomo wamalungisa uyabasindisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 7, 'Batshabalala abangendawo, ababikho; Indlu yamalungisa iyema.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 8, 'Indoda idunyiswa ngokobulumko bayo, Intliziyo engendawo ideliwe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 9, 'Ulungile ophantsi enesicaka esilungileyo, ngaphezu kozidlayo oswele ukudla.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 10, 'Ilungisa liyawazalelela umphefumlo wenkomo yalo; Iimfesane zabangendawo zibubujorha.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 11, 'Owusebenzayo amasimi akhe uya kuhlutha kukudla;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 12, 'Ongendawo ukhanuka okuzingelwa ngabangendawo; Ke yona ingcambu yamalungisa iyanika.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 13, 'Isiphoso somlomo wakhe sibanjwe ongendawo, Ke lona ilungisa liyahlangulwa embandezelweni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 14, 'Umntu uyahlutha kokulungileyo ngesiqhamo somlomo wakhe, aze umntu afumane umvuzo womvuzo wezandla zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 15, 'Indlela yesimathane ithe tye kwamehlo akho; Ophulaphula ukucetyiswa usisilumko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 16, 'Isimathane siyaziwa ngomsindo wesinyabi; Ke sona isilumko siyakufihla ukucukucezwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 17, 'Othetha inyaniso uxela ubulungisa; Ingqina elixokayo liyinkohliso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 18, 'Kukho abathetha njengokuhlaba kwekrele, kodwa ulwimi lwezilumko luphilile.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 19, 'Umlomo wenyaniso umi ngonaphakade; Ke lona ulwimi oluxokayo lolwephanyazo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 20, 'Inkohliso isentliziyweni yabayila ububi; Ke bona abacebi boxolo bayavuya.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 21, 'Ilungisa aliqubisani nobubi; Ke bona abangendawo bazala bububi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 22, 'Ilisikizi kuYehova umlomo oxokayo, kodwa abo benza ngenyaniso ukholekile kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 23, 'Isilumko sikufihla ukwazi; Intliziyo yesinyabi ivakalisa ukumatha.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 24, 'Isandla sabasebenzayo siya kulawula, ke sona ivila liya kohlwaywa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 25, 'Imbandezelo entliziyweni yendoda iyenza igobe; Liyayivuyisa ilizwi elihle.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 26, 'Ilungisa ligqithisela ummelwane walo ngobuhle; Ke indlela yabangendawo iyamlahlekisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 27, 'Ikhoboka aliyi kubanjiswa lizingela, kodwa impahla yomntu okhutheleyo ixabisekile.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 12, 28, 'Busemendweni wobulungisa ubomi; kwaye akukho kufa emendweni wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 1, 'Unyana osisilumko uva uqeqesho lukayise; Ke yena umgxeki akeva kukhalinyelwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 2, 'Umntu uya kudla isiqhamo somlomo wakhe, kodwa umphefumlo wabakreqi uya kudla ugonyamelo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 3, 'Obambe umlomo wakhe ugcine umphefumlo wakhe; Owuvulayo umlomo wakhe uyatshabalala.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 4, 'Umphefumlo womntu omdala uyanqwena, awuzuzi;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 5, 'Ilungisa liyithiyile into ebubuxoki; Ke yena ongendawo ulisikizi, uneentloni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 6, 'Kusesikweni ukuligcina ilungisa endleleni; Okungendawo kuyamtshabalalisa umoni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 7, 'Kukho ozenza isityebi, engenayo nento; Kukho ozenza isisweli, kanti usisityebi kunene.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 8, 'Ucamagusho lomphefumlo wendoda bubutyebi bayo; Osweleyo akeva kululekwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 9, 'Ukukhanya kwelungisa kuyavuya, Ke sona isibane sabangendawo siyacinywa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 10, 'Ukukhukhumala kusenza sibe nehlazo kuphela, kodwa ubulumko bunabanokwazi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 11, 'Ubutyebi ofunyanwa ngelize buya kuncipha; Ke yena owandisa ngomsebenzi uya kubanda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 12, 'Ukulindela okubanjezelweyo kubulala intliziyo; Umnqweno xa uthe wafika, ngumthi wobomi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 13, 'Odela ilizwi uya kutshabalala; Owoyikayo umyalelo uya kufumana umvuzo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 14, 'Umyalelo wesilumko liqula lobomi, Ukuze kumkiwe ezirhintyelweni zokufa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 15, 'Ingqondo entle iyamkeleka; Ke yona indlela yabakreqi inzima.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 16, 'Sonke isilumko sisebenza ngokwazi; Isinyabi siya kwaneka ukumatha.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 17, 'Umthunywa ongendawo weyela ebubini; Umthunywa othembekileyo uyaphilisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 18, 'Ubuhlwempu nocukucezo lomntu osilahlayo isohlwayo; Osihlonelayo isohlwayo uyazukiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 19, 'Umnqweno ogqibeleleyo unencasa emphefumlweni; Ke ukusuka ebubini kulisikizi kwisinyabi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 20, 'Ohamba nezilumko uba sisilumko naye; Ke yena olikholwane lesidenge uyatshabalala.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 21, 'Aboni basukelwa bububi; Ke wona amalungisa ayavuzwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 22, 'Olungileyo ushiya ilifa kubantwana bakhe, Ke ubutyebi bomoni bugcinelwe ilungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 23, 'Intsimi yehlwempu inokutya okuninzi, kanti ke into yonakala ngenxa yokuswela isigwebo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 24, 'Ophethe intonga umthiyile unyana wakhe; ke omthandayo umqeqesha esemncinane.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 13, 25, 'Ilungisa lidla wahlutha umphefumlo walo; Ke sona isisu songendawo siyalamba.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 1, 'Ubulumko bomfazi buyayakha indlu yakhe; Isinyabi siyayichitha ngezakhe izandla.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 2, 'Uhamba ngobulungisa bakhe uyamoyika uYehova; Ongendawo ngeendlela zakhe uyamdela.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 3, 'Emlonyeni wesinyabi kukho intonga yekratshi; Umlomo wezilumko uyazisindisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 4, 'Apho kungekho nkomo, umkhombe uhlambulukile;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 5, 'Ingqina elinyanisileyo aliwathethi amanga; Ke lifutha amanga ingqina elixokayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 6, 'Umgxeki ufuna ubulumko, angabufumani, kodwa ukwazi kulula kohlakaniphileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 7, 'Suka ebusweni begeza; Ukuba akuwubonanga umlomo wokwazi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 8, 'Ubulumko bosisilumko kukuyiqonda indlela yaso; Ukumatha kwezinyabi yinkohliso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 9, 'Isono sigculela izimathane; Phakathi kwamalungisa yinceba.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 10, 'Intliziyo iyazazi iintlungu zayo; kwaye owasemzini akanxulumani nolonwabo lwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 11, 'Indlu yabangendawo iyatshatyalaliswa; Ke intente yamalungisa iyachuma.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 12, 'Kukho indlela ethe tye emehlweni omntu, Ukanti ukuphela kwayo ziindlela zokufa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 13, 'Nasekuhlekeni intliziyo inomvandedwa; kwaye isiphelo saloo lonwabo sinzima.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 14, 'Intliziyo ewexukileyo yanelisa iindlela zakhe, yaye umntu olungileyo uhlutha bubomi bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 15, 'Isimathane sikholwa yinto yonke, Ke sona isilumko siyazazi iindlela zaso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 16, 'Isilumko siyoyika, sisuke ebubini; Ke sona isinyabi siyaqumba, sikholosile.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 17, 'Ozeka kade umsindo wenza ngobudenge, nomntu oyila ububi uthiyiwe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 18, 'Ilifa lesimathane kukumatha; Ke zona izilumko zithwele ukwazi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 19, 'Abenzi bobubi basibekeka phambi kwabalungileyo; nabangendawo emasangweni amalungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 20, 'Ihlwempu lithiywa kowalo umzi; Ke bona isityebi siba nabahlobo abaninzi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 21, 'Omgxekayo ummelwane wakhe uyona; Obabala abaziintsizana, uyolo lwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 22, 'Abayi kulahlekiswa na abayila ububi? Ke yona inceba nenyaniso iba kwabacinga okulungileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 23, 'Kuwo wonke umsebenzi kukho ingeniso, kodwa ukuthetha ngomlomo kungaphumeleli.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 24, 'Umthwalo wezilumko bubutyebi bazo; Ukumatha kwezinyabi kukumatha.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 25, 'Ingqina lenyaniso lisindisa imiphefumlo; Ke elifutha amanga lifutha amanga.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 26, 'Ekoyikeni uYehova kukho ithemba eliqinileyo, nabantwana bakhe baya kuba nendawo yokusabela.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 27, 'Ukoyika uYehova lithende lobomi, Ukuze kusukwe ezirhintyelweni zokufa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 28, 'Ubungangamsha bokumkani buphakathi kwezizwe ezininzi; Ke ukutshabalala kwesidwangube kukuswela kwabantu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 29, 'Ozeka kade umsindo unengqondo eninzi;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 30, 'Bubomi benyama intliziyo epholileyo; Inomona ke wona ukubola kwamathambo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 31, 'Ocudisa isisweli ukhanyela uMdali wakhe; Ke yena omhlonelayo unenceba kumahlwempu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 32, 'Ongendawo utshatyalaliswa bububi bakhe; Ke lona ilungisa lilinda ukufa kwalo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 33, 'Entliziyweni yonengqondo buyahlala ubulumko; Ke yona intliziyo yesinyabi iyaziwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 34, 'Ubulungisa buyaphakamisa uhlanga; Ke sona isono lihlazo kuhlanga lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 14, 35, 'Ububele bokumkani bukwikhoboka elisisilumko, kodwa umsindo wakhe unxamnye nehlazo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 1, 'Impendulo ethambileyo ibuyisa ubushushu; Ilizwi elidubulayo linyusa umsindo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 2, 'Ulwimi lwezilumko lulungisa ukwazi; Ke yona imilebe yesinyabi impompoza ukumatha.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 3, 'Amehlo kaYehova akuyo yonke indawo, yaye abona ababi nabalungileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 4, 'Ukuphola kolwimi ngumthi wobomi;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 5, 'Isimathane sigiba uqeqesho lukayise; Osigcinileyo isohlwayo sisilumko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 6, 'Indlu yelungisa nguvimba omkhulu; ke wona umvuzo wongendawo ngamashwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 7, 'Umlomo wesilumko usasaza ukwazi: Ke yona intliziyo yesinyabi ayinanto.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 8, 'Umbingelelo wabangendawo lisikizi kuYehova; Ke wona umthandazo wamalungisa luvuyo lwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 9, 'Ilisikizi kuYehova indlela yongendawo; ke ophuthuma ubulungisa uyamthanda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 10, 'Isohlwayo siqatha kojika endleleni; othiya isohlwayo uya kufa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 11, 'Yintlekele nentshabalalo phambi koYehova; kukangakanani ke kunentliziyo yoonyana babantu?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 12, 'Umgxeki akakuthandi ukohlwaywa, Akayi kwizilumko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 13, 'Intliziyo evuyileyo iyabuchwayithisa ubuso; Ubuhlungu bubuhlungu bentliziyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 14, 'Intliziyo enengqondo ifuna ukwazi; Umlomo wesinyabi usukelana nokumatha.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 15, 'Yonke imihla yesisweli mibi; Ke yena ontliziyo ichwayithileyo uhlala evuya.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 16, 'Intwana yokoyika uYehova ilungile, Ngaphezu kobutyebi obuninzi neembandezelo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 17, 'Ukutya imifuno kuphela apho kukho uthando kulunge ngaphezu kokutyiwa yinkukhu enentiyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 18, 'Umntu onomsindo uxhaya ingxabano;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 19, 'Indlela yesimathane injengothango lweminga; Ke yona indlela yamalungisa iqaqambile.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 20, 'Umntwana osisilumko uyamvuyisa uyise; Umntu osisinyabi udela unina.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 21, 'Ukumatha lunoyolo oswele ubulumko; Ke indoda enengqondo ithi tye ukuhamba.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 22, 'Iingcinga ziyadana ngokungabikho kokucweya; Ke zona zima ngamaphakathi amaninzi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 23, 'Unoyolo umntu ngempendulo yomlomo wakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 24, 'Indlela yobomi iphakamile kunobulumko, Ukuba alishiye elabafileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 25, 'uYehova uyayincothula indlu yabanekratshi, Amise umlimandlela womhlolokazi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 26, 'Zingamasikizi kuYehova iingcinga zongendawo; Ke amazwi ahlambulukileyo ayathandeka.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 27, 'Olungileyo uyihlisela ububi indlu yakhe; Ke yena othiya izibabalo uya kudla ubomi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 28, 'Intliziyo yelungisa iya kuphendula; Ke yona imilebe yongendawo impompoza ububi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 29, 'uYehova ukude nabangendawo, kodwa uyawuva umthandazo wamalungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 30, 'Ukukhanya kwamehlo kuvuyisa intliziyo; Iindaba ezimnandi zityebisa amathambo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 31, 'Indlebe esivayo isohlwayo sobomi, Ihlala phakathi kwezilumko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 32, 'Ophulukene noqeqesho ucekisa umphefumlo wakhe; Osivayo isohlwayo uba nokuqonda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 15, 33, 'Ukoyika uYehova luqeqesho lobulumko; kwaye ukuthobeka kukhokela isidima.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 1, 'Ingqondo yentliziyo isebantwini; Ke yona impendulo yolwimi ivela kuYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 2, 'Zonke iindlela zendoda ziqaqambile emehlweni ayo; NguYehova olinganiselayo imiphefumlo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 3, 'Ziyekele kuYehova izenzo zakho, Zizimase iingcinga zakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 4, 'Zonke izinto uYehova uzenzele ngokwakhe, kwanongendawo uzenzele imini yeshwangusha.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 5, 'Balisikizi kuYehova bonke abantliziyo izidlayo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 6, 'Ngenceba nenyaniso buyahlanjululwa ubungendawo; Ngokoyika uYehova abantu bayatyeka ebubini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 7, 'Xa iindlela zomntu zikholekile kuYehova, wenza kwaneentshaba zakhe zibe seluxolweni naye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 8, 'Umvuzo omncinane osesikweni ulungile kunomvuzo omkhulu wokungalungisi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 9, 'Intliziyo yomntu icinga indlela yakhe; NguYehova oyalela ukunyathela kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 10, 'Isigwebo sobuthixo sisemlonyeni wokumkani; umlomo wakhe awugwebi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 11, 'Isikali esisesikweni nesikali sesikaYehova; Yonke imilinganiso yengxowa ingumsebenzi wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 12, 'Lisikizi kubo ookumkani ukwenza okungendawo, Kuba itrone izinziswa bubulungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 13, 'Ukumkani uyavuyiswa ngumlomo wobulungisa; yaye bayamthanda Lowo uthetha inyaniso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 14, 'Umsindo wokumkani unjengezithunywa zokufa; Ke indoda elumkileyo iyakuzola.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 15, 'Ekukhanyeni kobuso bokumkani kukho ubomi; uvuyo lwakhe lunjengelifu lemvula yasekwindla.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 16, 'Ukurhweba ubulumko kungakanani na ukulunga kwako, ngaphezu kwegolide embiweyo! nokuzuza ukuqonda kulunge ngakumbi kunesilivere!', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 17, 'Ubuninzi bendlela yelungisa kukutyeka ebubini; Ogcina indlela yakhe ugcine umphefumlo wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 18, 'Ikratshi likhokelela entshabalalweni;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 19, 'Kulungile ukuba nokuthobeka kwabalulamileyo, Ngaphezu kokwabelana ngamaxhoba nabanekratshi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 20, 'Oyilungisayo imicimbi uya kufumana okulungileyo; ke yena okholose ngoYehova, hayi, uyolo lwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 21, 'Ontliziyo ilumkileyo kuthiwa sisilumko; Nomlomo omnandi wongeza imfundiso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 22, 'Ingqondo ingumthombo wobomi kumniniyo; Ke isohlwayo sesinyabi bubudenge.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 23, 'Intliziyo yesilumko iyawuqiqisa umlomo waso, Songeze uqeqesho emlonyeni waso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 24, 'Linqatha lobusi amazwi amnandi, amnandi emphefumlweni, aphilisa emathanjeni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 25, 'Kukho indlela ethe tye emehlweni omntu, Ukanti ukuphela kwayo ziindlela zokufa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 26, 'Lowo ubulalekayo uzenza buthathaka; ngokuba umlomo wakhe uyamcebisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 27, 'Ongendawo umba ububi, Emlonyeni wakhe ngathi ngumlilo otshayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 28, 'Umntu osisinyabi ungenisa intlebendwane;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 29, 'Umntu okhohlakeleyo ungcatsha usapho lwakhe, amkhokelele ngendlela engalunganga.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 30, 'Owavala amehlo akhe, ukuba acinge ububi; ngokushukumisa umlomo wakhe ubonakalisa ububi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 31, 'Isithsaba sokuhomba zizimvi, Sifunyanwa endleleni yobulungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 32, 'Ozeka kade umsindo ulunge ngaphezu kwegorha; Owulawulayo umphefumlo wakhe ufana nomntu othimba isixeko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 16, 33, 'Kuphosa iqashiso emkhombeni; kodwa sonke isimo sawo sivela kuYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 1, 'Indawo engumqwebedu, enoxolo, ilungile Ngaphezu kwendlu ezele luqhumiso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 2, 'Umkhonzi onengqiqo uya kumlawula unyana oziintloni, abe nesahlulo selifa phakathi kwabazalwana.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 3, 'Imbiza yeyesilivere negolide eziko; Umcikidi weentliziyo nguYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 4, 'Ongendawo uwubazela indlebe umlomo wobuxoki; Umntu oxokayo uliphulaphula ngolwimi olungendawo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 5, 'Ogculela ihlwempu udela uMdali walo; yaye ovuyela ilishwa akayi kufuna ukohlwaywa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 6, 'Isithsaba samadoda amakhulu sisithsaba soonyana; Isihombo sabantwana nguyise.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 7, 'Ilizwi elilungileyo alisebenzi isidenge;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 8, 'Sililitye elinqabileyo emehlweni alowo unalo isipho;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 9, 'Olufihlayo ukreqo ufuna uthando; kodwa umbalisi wohlula abahlobo abaninzi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 10, 'Isilumko sifikelwa sisohlwayo ngaphezu kwekhulu kwisinyabi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 11, 'Abangendawo bafuna ukutyeka bodwa; ke ngoko kuya kuthunyelwa kuye umthunywa okhohlakeleyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 12, 'Kulungile ukuhlangana nebhere ehluthe abantwana bayo, Ngaphezu kokuhlangana nesidenge ebudeni baso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 13, 'Obuyekeza ububi ngokulungileyo, akayi kuyishiya indlu yakhe ububi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 14, 'Kunjengokukha amanzi, kukuqala kwengxabano; ngoko yiyeke ingxabano ngaphambi kokuba ungenelele.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 15, 'Omgwebelayo ongendawo, kwanoligwebayo ilungisa, bangamasikizi kuYehova bobabini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 16, 'Yini na ukuba kukho umvuzo esandleni sesinyabi, ukuba sifumane ubulumko, wena ungenantliziyo kubo?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 17, 'Umhlobo uthanda ngamaxesha onke; Umzalwana uzalelwe embandezelweni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 18, 'Umntu ongaqondiyo ubamba ngesandla, Uboleka phambi kommelwane wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 19, 'Othanda ukunyelisa uthanda ukunxaxha;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 20, 'Ontliziyo inobubi akafumani okulungileyo; Ulwimi olungendawo lweyela ebubini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 21, 'Ozala iesile usisisweli; Akanakonwaba uyise wedonki.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 22, 'Intliziyo evuyileyo iyalungisa, ichachise; Umoya odakumbileyo uyawomisa amathambo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 23, 'Ongendawo uthabatha isicengo emkhombeni, Ukuze ayijike indlela yesiko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 24, 'Ubulumko buphambi konengqondo; ke wona amehlo esidenge abuyela eziphelweni zehlabathi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 25, 'Ubuhlungu kuyise umntwana osisiyatha, nentlungu kulowo wamzalayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 26, 'Akulungile ukohlwaya ilungisa, nokohlwaya amanene ngenxa yobulungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 27, 'Owanqandayo amazwi akhe unokwazi; Onengqondo ingumphefumlo olungisayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 17, 28, 'Kwanesidenge, xa sathe cwaka, kuthiwa sisilumko; nalowo uwuvalayo umlomo wakhe ugqalwa njengonengqondo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 1, 'Uzifunela ngomnqweno wakhe umntu ongento, Obuthwala bonke ubulumko;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 2, 'Ubudenge abukholiswa yingqondo yakho;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 3, 'Ekufikeni kongendawo kuya kuba yindelo, nokudela;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 4, 'Ngamanzi enzonzobila amazwi omlomo womntu, nomthombo wobulumko ngumlambo oqukuqelayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 5, 'Akulungile ukubamkela ubuso babangendawo, Nokuliwisa olilungisa ekugwebeni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 6, 'Umlomo wesinyabi uyabethana, Nomlomo waso ukhala;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 7, 'Umlomo wesinyabi yintshabalalo yaso, Nomlomo waso sisirhintyelo somphefumlo waso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 8, 'Amazwi entlebi anjengamanxeba, ahla aye embilinini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 9, 'Lowo udlala ngothando emsebenzini wakhe ukwangumzalwana wakhe osisaphuli-mthetho esikhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 10, 'Yinqaba eliqele igama likaYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 11, 'Ubuncwane bobutyebi ngumzi wabo oyinqaba, Njengodonga oluphakamileyo lwekratshi labo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 12, 'Intliziyo yendoda inekratshi ngaphambi kwentshabalalo, Ukuthobeka kukhokela indumiso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 13, 'Ophendula engekaviwa, usisidenge, uneentloni kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 14, 'Umphefumlo womntu uya kusigcina isifo sakhe; Umoya owaphukileyo ngubani na ongawunyamezelayo?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 15, 'Intliziyo yesilumko ifumana ukwazi; indlebe yezilumko ifuna ukwazi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 16, 'Isipho somntu siyamvulela ithuba, simzise phambi kwamadoda amakhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 17, 'Lowo ufika kuqala ekugwebeni kwakhe ubonakala elungile; Weza ummelwane wakhe, wamgocagoca.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 18, 'Ikamva lipheliswa iimfazwe, kwahlula abomeleleyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 19, 'Mzalwana wam, umntu okreqileyo ungaphezu kwesixeko esiliqele, neendonga zaso zinjengemivalo yenqaba.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 20, 'Umntu uyahlutha sisiqhamo somlomo wakhe isisu; uya kwanela ngobuninzi bomlomo wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 21, 'Ukufa nobomi kusemandleni olwimi, yaye abo baluthandayo baya kudla iziqhamo zalo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 22, 'Othe wafumana umfazi, ufumene okulungileyo, ukholekile kuYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 23, 'Ihlwempu liyathandaza; zaphendula izityebi ngezwi elikhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 18, 24, 'Umntu onobuhlobo ufanele abe nobuhlobo; kodwa kukho umhlobo obambelela ngaphezu komntakwenu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 1, 'Lilungile ihlwempu elihamba ngobulungisa balo, ngaphezu kothetha kakubi, ke sona isinyabi sona.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 2, 'Kanjalo, xa umphefumlo uswele ukwazi, akulungile; Ke yena onyawo zingxamayo wenza isono.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 3, 'Ukumatha komntu kuphenula indlela yakhe; Ijalele uYehova intliziyo yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 4, 'Ukutyeba kongeza izihlobo ezininzi; kodwa ihlwempu liyahlukaniswa nendlu yalo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 5, 'Ingqina elixokayo alibi msulwa, nexoki alisindi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 6, 'Baninzi abaya kucela inceba kukumkani; elowo ke sisihlobo sikalowo uphayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 7, 'Bonke abazalwana behlwempu balithiyile; kangakanani, abahlobo bakhe bemka kuye? uyawasukela ngamazwi, asuke atyhafe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 8, 'Owuzuza ilifa ubulumko uthanda umphefumlo wakhe; Ogcina ingqondo uya kufumana okulungileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 9, 'Ingqina elixokayo alibi msulwa; Ofutha amanga uyatshabalala.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 10, 'Uvuyo alusifanelanga isidenge; ngakumbi xa umkhonzi elawula abathetheli.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 11, 'Intliziyo yomntu izeka kade umsindo; yaye sisihombo sakhe ukukubetha ngoyaba ukunxaxha.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 12, 'Kukugquma kwengonyama entsha umsindo wokumkani; Ke uvuyo lwakhe lunjengombethe engceni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 13, 'Ulishwa likayise umntwana osisinyabi; Ke ingxabano yomfazi ngumda ongunaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 14, 'Indlu nobutyebi lilifa looyise; Ke yena umfazi osisilumko uvela kuYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 15, 'Ubuvila bukhokelela ebuthongweni obukhulu; nomphefumlo wabafileyo uya kufa yindlala.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 16, 'Owugcinayo umyalelo ugcine umphefumlo wakhe; Ozidelayo iindlela zakhe uya kufa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 17, 'Obabala isisweli uboleka uYehova; yaye uya kumbuyekeza oko wamnika kona.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 18, 'Mqeqeshe unyana wakho, xa kusekho ithemba, Ungawucongi umphefumlo wakho ngenxa yokukhala kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 19, 'Onomsindo omkhulu umelwe kukuhlawula, kuba xa uthe wamhlangula, uya kuphinda enze kwaloo nto.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 20, 'Live icebo, ulwamkele uqeqesho, Ukuze ulumke ekupheleni kwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 21, 'Zininzi iingcinga entliziyweni yomntu; kodwa injongo kaYehova iya kuqina.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 22, 'Umnqweno womntu yinceba yakhe; Ke lilungile ihlwempu ngaphezu kwendoda enamanga.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 23, 'Ukoyika uYehova kusa ebomini, Onako uya kwanela; akayi kuvelelwa bububi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 24, 'Ukubola kusifaka isandla sakhe esifubeni sakhe, kungasibuyiseli emlonyeni wayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 25, 'Umbethile umgxeki, sibaze isidenge; Umohlwaye onengqondo, woqonda azi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 26, 'Ombhuqayo uyise, omgxothayo unina, Ngunyana owenza okuziintloni, ohlazisayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 27, 'Nyana wam, musa ukumamela amazwi obulumko alahlekisayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 28, 'Ingqina elingendawo lidela isiko, Nomlomo ongendawo udla ubutshinga.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 19, 29, 'Izigwebo zilungiselwe abagxeki;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 1, 'Ingumgxeki iwayini, singxola isiselo esinxilisayo; kwaye nabani na olahlekiswa yiyo akalumkanga.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 2, 'Ngumgqumo onjengowengonyama entsha umothuso wokumkani; Omgculelayo wona umphefumlo wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 3, 'Kuluzuko endodeni ukupheza ingxabano; Ke sona isinyabi siyayinqanda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 4, 'Ukubola akuyi kukhula ngenxa yengqele; ngoko ke, xa lithe lavunwa, liya kucela, lingaswele nto.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 5, 'Ngamanzi anzulu icebo entliziyweni yendoda; Ke indoda enengqondo iya kuyikhupha.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 6, 'Abantu abaninzi baya kuvakalisa ukulunga kwakhe, kodwa ngubani na onokufumana indoda ethembekileyo?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 7, 'Ilungisa lihamba ngobulungisa balo; mabasikeleleke abantwana bakhe emva kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 8, 'Ukumkani, ehleli esihlalweni sokugweba, Uchithachitha ububi bonke ngamehlo akhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 9, 'Ngubani na ongathi, Ndiyihlambulule intliziyo yam, Ndihlambulukile esonweni sam?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 10, 'Ngamasikizi kuYehova zombini iiefa neeefa ngeefa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 11, 'Kwanenkwenkwe iyaziwa ngezenzo zayo, ukuba kuqaqambile na, nokuba kubulungisa na, nokuba kunyulu, kusini na.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 12, 'Indlebe evayo, neliso elibonayo, uYehova wazenza zombini ezi zinto.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 13, 'Musa ukuthanda ubuthongo, hleze uhlwempuzeke; vula amehlo akho, uya kuhlutha sisonka.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 14, 'Akunto, akunto, utsho umthengi; athi ke emkile aqhayise.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 15, 'Ininzi igolide neerubhi, Ke wona umlomo wokwazi sisivatho esinqabileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 16, 'Thabatha ingubo yolunye uhlanga, uthabathe isibambiso kuye ngenxa yomfazi wolunye uhlanga.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 17, 'Sinencasa emntwini isonka sobuxoki; kodwa kamva, umlomo wakhe uya kuzaliswa luhlalutye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 18, 'Iingcinga zonke zicetywa bubulumko;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 19, 'Ohamba ehleba uhlakaza ucweyo; Ngoko ke musa ukumphazamisa odumisa ngomlomo wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 20, 'Othuka uyise nokuba ngunina, Isibane sakhe siya kucinywa ebumnyameni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 21, 'Ilifa linokufunyanwa ngokukhawuleza ekuqalekeni; kodwa ukuphela kwayo akuyi kusikelelwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 22, 'Musa ukuthi, Ndiya kubuphindezela ububi; wena nje ukholose ngoYehova, wokusindisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 23, 'Ngamasikizi kuYehova ubunzima; kwaye iqondo elingalunganga alilungile.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 24, 'Iindlela zomntu ziphuma kuYehova; Umntu angathini na ukuyiqonda indlela yakhe?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 25, 'Esi sisirhintyelo kumntu othe watya ukutya okungcwele, aze abuze ngesibhambathiso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 26, 'Uchithachitha abangendawo ukumkani olumkileyo, Aguqulele phezu kwabo ivili elijikelezayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 27, 'Sisibane sikaYehova umphefumlo womntu, Owahlolisisayo onke amathumbu esisu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 28, 'Inceba nenyaniso ikhusela ukumkani, Uyixhasa itrone yakhe ngenceba.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 29, 'Isihombo samadodana ngamandla awo; Isihombo samadoda amakhulu zizimvi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 20, 30, 'Ububomvu benxeba buguxa ububi; kuyafana nakwimithambo engaphakathi esiswini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 1, 'Yimijelo yamanzi intliziyo yokumkani esandleni sikaYehova; Usalathisa apho athanda khona.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 2, 'Zonke iindlela zendoda zithe tye kwawayo amehlo; Uyigocagocile intliziyo uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 3, 'Ukwenza okusesikweni nomgwebo kukholekile kuYehova ngaphezu kombingelelo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 4, 'Amehlo aqwayingayo, nokuqwayinga kwentliziyo, Kwanekhuba labangendawo, sisono.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 5, 'Iingcinga zamatshijolo ziba bubutyebi bodwa; ke bonke abangxamayo bayaswela.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 6, 'Ukuzuza ubutyebi ngolwimi oluxokayo Ngumphunga ophephezelwa ngabafuna ukufa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 7, 'Ukubhuqwa kwabangendawo kuyabaqweqwedisa; ngokuba abavumi ukugweba.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 8, 'Ilibi, ilungile indlela yendoda; Ke yena ohlambulukileyo, umsebenzi wakhe ulungile.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 9, 'Kulungile ukuhlala elungqamekweni oluphezu kwendlu, Kunokuhlala ndlwini-nye nomfazi onengxabano.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 10, 'Umoya wongendawo unqwenela ububi, Ummelwane wakhe akayiboni inceba emehlweni akhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 11, 'Ekubethwa komgxeki siyalumka isidenge; sakuba sithe safundiswa isilumko, samkela ukwazi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 12, 'Ilungisa liwazi ngobulumko indlu yongendawo; kodwa uThixo uyabatshabalalisa abangendawo ngenxa yobungendawo babo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 13, 'Ovingca iindlebe zakhe ekukhaleni kwesisweli, Naye uya kubiza, angaviwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 14, 'Isipho entsithelweni sisusa umsindo; Umvuzo esifubeni ususa umsindo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 15, 'Kuluvuyo kwilungisa ukwenza okulungileyo; Ke abenzi bobubi baya kutshabalala.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 16, 'Umntu ondwendwayo emendweni wokuqonda uya kuhlala esikhungwini sabafileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 17, 'Othanda iziyolo uya kuba lihlwempu; Othanda iwayini neoli akabi sisityebi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 18, 'Ongendawo uya kuba yintlawulelo yelungisa, nalowo unxaxhayo abe yintlawulelo yelungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 19, 'Kulungile ukuhlala entlango, Kunokuhlala nomfazi onengxabano neengqumbo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 20, 'Kukho ubuncwane obunqwenelekayo neoli endlwini yesilumko; ke sona isidenge siyayonakalisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 21, 'Ophuthuma ubulungisa nenceba ubona ubomi nokusesikweni nozuko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 22, 'Isilumko siyenyuka siye emzini wamagorha, siyitshabalalise inqaba esikholose ngayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 23, 'Obambe umlomo wakhe nolwimi lwakhe Ugcina umphefumlo wakhe ebubini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 24, 'Igama lakhe lingumgxeki, umkhukhumali, Owenza ngokukhukhumala.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 25, 'Icebo lomntu liyambulala; ngokuba izandla zakhe azivumi ukusebenza.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 26, 'Unqwenela imini yonke, kodwa ilungisa aliniki, lingavimbi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 27, 'Umbingelelo wabangendawo lisikizi; yimalini ayizisa ngengqondo engendawo?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 28, 'Ingqina elixokayo liyatshabalala; Ke yena ovayo usoloko ethetha.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 29, 'Indoda engendawo iyingwanyalala ubuso, Ke lona ilungisa liyayilungisa indlela yalo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 30, 'Akukho bulumko nakuqonda okanye njongo nxamnye noYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 21, 31, 'Ihashe lilungiselwe imini yokulwa, kodwa usindiso luvela kuYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 1, 'Igama elilungileyo lingaphezulu kobutyebi obuninzi; Isimilo esilungileyo silunge ngaphezu kwesilivere negolide.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 2, 'Izityebi namahlwempu bayahlangana: uYehova nguMdali wazo zonke izinto.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 3, 'Umntu osisilumko, xa angaboni nto imbi, azifihle; ke zona izinyabi ziya kugqitha kuyo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 4, 'Ukuthobeka nokoyika uYehova bubutyebi, nozuko, nobomi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 5, 'Ameva nezirhintyelo endleleni yabangendawo; Lowo uwugcinayo kuzo umphefumlo wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 6, 'Mfundise umntwana indlela ethe tye, Nokuba athe wamkhulu, akasayi kumka kuyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 7, 'Isityebi siya kuwalawula amahlwempu; Nobolekayo ngumkhonzi endodeni embolekayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 8, 'Ohlwayela ubugqwetha, wovuna into engeyako; nomsimelelo wokuvutha komsindo wakhe wotshabalala.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 9, 'Oliso libanzi uya kusikelelwa; ngokuba unika amahlwempu isonka sakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 10, 'Mgxothe umgxeki, kusuke ingxabano; ewe, iingxabano nonyeliso ziya kuphela.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 11, 'Othanda intliziyo ehlambulukileyo, Ngenxa yenceba yomlomo wakhe, ukumkani ungumhlobo wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 12, 'Amehlo kaYehova agcina ukwazi, Uyalitshabalalisa ilizwi labangendawo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 13, 'Wathi uSebhodu, Kukho ingonyama phandle, ndiya kubulawa ebaleni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 14, 'Liqula elinzulu umlomo wabafazi bolunye uhlanga; omgibayo uYehova uya kuwela kuyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 15, 'Ukumatha kubotshiwe entliziyweni yomntwana; Ke yona intonga yesohlwayo iya kumsusa kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 16, 'Ocudisa isisweli, ukuba andise ubutyebi baso; Nowabela isityebi, uya kuswela yena.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 17, 'Thoba indlebe yakho, uve amazwi ezilumko, Uyibhekise intliziyo yakho ekwazini kwam.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 18, 'Ngokuba kumnandi, xa uthe wawagcina embilinini; ziya kuwufanela umlomo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 19, 'Ukuze ithemba lakho likuYehova, ndikwazisile namhlanje.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 20, 'Andinibhalelanga na izinto ezimangalisayo, ezinamacebo nokwazi?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 21, 'Ndiya kwazisa inyaniso yamazwi enyaniso; Ukuba uphendule amazwi enyaniso, ubaphendule abo bakuthumayo?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 22, 'Musa ukusihlutha isisweli, ngokuba lilihlwempu; uze ungawacinezeli amahlwempu emnyango.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 23, 'Ngenxa yokuba uYehova uya kubamela aze awutshabalalise umphefumlo wabo baphangayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 24, 'Musani ukunxulumana nomntu onomsindo; kwaye ungahambi nomntu onomsindo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 25, 'Hleze ungazifundi iindlela zayo, Uwufumanele umgibe umphefumlo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 26, 'Musa ukuba phakathi kwabaqhwabayo, Ozibambisayo ngezinto ezibolekiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 27, 'Ukuba uthe akwaba nanto yakuhlawula, Yini na ukuba athabathe ukhuko lwakho phantsi kwakho?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 28, 'Musa ukuwususa umda omdala, abawumisayo ooyihlo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 22, 29, 'Uyambona na umntu okhutheleyo? uya kuma phambi kookumkani; akanakuma phambi kongendawo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 1, 'Xa uthe wahlala phantsi, ukuba udle nomlawuli, zigqale izinto eziphambi kwakho;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 2, 'Ukuba unqwenela ukutya, beka isitshetshe emqaleni wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 3, 'Musa ukuzinqwenela izidlo zakhe ezinencasa, Kukudla kwenkohliso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 4, 'Musani ukuzisebenzela ukuba sisityebi; bushiye ngasemva ubulumko bakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 5, 'Ngaba uyathanda ukubeka amehlo akho kwindawo ephosakeleyo? Kuba okunene ubutyebi benza amaphiko; ziphaphazela njengexhalanga esibhakabhakeni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 6, 'Musa ukudla isonka seliso elibi, Ungazinqweneli izidlo zakhe ezinencasa;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 7, 'Ngokokuba elinganisele entliziyweni yakhe, unjengoko athi kuwe, Yidla, sela; kodwa intliziyo yakhe ayikho kuwe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 8, 'Uya kuyilahla loo nto uyityileyo, ulahlekelwe namazwi akho amnandi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 9, 'Musa ukuthetha ezindlebeni zesinyabi, Ngokuba siya kugxeka ubulumko bamazwi akho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 10, 'Musa ukuwususa umda omdala; kwaye aliyi kungena entsimini yeenkedama.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 11, 'Ngokuba womelele umsindisi wabo; wobambana nawe yena.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 12, 'Yinikele intliziyo yakho eluqeqeshweni, Ubephulaphule amazwi okwazi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 13, 'Musa ukuluyeka uqeqesho lomntwana, kuba xa uthe wambetha ngentonga akayi kufa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 14, 'Mbethe ngentonga, uze uwusindise umphefumlo wakhe kwelabafileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 15, 'Nyana wam, ukuba ithe yalumka intliziyo yakho, Yovuya intliziyo yam, ewe eyam.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 16, 'Ewe, ziya kuvuya izintso zam xa imilebe yakho ithetha inyaniso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 17, 'Intliziyo yakho mayingabamoneli aboni; Ke yoyika uYehova imini yonke.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 18, 'Ngokuba inene, kukho isiphelo; kwaye ithemba lakho aliyi kutshabalala.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 19, 'Yiva, nyana wam, ulumke, Uyinyathelise intliziyo yakho ithi gca endleleni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 20, 'Musa ukuba phantsi kwabasela iwayini; phakathi kwabadla inyama bengxola.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 21, 'Kuba isela-wayini nedla-kudla liya kuba lihlwempu;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 22, 'Mphulaphule uyihlo, lowo wakuzalayo, Ungamdeli unyoko akuba mkhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 23, 'Thenga inyaniso, ungathengisi ngayo; nobulumko, nengqeqesho, nokuqonda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 24, 'Uyise olilungisa uba nemihlali kakhulu; Ozala umntwana osisilumko unoyolo ngenxa yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 25, 'Woba noyolo uyihlo nonyoko, Agcobe lowo wakuzalayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 26, 'Ndinike intliziyo yakho, nyana wam, Amehlo akho azibone iindlela zam.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 27, 'Kuba sisihogo esinzulu ihenyukazi; kwaye omnye umfazi ngumngxuma omxinwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 28, 'Ulalela njengexhoba, andise abangendawo ebantwini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 29, 'Ngubani onelishwa? ngubani uxolo? Ngubani na ophikayo, uthetha ngubani na? Ngubani na onamanxeba ngelize? ngubani onamehlo abomvu?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 30, 'Bazeka kade ukusela iwayini; abahamba befuna iwayini ephithikeziweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 31, 'Musa ukuyijonga iwayini, xa ibomvu, nokuba ibengezela eglasini, xa inyibilika.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 32, 'Ekugqibeleni iluma njengenyoka, iluma njengonomadudwane.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 33, 'Amehlo akho aya kubabona abafazi beentlanga, intliziyo yakho ithethe okubi;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 34, 'Ewe, uya kuba njengolele esazulwini solwandle, nanjengolele esanekweni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 23, 35, 'Uya kuthi, Bandibetha, andizange ndigule; Bandibetha, andakuva; Ndizovuka nini ndiphinde ndiyijonge?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 1, 'Musa ukubamonela abantu ababi, ungakunqweneli ukuba uhlale nabo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 2, 'Kuba intliziyo yabo ifunda ukubola, nemilebe yabo ithetha kakubi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 3, 'Indlu yona yakhiwe ngobulumko; izinziswe ngengqondo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 4, 'Ngokwazi kuzaliswa amaqonga bubutyebi obunqwenelekayo nobunqwenelekayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 5, 'Indoda elumkileyo iyomelela; ewe, umntu onolwazi wongeza amandla.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 6, 'Kuba uya kulwa idabi lakho unecebo lobulumko, yaye xa kukho abacebisi abaninzi kukho usindiso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 7, 'Ubulumko bungaphezu kwesidenge, Abuwuvuli umlomo wabo emnyango.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 8, 'Lowo uceba ukwenza ububi kuya kuthiwa ngongendawo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 9, 'Iingcinga zobudenge sisono; Lisikizi ebantwini umgxeki.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 10, 'Ukuba uthe watyhafa ngemini yembandezelo, Mancinane amandla akho;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 11, 'Ukuba nikuhilile ukubakhusela abasiwa ekufeni, nababuganga bokubulawa;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 12, 'Ukuba uthe, Yabona, besingakwazi oko; Ngaba uyayiqwalasela into ecingwa yintliziyo? kanti lowo uwugcinayo umphefumlo wakho akazi? Akayi kumbuyekeza elowo ngokwemisebenzi yakhe na?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 13, 'Yidla ubusi, nyana wam, kuba bulungile; nenqatha lobusi, enencasa ekhuhlangubeni lakho;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 14, 'Ukwazi ubulumko kuya kuba njalo emphefumlweni wakho;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 15, 'Musa ukulilinda ikhaya lamalungisa, wena ungendawo; indawo yakhe yokuphumla ayonakaliswanga.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 16, 'Kuba ilungisa liwa kasixhenxe lize livuke, kodwa abangendawo baya kuwela ebubini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 17, 'Musa ukuvuya ekuweni kotshaba lwakho, Ungagcobi ekukhubekeni kwentliziyo yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 18, 'Ngamana uYehova angakuboni oko, kungabi ngokuthanda kwakhe, yaye uya kuwususa umsindo wakhe kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 19, 'Musa ukuxhalela ububi, ungamoneli ongendawo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 20, 'Ngokuba akukho mvuzo kongendawo; Isibane sabangendawo siya kucinywa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 21, 'Nyana wam, moyike uYehova nokumkani, ungangeneleli kwabatshintshileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 22, 'Kuba iya kubonakala kwangoko intlekele yabo; Ngubani na olaziyo isiphelo sabo bobabini?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 23, 'Nazo ezo zinto zezezilumko. Ukuhlonela umntu ekugwebeni akulungile.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 24, 'Othi kongendawo, Ulilungisa wena; Ziya kumqalekisa iintlanga, zimthiye iintlanga;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 25, 'Banoyolo abo bamohlwayayo, Kubo banoyolo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 26, 'Lowo uphendulayo uya kwanga umlomo wakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 27, 'Lilungise ishishini lakho khona, ube ulungile entsimini; wandule ukwakha indlu yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 28, 'Musa ukuba lingqina ngommelwane wakho ngaphandle kwesizathu; kwaye musani ukukhohliswa zizipaji zenu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 29, 'Musa ukuthi, Njengoko enze ngako kum, ndiya kwenjenjalo nam kuye; ndiya kumbuyisela umntu ngokwemisebenzi yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 30, 'Ndacanda ezweni lobukhoboka, nasesidiliyeni sesilumko;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 31, 'Yabona, luzele yimithana enameva ngaphambili, ludilikile udonga lwamatye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 32, 'Ndabona, ndacinga kakuhle; Ndayibona ndaza ndafumana umyalelo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 33, 'Ukulala kancinane, ukozela kancinane, nokusonga iingalo zomntu kancinane, alale.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 24, 34, 'Ngoko ubuhlwempu bakho bokuza njengondwendwe; Nentswelo yakho njengomntu oxhobileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 1, 'Nale yimizekeliso kaSolomon, awayibhalayo amadoda kaHezekiya, ukumkani wakwaYuda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 2, 'Kuluzuko kuThixo ukufihla into; Ke isidima sokumkani ukuyigocagoca loo nto.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 3, 'Izulu liphakamile, nomhlaba unzulu, nentliziyo yookumkani ayinakulinganiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 4, 'Lisuse igwebu lesilivere, kuphume isitya somhlambululi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 5, 'Shenxisa ongendawo kukumkani, Yozinza itrone yakhe ngobulungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 6, 'Uze ungaveli phambi kokumkani, ungemi endaweni yamadoda amakhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 7, 'Kuba kulungile ukuthi, Nyuka apha; Kunokuba uzithobe phambi kwenkosi ebone amehlo akho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 8, 'Musa ukungxamela ingxabano, hleze ukwazi oko uya kukwenza ekupheleni kwako, ukuba uthe wakudanisa ummelwane wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 9, 'Thetha nommelwane wakho; imfihlakalo uze ungayityhili komnye;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 10, 'ukuze lowo uvayo anganihlazisi, lingasuswa ihlazo lakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 11, 'Ziilamuni zegolide kwizitya zesilivere.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 12, 'Isohlwayo esilumkileyo sikwindlebe evayo, Lijikazi legolide, nesidanga segolide engcwengiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 13, 'Umthunywa othembekileyo othunyelwayo ufana nekhephu ngekhephu ngexesha lokuvuna, kuba iyabaphumza umoya yabaniniyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 14, 'Oqhayisa ngesipho sobuxoki ufana namafu nomoya ongenamvula.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 15, 'Ngokuzeka kade umsindo, ukumkani uya koyiseka, Nolwimi oluthambileyo lwaphula amathambo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 16, 'Ufumene ubusi? yidla, uhluthe, ungahluthi, uhlanze;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 17, 'Lususe unyawo lwakho endlwini yommelwane wakho; ukuze angadinwa nguwe aze akucaphukele kakhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 18, 'Indoda engqina ubuxoki ngommelwane wayo iyisambatho nekrele notolo olubukhali.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 19, 'Ukukholosa ngenginingini ngexesha lembandezelo Lizinyo elaphukileyo nomlenze owaphukileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 20, 'Lowo wenzakalisa intliziyo ufana nomntu okhulula ingubo yakhe xa kubanda, nanjengewayini ephithikezwa ngetyuwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 21, 'Ukuba okuthiyileyo uthe walamba, mphe ukudla adle; ukuba lunxaniwe, luseze amanzi;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 22, 'Kuba ufumba wena amalahle omlilo phezu kwentloko yakhe, yaye uYehova wokuvuza.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 23, 'Umoya ovela ngasentla uvelisa isiphango;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 24, 'Kulungile ukuhlala elungqamekweni oluphezu kophahla, Kunokuhlala nomfazi onentsimbi ndlwini-nye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 25, 'Ngamanzi abandayo emphefumlweni onxaniweyo Iindaba ezilungileyo, ezivela ezweni elikude.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 26, 'Liqula elibhukuqekileyo, nomthombo owonakeleyo, olilungisa eliwa phambi kongendawo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 27, 'Ukudla ubusi obuninzi akulungile; ke ngoko, akuhlonipheki ukuba abantu bavavanye isidima sabo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 25, 28, 'Ufana nesixeko esiqhekeziweyo, esingamabhodlo, ongawunqandiyo umoya wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 1, 'Njengekhephu ehlotyeni, njengemvula ngexa lokuvuna, Ayisifanele isidenge uzuko.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 2, 'Njengentaka ebhadulayo, nanjengesikhukukazi esiphaphazelayo, ukuqalekisa akuyi kuza ngelize;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 3, 'Isiniya ngowehashe, umkhala ngowe-esile, umsimelelo ngowomhlana wesidenge.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 4, 'Musa ukusiphendula isidenge ngokobudenge baso, Hleze ufane naso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 5, 'Siphendule isidenge ngobudenge baso, Hleze sibe sisilumko kwawaso amehlo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 6, 'Othumela ilizwi njengegeza, Uzinqumla iinyawo, usela ububi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 7, 'Imilenze yesiqhwala ayanelanga; Umzekeliso onjalo emlonyeni wesidenge.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 8, 'Obopha ilitye kwinkwitshi Ufana nohlonela isidenge.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 9, 'Njengoko kunyuka uviko esandleni senxila, unjalo umzekeliso emlonyeni wesinyabi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 10, 'uThixo omkhulu owenza zonke izinto uyabavuza abaziziyatha nabakreqi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 11, 'Njengenja ibuyela emhlanzweni wayo, isidenge sibuyela emanyathelweni aso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 12, 'Ngaba uyambona na umntu osisilumko? kukho ithemba ngesinyabi kunayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 13, 'uSebhodo uthi, Kukho ingonyama endleleni; ingonyama egqumayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 14, 'Njengocango lujikajika kwiihenjisi zalo, Linjalo ivila esililini salo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 15, 'Ongendawo ufaka isandla sakhe esifubeni sakhe; yamenza intloni ukuyibuyisela emlonyeni kwakhona.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 16, 'Ikhoboka lizicingela ukuba lilumke kunamadoda asixhenxe akwaziyo ukupha.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 17, 'Lowo ke ugxuphuleka entweni ezingeyakhe, ufana nalowo wandibamba ngeendlebe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 18, 'Njengendoda ephambeneyo ephosa iibhombu, iintolo nokufa,', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 19, 'Kukwanjalo ke nakulowo ulahlekisa ummelwane wakhe, athi, Andenza umthambo na?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 20, 'Apho kungekho nkuni, uyafa umlilo; Ngoko ke apho kungekho mnyelisi, ziyaphela izibetho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 21, 'Njengamalahle avuthayo, iinkuni zomlilo; unjalo ke nangomntu othanda ukuthuba.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 22, 'Amazwi entlebi anjengamanxeba, ahla aye embilinini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 23, 'Liziko elivutha umlilo, nentliziyo enobubi, liziko elilethwe ngesilivere.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 24, 'Lowo uthiyayo ngomlomo wakhe, ucebe entliziyweni yakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 25, 'Xa ethetha kakuhle, uze ungakholwa nguye, kuba kukho amasikizi asixhenxe entliziyweni yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 26, 'Omthiyayo ugutyungelwe ngenkohliso, ububi bakhe buya kwaziwa kamsinya kulo lonke ibandla.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 27, 'Ombe umngxuma uya kweyela kuwo; lowo uliqengqile ilitye, liya kubuyela kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 26, 28, 'Ulwimi oluxokayo luyabathiya abatshutshiswa lulo; kwaye loo mlomo uyonakalisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 1, 'Musa ukuqhayisa ngengomso; ngokuba ungayazi ukuba iya kuthini na loo mini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 2, 'Mawudunyiswe ngomnye, ingabi ngumlomo wakho; umntu wasemzini, hayi imilebe yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 3, 'Ilitye elinzima nentlabathi enzima; Ke yona ingqumbo yesimathane inobubi kunezo zibini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 4, 'Umsindo sisijorha, umsindo sisijorha; nekhwele, ngubani na onokuma phambi kwalo?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 5, 'Kulungile ukohlwaywa ekuhleni ngaphezu kothando olufihlakeleyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 6, 'Amanxeba omhlobo athembekile; kodwa yinkohliso ukwanga kotshaba.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 7, 'Ozele ngumoya uyithiyile ingxondorha; Kumphefumlo olambileyo, yonke into ekrakra imnandi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 8, 'Umntu ondwendwayo endaweni yakhe ufana nentaka ephekuziweyo endlwaneni yayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 9, 'Ioli nentlaka emhlophe zenza intliziyo ibe nemihlali;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 10, 'Musa ukumfulathela umhlobo wakho nomhlobo kayihlo; uze ungangeni endlwini yomzalwana wakho ngemini yeshwangusha lakho; ngokuba ummelwane wakho okufuphi ulungile kunomzalwana wakho okude.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 11, 'Yiba nobulumko, nyana wam, uyivuyise intliziyo yam, Ukuze ndimphendule ngezwi ondingcikivayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 12, 'Isilumko sibona ububi, sibufihle; kwaye abo bangantsonkothanga baya phambili kwaye bayohlwaywa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 13, 'Thabatha ingubo yolunye uhlanga, uthabathe isibambiso kuye ngenxa yomfazi wolunye uhlanga.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 14, 'Othe wasikelela ummelwane wakhe ngezwi elikhulu, wavuka kwakusasa, koba sisishwabulo kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 15, 'Lithontsi elizothileyo ngemini yemvula, Nomfazi onengxabano mnye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 16, 'Ufihla umoya nokutyeba kwesandla sakhe sokunene.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 17, 'Isinyithi silola isinyithi; indoda ilola ubuso bowayo ngokunjalo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 18, 'Lowo uwugcina umkhiwane uya kutya isiqhamo sawo; ngokunjalo ke othembele kukumkani uya kuzukiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 19, 'Njengobuso emanzini buye bajongana nobuso, injalo intliziyo yomntu emntwini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 20, 'Imbuqo nentshabalalo ayiyi kuzala; ngokunjalo akahluthi amehlo omntu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 21, 'Njengembiza yesilivere, iziko legolide; umntu onjalo ukumdumisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 22, 'Nokuba uthe wangcwatywa ngotolo, isinyabi wasingcwaba ngotolo ngotolo, Ukumatha kwaso abuyi kumka.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 23, 'Yilumkele ubume bomhlambi wakho, Waluse umhlambi wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 24, 'Emva kokuba bonke ubutyebi abubo banaphakade, kwaye ingaba isithsaba siya kubakho ukusuka kwesinye isizukulwana kuye kwesinye?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 25, 'Kuvela umtya, kubonakale utyani obuthambileyo, buhlanganiswe utyani ezintabeni;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 26, 'Iimvana yingubo yakho, lixabiso lentsimi iinkunzi zeebhokhwe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 27, 27, 'Wokwanela ubisi lwebhokhwe ekutyeni kwakho, nasekudleni kwendlu yakho, nasekunyamekeleni abakhonzazana bakho;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 1, 'Abangendawo babaleka ababasukelayo; Ke wona amalungisa akholosa njengengonyama.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 2, 'Baninzi abathetheli bakho, ngenxa yobugwenxa belizwe;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 3, 'Umfo oyintloko ekutshutshiseni isisweli Unjengemvula etshayelayo, ingashiyi kudla.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 4, 'Abatyekayo emthethweni badumisa abangendawo; Ke abawugcinayo umyalelo bayazixhokonxa ngabo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 5, 'Abangendawo abanangqondo yodwa; Ke bona abamquqelayo uYehova baqonda izinto zonke.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 6, 'Lilungile ihlwempu elihamba ngobulungisa balo, Ngaphezu kongendawo ongendawo, nokuba esisityebi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 7, 'Obamba umyalelo ngunyana onengqondo; Ke yena ohamba namahenyukazi uhlazisa uyise.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 8, 'Owongeza ubutyebi bakhe ngorhwebo, ngogonyamelo, Ubuthela obabala abaziintsizana.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 9, 'Osusa indlebe yakhe ekuwuthobeleni umyalelo, nomthandazo wakhe ulisikizi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 10, 'Olahlekisa ilungisa ngendlela embi, uya kweyela esihogweni sakhe; ke wona amalungisa aya kukudla ilifa okulungileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 11, 'Isityebi siziba sisilumko; Ke zona izisweli ezinengqondo ziyamgocagoca.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 12, 'Ekudlamkeni kwamalungisa kwanda uzuko; kodwa xa kuthe kwenyuka ububi, ubani azimele.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 13, 'Ocamagushela izono zakhe akayi kuba nampumelelo; kodwa othe wayixela, wayijika, wosinda.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 14, 'Hayi, uyolo lomntu ohlala enkwantya; Ke yena ontliziyo ilukhuni weyela ebubini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 15, 'Njengengonyama egqumayo, nebhere ejingayo; Unjalo umlawuli ongendawo kwizisweli.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 16, 'Inganga eliswele ukuqonda, linokucudisa okuninzi; Ke yena othiya ubutyebi, uya kongeza imihla.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 17, 'Umntu othe wagonyamela ngegazi lakhe, abalekele emhadini; makungabikho bani umnqandayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 18, 'Ohamba ngobulungisa uya kusindiswa; Ke ongendawo uyakhubeka ngeendlela zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 19, 'Osebenza amasimi akhe woba nentabalala;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 20, 'Umntu onyanisekileyo uneentsikelelo ezininzi; Ke yena ongxamayo ukuba sisityebi, akabi msulwa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 21, 'Ukuhlonela umntu akulunganga, kuba umntu wona ngenxa yeqhekeza lesonka.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 22, 'Indoda eliso libi ikhawulezela ukutyeba; Akacingi ukuba ukuswela kuya kuyifikela.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 23, 'Omohlwayayo wothi kamva afumane inceba, Ngaphezu koncoma ngolwimi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 24, 'Ophanga uyise nokuba ngunina, athi, Asinto imbi leyo; ifana neqabane lesikrelemnqa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 25, 'Okhukhumeleyo uxhaya ihlazo; Ke yena okholose ngoYehova uyatyetyiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 26, 'Okholose ngentliziyo yakhe usisidenge; ke yena ohamba ngengqiqo uya kusindiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 27, 'Opha ihlwempu akasweli; Ke yena ofihla amehlo akhe uneengqalekiso ezininzi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 28, 28, 'Ekuphakameni kwabangendawo bayasithela abantu; kodwa xa etshabalala ayanda amalungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 1, 'Ohlala eyenze lukhuni intamo yakhe ekhalinyelwa, Uya kutshabalala kwaoko, kungabikho kuphiliswa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 2, 'Ekulawuleni kwelungisa banoyolo; Kodwa xa umntu okhohlakeleyo elawula, abantu bayakhala.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 3, 'Othanda ubulumko uvuyisa uyise; Ke yena osebenza namahenyukazi uya kuchitha ubutyebi bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 4, 'iNkosi iliseka ihlabathi ngomgwebo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 5, 'Umntu olahlekisa ilizwe lakhe uthiyela iinyawo zakhe ngomnatha.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 6, 'Kukho isirhintyelo elukreqweni lwabangendawo; Ke wona amalungisa aya kuvuya avuye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 7, 'Ilungisa liyalazi ityala lesisweli; ke yena ongendawo akaliqondi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 8, 'Iingxilimbela ziphemba umzi ngomgibe; Ke zona izilumko ziyawudambisa umsindo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 9, 'Saxabana isilumko nesiyatha, Socaphuka, sihleka, kungabikho kuthozama.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 10, 'Amadoda amagazi ayalithiya ilungisa, Ke lona ilungisa lifuna umphefumlo walo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 11, 'Isinyabi siya kuxela bonke ubulumko baso, Ke sona isilumko sikuchaza kwaso.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 12, 'Ukuba umlawuli uphulaphula ubuxoki, bonke abakhonzi bakhe baba bubi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 13, 'Ihlwempu nesikhohlisi bayaqubisana; uYehova uyawakhanyisela amehlo abo omabini.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 14, 'Ukumkani ogweba ityala lezisweli ngenyaniso, Itrone yakhe iya kuzinza ngonaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 15, 'Intonga nesohlwayo sinika ubulumko; Ke yena umntwana oshiyiweyo udanisa unina.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 16, 'Ekwandeni kongendawo kuyanda ubutshinga, Ke wona amalungisa aya kukubona ukuwa kwabo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 17, 'Mqeqeshe unyana wakho, wokuphefumlisa; ewe, iya kuwenza wonwabe umphefumlo wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 18, 'Apho kungekho buso, bayatshabalala abantu; Hayi, uyolo lwalowo uwugcinayo umthetho!', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 19, 'Umkhonzi akanakuhlwahlwa ngamazwi, Ngokuba nokuba uyaqiqa, akaphenduli.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 20, 'Uyambona na umntu ongxamileyo ngamazwi akhe? kukho ithemba ngesinyabi kunayo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 21, 'Osiqeqeshela kwasebuncinaneni isicaka sakhe Uya kuba ngunyana wakhe ngonaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 22, 'Umntu onomsindo uxhaya; Umntu onobushushu uzele lukreqo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 23, 'Ikratshi lomntu liya kumthoba; Umphefumlo othobekileyo uyazukiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 24, 'Ozimanya nesela uthiye umphefumlo wakhe; uyasiva isiqalekiso, anganginizi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 25, 'Ukugubha ngumntu kunesirhintyelo; ke yena okholose ngoYehova uya kusindiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 26, 'Abaninzi bafuna ukuthandwa ngumlawuli; kodwa umgwebo wonke uvela kuYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 29, 27, 'Indoda enobugqwetha lisikizi kumalungisa; Ilungisa lisikizi kongendawo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 1, 'Amazwi ka-Agure unyana kaYake, asisiprofeto: Yathetha indoda leyo kuItiyeli, noItiyeli, noUkali,', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 2, 'Kuba ndisisijorha, andiqondi;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 3, 'Andifundanga bulumko, Ukuba andimazi oyiNgcwele oyiNgcwele.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 4, 'Ngubani na owenyuka waya emazulwini okanye wehla? ngubani na owahlanganisa umoya ngamanqindi? Ngubani na osongele amanzi engutyeni? Ngubani na otywine zonke iziphelo zehlabathi? Lingubani na igama lakhe, lingubani na igama lonyana wakhe, ukuba uyalazi?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 5, 'Onke amazwi kaThixo anyulu, Ndiyingweletshetshe kwabazimela ngaye.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 6, 'Musa ukongeza emazwini akhe, Hleze wohlwaywe, ufunyanwe ulixoki.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 7, 'Ndafuna kuwe izinto ezimbini; musani ukukhanyela kum, andikafi;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 8, 'Shenxisa kum inkohlakalo nenkohliso; musa ukundinika ubutyebi, nokuba bububutyebi; ndidlise ukudla okundigcina ndiphaphile;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 9, 'Hleze ndihluthe, ndikhanyele, ndithi, Ngubani na uYehova? ukuze ndingabi lihlwempu, ndibe, ndifumane igama loThixo wam.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 10, 'Musa ukusigwebela isicaka enkosini yaso, Hleze usitshabhise, ube netyala.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 11, 'Kukho isizukulwana esitshabhisa uyise, Singamsikeleli unina;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 12, 'Kukho isizukulwana esibonakala sicocekile, kanti asikahlambululi ukungcola kwaso;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 13, 'Kukho isizukulwana, hayi, ukuphakama kwamehlo aso! ephakamise amashiya abo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 14, 'Kukho isizwe esimazinyo angamakrele, esimazinyo aziintshetshe, Zokudla iintsizana zehlabathi, namahlwempu phakathi kwabantu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 15, 'Umkhweli wehashe uneentombi ezimbini ezidanduluka zisithi: “Siphe! Zintathu izinto ezinganeliyo, zine ezingatshoyo ukuthi, Kwanele;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 16, 'Ingcwaba; nesizalo esingazaliyo; umhlaba ongenamanzi; nomlilo ongatshoyo ukuthi: Kwanele!', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 17, 'Iliso eligculela uyise, elidela ukuva unina, liya kulihlutha amahlungulu asentlanjeni, alidle amaxhalanga.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 18, 'Kukho izinto ezintathu ezibalulekileyo kum, ezine endingazaziyo:', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 19, 'Ngumendo wokhozi ezulwini; indlela yenyoka eweni; umjelo ophakathi elwandle; nendlela yomfo nomkhonzazana.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 20, 'Injalo indlela yehenyukazi; uyadla, asule umlomo wakhe, athi, Andenzanga bubi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 21, 'Kukho izinto ezintathu ezothusayo emhlabeni, ongenakukwazi ukuzithwala:', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 22, 'Kuba umkhonzi akanakuba ngukumkani; nesidenge asihluthi;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 23, 'Ngaphantsi komfazi olisikizi, xa athe wenda; nomkhonzazana oza kuba yindlalifa yenkosikazi yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 24, 'Kukho izinto ezine ezingenamandla ehlabathini, kambe ke zilumkile;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 25, 'Iimbovane luhlanga oluthambileyo, Isuka ilungise ukudla kwayo ehlotyeni;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 26, 'Iimbila zimbalwa, kodwa izindlu zabo zakhela emaweni;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 27, 'Iinkumbi azinakumkani, ziphela zingamaqela ngamaqela;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 28, 'Icilitshe libamba izandla zalo, Kanti lisemabhotweni ookumkani.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 29, 'Kukho izinto ezintathu ezihamba kakuhle, ewe, zine zihamba kakuhle:', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 30, 'Ingonyama le inamandla phakathi kwezilwanyana, ayijiki mntwini;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 31, 'Ingwenya emnyama; kunye nomntwana; nokumkani ekungekho bani unokuma phambi kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 32, 'Ukuba uthe wenza ngobudenge ngokuziphakamisa, nokuba uthe wakhumbula ububi, beka isandla emlonyeni.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 30, 33, 'Kuba ukucofa ubisi kuvelisa amasi, Ukucofa impumlo kuvelisa igazi;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 1, 'Amazwi kakumkani uLemuweli, awamqeqesha ngawo unina.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 2, 'Yintoni, nyana wam? Yini na, nyana wesizalo sam? kuthini na, emva kwesibhambathiso sam?', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 3, 'Amandla akho musa ukuwanika amankazana, Iindlela zakho uzinike ookumkani.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 4, 'Asiyindawo yokumkani, Lemuweli, akubafanelanga ookumkani ukusela iwayini; esi siselo sinxilisayo sezabathetheli.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 5, 'Ukuze bangaseli, bawulibale umyalelo, basijike isigwebo salo lonke ihlwempu;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 6, 'Isiselo esinxilisayo sinikeni otshabalalayo;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 7, 'Makasele, abulibale ubuhlwempu bakhe, Angabi sacinga ngokubandezeleka kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 8, 'Wuvule umlomo wakho kulowo ungenakuthetha, Ngenxa yabo bonke abo bamiselwe intshabalalo.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 9, 'Vula umlomo wakho, ugwebe ngobulungisa, Ukhusele usizana nolihlwempu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 10, 'Ngubani na ongamfumanayo umfazi olungileyo? Kuba ixabiso lakhe lingaphezulu leeperile.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 11, 'Ikholose ngaye intliziyo yendoda yakhe, ukuze angaphangi;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 12, 'Uyiphatha kakuhle, kungabi kakubi, yonke imihla yobomi bakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 13, 'Ufuna uboya begusha nelinen ecikizekileyo, Asebenze ngokuqhutywa yintliziyo ngezandla zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 14, 'Unjengeenqanawa zabarhwebi; uya kuthabatha kude ukudla kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 15, 'Uvuka ekuseni, ayinike ukudla indlu yakhe nabakhonzazana bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 16, 'Uyalikhangela ilizwe, alithenge; ngeziqhamo zezandla zakhe utyala isidiliya.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 17, 'Ubhinqa amandla esinqeni sakhe, Womeleza izandla zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 18, 'Uyawubona umsebenzi wakhe ulungile; Isibane sakhe asicimi ebusuku.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 19, 'Ubeka izandla zakhe phezu kwentonga yokusonta, nezandla zakhe zibambe ihagu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 20, 'Isandla sakhe usolulela kwihlwempu; Ewe, izandla zakhe uzolulela kumahlwempu.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 21, 'Ikhephu akaboyiki, ngenxa yabasendlwini yakhe, kuba elowo endlwini yakhe uvathe iingubo ezibomvu;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 22, 'Uzenzela ezakhe iingubo ngengubo; iimpahla zakhe ziyisilika nezimfusa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 23, 'Iyaziwa indoda yakhe emasangweni, ngokuba ihleli namadoda amakhulu elizwe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 24, 'Wenza ilinen ecikizekileyo, athengise ngayo; amabhanti uwanike umthengisi.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 25, 'Ngamandla nozuko ziingubo zakhe; kwaye uya kunandipha ikamva.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 26, 'Umlomo wakhe uwuvula ngobulumko; Umyalelo wenceba uselulwimini lwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 27, 'Unikela ingqalelo ekushukumeni kwabasendlwini yakhe, yaye akasidli isonka sevila.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 28, 'Bayasuka oonyana bakhe, bathi unoyolo; nendoda yakhe, imdumise;', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 29, 'Zininzi iintombi ezenza kakuhle, kodwa wena uzidlule zonke.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 30, 'Ubukumkani buyakhohlisa, ubuhle bungamampunge; kodwa ngumfazi owoyika uYehova oya kudunyiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(24, 31, 31, 'Mnikeni kwiziqhamo zezandla zakhe; zimdumise emasangweni omzi izenzo zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 1, 'Amazwi omprofeti, unyana kaDavide, ukumkani waseYerusalem.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 2, 'Amampunge awo amampunge, itsho iNtshumayeli, amampunge awo amampunge; yonke into ingamampunge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 3, 'Unalungelo lini umntu emigudwini yakhe yonke, ayenzayo phantsi kwelanga?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 4, 'Kumka esinye isizukulwana, kuza esinye isizukulwana, kodwa elimiweyo limi ngonaphakade.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 5, 'Ilanga liyaphuma kwakhona, ilanga litshona lize liphikele kwindawo yalo apho liphume khona.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 6, 'Umoya uya ezantsi, ubhekise entla; isahexa, yaye umoya ubuya ngokwemijikelo yawo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 7, 'Yonke imilambo iya elwandle; ukanti ulwandle belungazali; apho ivela khona imilambo, ibuyela kwalapho.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 8, 'Yonke into inomsebenzi; alihluthi iliso kukubona, nendlebe ayihluthi kukuva.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 9, 'Okwakuyikho, kuya kubakho; kuya kwenzeka ntoni na; akukho nto intsha phantsi kwelanga.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 10, 'Ukuba kukho into ekuthiwa, Yabona, intsha! phambi kwethu kwakudala.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 11, 'Izinto zokuqala azikhunjulwa; Kanjalo, abo baya kuza, abasayi kukhunjulwa nabaza emva kwabo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 12, 'Mna Mmoledi, ndandingukumkani wakwaSirayeli, Yerusalem.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 13, 'Intliziyo yam ndayinikela ukuba iphengulule yaye iphengulule ngobulumko ngayo yonke into eyenzekayo phantsi kwesibhakabhaka: lo mzamo wobuhlungu uThixo awunike oonyana babantu ukuze baqeqeshwe ngabo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 14, 'Ndizibonile ke zonke izenzo ezenziwayo phantsi kwelanga; yabona, ingamampunge neentuthumbo zomphefumlo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 15, 'Into egoso ayinakolulwa; nento engekhoyo ayinakubalwa.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 16, 'Ndathetha mna nentliziyo yam, ndathi, Yabona, ngoku ndikwimeko entle, ndingobulumko ngaphezu kwabo bonke ababephethe iYerusalem phambi kwam; nentliziyo yam ibone ubulumko nokwazi okukhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 17, 'Intliziyo yam ndayinikela ekwazini ubulumko, nasekwazini ubugeza nobuyatha;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 1, 18, 'Ngokuba ebuninzini bobulumko, kukho iintlungu ezininzi;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 1, 'Ndathi mna entliziyweni yam, Khawuze khe ndikulinge ngovuyo; Ziyolise ngoko; yabona, kwanaloo nto ingamampunge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 2, 'Ndathi ngokuhleka, Kukuphambana, nolonwabo: Wenza ntoni na?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 3, 'Bendisithi, ngentliziyo yam ukuzinikela ewayinini, kodwa ndayinikela intliziyo yam ngobulumko; yaye ndibambelele ngobudenge de ndibone oko baya kukwenza oonyana babantu phantsi kwezulu yonke imihla yobomi babo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 4, 'Ndizenzele imisebenzi emikhulu; ndazakhela izindlu; Mna ndityale izidiliya zam;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 5, 'Ndazenzela imiyezo namasimi, ndatyala kuyo imithi eneziqhamo zonke;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 6, 'Ndazenzela amaqula okunkcenkceshela imithi evelisa imithi.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 7, 'Ndazuza izicaka nezicakakazi, kwaza kwazalelwa endlwini yam; Kananjalo bendineenkomo neenkomo ezininzi ngaphezu kwabo bonke ababengaphambi kwam eYerusalem.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 8, 'Kwakhona ndaqokelela isilivere negolide nobuncwane obukhethekileyo bookumkani nobamaphondo, yaye ndineemvumi neemvumikazi nezinto ezivuyisayo zoonyana babantu, njengezixhobo zeentlobo ngeentlobo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 9, 'Ndakhula, ndanda, ndanda ngaphezu kwabo bonke ababengaphambi kwam eYerusalem; bahlala nam ubulumko bam.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 10, 'Andikuthandi konke akunqwenelayo amehlo am; andiyivimbanga intliziyo yam namnye umvuyo; ngokuba intliziyo yam yayivuya emigudwini yam yonke;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 11, 'Ndabheka mna ezenzweni zam zonke, ezazenzayo izandla zam, nomsebenzi endawenza;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 12, 'Ndajika ke mna, ndakhangela ubulumko, nobugeza, nobuyatha; Angenza ntoni na umntu oza emva kokumkani? kuninzi okwenziweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 13, 'Ndabona ukuba ubulumko bukhulu kunobudenge, njengokuba ukukhanya kubungaphezu kobumnyama.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 14, 'Amehlo esilumko asentlokweni yaso; ke sona isidenge sihamba ebumnyameni;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 15, 'Ndathi mna entliziyweni yam, Njengoko sihlelwa kuko isinyabi, kuya kuba njalo nakum; kwaye kutheni ndikrelekrele ngakumbi? Ndathi ke entliziyweni yam nalo ngamampunge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 16, 'Ngokuba akukho silumko ngaphezu kwesidenge, ukuze kukhunjulwe ngonaphakade; ngokuba oko kuza kweli phakade kuya kulibaleka. Ke yena umntu osisilumko ufa njani? ngaphezu kwesidenge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 17, 'Ngenxa yoko ndibuthiyile ubomi; ngenxa yokuba unzima kum umsebenzi owenziweyo phantsi kwelanga, ngenxa yokuba yonk’ into ililize yaye umphefumlo uyagula.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 18, 'Ndayithiya yonke imisebenzi endayenzayo phantsi kwelanga, ekubeni ndiya kuyishiya nomntu oya kubakho emva kwam.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 19, 'Waziwa ngubani na, ukuba woba sisilumko, nokuba woba sisiyatha, kusini na? Noko ke uya kulawula kuzo zonke iinzame endazifundisayo, kwaye ndenze ngobulumko phantsi kwelanga. Oku kukwabubudenge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 20, 'Ngoko ke ndaba buhlungu intliziyo yam ngenxa yemisebenzi yonke endayenzayo phantsi kwelanga.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 21, 'Ngokuba kubakho umntu omsebenzi wakhe bubulumko nokwazi nokuqiqa; ke lowo ungenzanga nto, uya kuyishiya ibe sisabelo sakhe. Kwanaloo nto ingamampunge nobubi obukhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 22, 'Kuba uzuza ntoni umntu kuko konke ukusebenza kwakhe nzima nangentlungu yentliziyo yakhe azikhathaze ngayo phantsi kwelanga?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 23, 'Ngokuba yonke imihla yakhe inobubi, nomsebenzi wakhe unzima; nasebusuku ayiphumli intliziyo yakhe. Oku kukwabubudenge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 24, 'Akukho nto ilungileyo ebantwini kunokuba badle, basele, ukuze umphefumlo wakhe ube nemihlali ngemisebenzi yakhe. Ndaphinda ndabona ukuba iphuma esandleni sikaThixo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 25, 'Ngokuba ngubani na ongadlayo ngaphezu kwam, ngubani na ongangxamelayo khona?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 2, 26, 'Ngokuba umntu olungileyo phambi kwakhe umnika ubulumko nokwazi nolonwabo; ke yena umoni umnika ubutyebi, ukuze amnike okulungileyo phambi koThixo; Kukwalilize nentuthumbo yokomoya.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 1, 'Into yonke inexesha elimisiweyo, nexesha layo phantsi kwezulu:', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 2, 'Ukuzalwa kunexesha lako, ukufa kunexesha lako; ukutyala kunexesha lako, ukuvuna okutyelweyo kunexesha lako;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 3, 'ukubulala kunexesha lako, ukuphilisa kunexesha lako; ixesha elikhoyo lokudilizwa kunye nexesha lokwakha;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 4, 'ukulila kunexesha lako, ukuhleka kunexesha lako; kukho ixesha lokwenza isijwili nexesha lokucula;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 5, 'kukho ixesha lokuchithachitha amatye, kukho nexesha lokufumba amatye; kukho ixesha lokuthandaza, nexesha lokungathandazi linexesha lako;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 6, 'ukuzuza kunexesha lako, ukulahlekelwa kunexesha lako; ixesha elikhoyo lokugcina kunye nexesha lokulahla;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 7, 'ukukrazula kunexesha lako, ukuthunga kunexesha lako; kukho ixesha lokuthi cwaka nexesha lokuthetha;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 8, 'ukuthanda kunexesha lako, ukuthiya kunexesha lako; kukho ixesha lemfazwe, kukho nexesha loxolo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 9, 'Unceda ntoni na lowo usebenza nzima?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 10, 'Ndawubona umzamo, awunike oonyana babantu uThixo, ukuba bafundise.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 11, 'Zonke izinto uzenze zantle ngexesha lazo; walibeka elimiweyo ezintliziyweni zabo, ukuze ungawazi namnye umsebenzi awawenzayo uThixo, athabathele ekuqaleni ade ase ekupheleni.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 12, 'Ndiyazi ke ukuba akukho nto ilungileyo phakathi kwabo, ingekuko ukuba umntu onoyolo, enze okulungileyo ebomini bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 13, 'Kanjalo, ukuba wonk’ ubani adle, asele, aze abone okulungileyo kuyo yonke imisebenzi yakhe, sisipho esivela kuThixo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 14, 'Ndiyazi ke ukuba yonke into aya kuyenza uThixo, yiyo eya kuba ngonaphakade; akukho nto inokuziswa kuyo kwaye akukho nto inokukhutshwa kuyo; yaye uThixo uyakwenza oko ukuze abantu bamoyike.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 15, 'Bekuyintoni na ngoku? nabo baya kubakho, bebesele bekho; kwaye uThixo uxela kwangaphambili.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 16, 'Ndabuya ndabona phantsi kwelanga indawo yokugweba, ngokuba okungendawo kukhona; nendawo yobulungisa, ukuba okungendawo kukhona.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 17, 'Ndathi mna entliziyweni yam, Nolilungisa nongendawo, uThixo uya kulithetha ityala labo; ngokuba umise ixesha layo yonke imicimbi, nazo zonke izenzo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 18, 'Ndathi mna entliziyweni yam ngemeko yoonyana babantu, ukuba uThixo unokusityhilela kubo nokuba babone ukuba bazizilwanyana zasekhaya.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 19, 'Ngokuba bayahlelwa oonyana babantu, ziyahlelwa neenkomo, sinye isihlo kubo nakuzo; njengoko kunjalo ukufa kwabo, kunjalo ukufa kwabo; ewe, mnye umoya kubo bonke; ngokokuba akukho namnye ngaphezu kwenkomo, ngokuba yonke into ingamampunge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 20, 'Bonke baya ndaweni-nye; zonke zavela eluthulini, zabuyela eluthulini zonke.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 21, 'Ngubani na owaziyo umoya woonyana babantu, ukuba uyenyuka na?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 3, 22, 'Ndaqonda ke ngoko, ukuba akukho nto ilunge ngaphezu kokuba umntu axhamle imisebenzi yakhe; ngokuba kusisabelo sakhe oko; ngokuba ngubani na oya kumzisa ukuba akubone okuya kubakho emva kwakhe?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 1, 'Ndabuya ke mna, ndabubona bonke ububi obenziwayo phantsi kwelanga; yaye kwicala labacinezeli kwakukho amandla; Ke bona bengenamthuthuzeli.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 2, 'Ndabanqula abafileyo abafileyo, ngaphezu kwabadla ubomi abasahleliyo ngoku.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 3, 'Ewe, ulunge ngakumbi kunababini abangazange babekho, abangazange bawubone umsebenzi ombi owenziwe phantsi kwelanga.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 4, 'Kananjalo ndayiqonda ke mna yonke imigudu, nayo yonke imisebenzi elungileyo, yokuba umntu abe nekhwele ngommelwane wakhe ngenxa yoko. Kwanamampunge nokusukelana nomoya.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 5, 'Isidenge sisonga izandla zaso, siyidle inyama yaso.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 6, 'Kulungile ukuzalisa sandla sinye ngokuphumla, kunokuzalisa zozibini izandla ngomsebenzi onzima onzima.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 7, 'Ndabuya mna, ndabona kungekho nto phantsi kwelanga.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 8, 'Kukho mnye, akakho owesibini; ewe, akanamntwana nabantakwabo; nangona kunjalo, yonke imizamo yakhe ayipheli; alihluthi iliso lakhe bubutyebi; Athi, Ndiya kukhonza bani na, ndiwuhluthe okulungileyo umphefumlo wam? Ikwangamampunge, ewe, yingxaki ebuhlungu.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 9, 'Kulungile ukuba babe ngababini kunokuba abe mnye; ngenxa yokuba banomvuzo ngomsebenzi wabo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 10, 'Kuba xa bathe bawa, omnye wothabatha iqabane lakhe; kodwa ngelishwa omnye akazange awe; ngokuba engenaye umphakamisa.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 11, 'Kananjalo ababini, balala ndawonye, baya kuva ukusitha; angathini na ukusitha yedwa?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 12, 'Ukuba umntu uthe wameyisa umntu, baya kumchasa ababini; nentsontelo emithathu ayikhawulezi ukuqhawuka.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 13, 'Ulungile umntwana olihlwempu, esisilumko, ngaphezu kokumkani oselekhulile esisidenge, ongasabeliyo ukucetyiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 14, 'Kuba uphuma entolongweni ukuba alawule; kanti ozalelwe ebukumkanini bakhe uba lihlwempu.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 15, 'Ndababona bonke abadla ubomi, behamba phantsi kwelanga kunye nomntwana wesibini, oya kuphuma kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 4, 16, 'Akukho kuphela kwabantu bonke, kwanabo bonke angaphambi kwabo; nabasemva kwakhe abayi kukholiswa nguye. Ewe, kwanaloo nto ingamampunge, iwuthuthumbisa umphefumlo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 1, 'Gcina unyawo lwakho xeshikweni uya endlwini kaThixo; ukuthanda ukuva ngaphezu kombingelelo wezidenge; ngenxa yokuba bengacingi ukuba benza ububi.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 2, 'Musa ukungxama ngomlomo wakho, intliziyo yakho ingaphangi ukuthetha phambi koThixo; ngokuba uThixo usemazulwini, ke wena usehlabathini; ke ngoko amazwi akho kufuneka abe mancinane.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 3, 'Ngokuba iphupha liza neendaba ezininzi; kwaye ilizwi lesidenge laziwa ngamazwi amaninzi.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 4, 'Xa uthe wafunga kuThixo, musa ukulibala ukusizalisekisa; ngokuba akakholiswa ziziyatha; hlawula isithembiso sakho.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 5, 'Kulungile ukuba ungathembisi, kunokuthembisa ungahlawuli.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 6, 'Musa ukuwuvumela umlomo wakho ukuba uyikhubekise inyama yakho; uze ungatsho phambi kwesithunywa sezulu ukuba ibiyimpazamo. Yini na ukuba uThixo abe noburhalarhume ngelizwi lakho, asonakalise isenzo sezandla zakho?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 7, 'Ngokuba kumaphupha namazwi, maninzi amazwi; kodwa yoyika uThixo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 8, 'Ukuba ubona ukucinezelwa kwehlwempu nokugqwethwa komthetho nokusesikweni kwelinye ilizwe, musa ukumangaliswa yiloo nto, kuba oyena uphakamileyo uphakamileyo kunoyena uphakamileyo, yaye ukho nophakamileyo kunabo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 9, 'Ungeniselo lwelizwe lolwabantu bonke; Ukumkani ulungiselwa amasimi.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 10, 'Othanda isilivere akaneliswa yisilivere; nokuba uthanda ubutyebi, akaphumi;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 11, 'Ekwandeni kokulungileyo, bayanda abakudlayo;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 12, 'Bumnandi ubuthongo bosebenzayo, nokuba incinane, nokuba ininzi into ayidlayo; ke bona ubutyebi besityebi abukulalisi.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 13, 'Kukho ububi obukhulu endibubonileyo phantsi kwelanga;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 14, 'obo butyebi butshabalala ngento embi; uzale unyana, kungekho nto esandleni sakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 15, 'Uya kubuya eze esizalweni sonina, ahambe njengoko weza ngako;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 16, 'Kananjalo bububi obukhulu, ukuba uya kuhamba ngeendlela zonke njengoko weza; yaye uba yintoni umphumo walowo ubetha umoya?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 17, 'Yaye yonke imihla yakhe uyidla ebumnyameni, enentlungu enkulu nomsindo ngenxa yokugula kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 18, 'Bona ke endikubonileyo: kulungile, kumnandi ukuba umntu adle, asele, abone okulungileyo kokubila kwakhe konke, akwenzayo phantsi kwelanga, yonke imihla yobomi bakhe, amnikayo uThixo bona; ngokuba kusisabelo sakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 19, 'Kananjalo wonke umntu, athe uThixo wamnika ubutyebi, wamnika negunya lokudla, adle, abone okulungileyo emisebenzini yakhe; sisipho esivela kuThixo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 5, 20, 'Ngokuba akayi kucinga kakhulu ngemihla yobomi bakhe; ngokuba uThixo emphendule ngovuyo lwentliziyo yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 6, 1, 'Kukho ububi endibubonileyo phantsi kwelanga, bukhulu phakathi kwabantu;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 6, 2, 'Umntu athe uThixo wamnika ubutyebi nozuko, ongaswele nto emphefumlweni wakhe, kuko konke asukuba enqwenela ngako, kodwa uThixo akamnikanga gunya lokuzidla; udliwa ngowasemzini; asinto, asinto sisifo esibi.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 6, 3, 'Ukuba umntu uthe wazala ikhulu labantwana, wadla ubomi iminyaka emininzi, yande imihla yeminyaka yakhe, umphefumlo wakhe awahlutha zizinto ezilungileyo, angangcwatywa; Ndithi, ukuzalwa engalindelekanga kungcono kunaye.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 6, 4, 'Kuba ingene ngelize, imka ebumnyameni, negama lakhe ligutyungelwe bubumnyama;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 6, 5, 'Ngaphezu koko, akazange alibone ilanga engazi nto; buphumla ngakumbi kunabanye.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 6, 6, 'Nokuba uthe wadla ubomi iminyaka engamawaka amabini, akaboni nto ilungileyo; azihambi ndaweni-nye zonke?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 6, 7, 'Yonke imisebenzi yomntu uyenzela umlomo wakhe; ke umnqweno wakhe awuwuzali.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 6, 8, 'Ngokuba isilumko sisigqitha ngantoni na isidenge? Liyintoni na ihlwempu, ngubani na okwaziyo ukuhamba phakathi kwabaphilileyo?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 6, 9, 'Ukubona kwamehlo kulunge ngaphezu kokuhambahamba kwenkanuko;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 6, 10, 'Sele kuthethiwe ke, yaziwa ukuba yena ungumntu;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 6, 11, 'Ekubeni kukho izinto ezininzi nje, ezongeza amampunge;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 6, 12, 'Ngokuba ngubani na owaziyo okumlungeleyo umntu ebomini, ngangenani lemihla yobomi bakhe obungamampunge, ayigqiba njengesithunzi? ngokuba ngubani na owaziyo okuya kubakho emva kwakhe phantsi kwelanga?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 1, 'Igama elilungileyo lingaphezulu nakwioli elungileyo; Umhla wokufa unjengomhla wokuzalwa komntu.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 2, 'Kulungile ukuya endlwini yobumnyama ngaphezu kokuya endlwini yemigidi; kuba kukuphela kwabantu bonke; yaye ophilayo uya kukubeka entliziyweni yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 3, 'Kulungile ukuba nosizi ngaphezu kokuhleka; ngokuba intliziyo inobuso obuthe khunubembe.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 4, 'Intliziyo yezilumko isendlwini yobumnyama; ke yona intliziyo yezidenge isendlwini yovuyo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 5, 'Kulungile ukuva ukukhalimela kwesilumko, kunokuba uve ingoma yezidenge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 6, 'Ngokuba lilizwi levaba phantsi kwembiza ukuhleka kwesidenge; kwanaloo nto ingamampunge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 7, 'Ewe, ukucudisa kugezisa isilumko; kwaye isipho siyayiphula intliziyo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 8, 'Kulungile ukugqitywa kwendawo, ngaphezu kokuqalwa kwayo;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 9, 'Musa ukukungxamela ukuqumba ngomoya wakho, ngokuba ingqumbo isesifubeni sezidenge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 10, 'Musa ukuthi, Ibiyini na ukuba imihla yokuqala ibilungile kunale? ngenxa yokuba akuceli ngengqiqo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 11, 'Bulungile ubulumko, kunye nelifa, bulungile kwabalibonayo ilanga.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 12, 'Ngokuba ubulumko buligwiba, imali iyindawo yokusabela, kodwa ingenelo yolwazi kukuba ubulumko buyabasindisa abo banabo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 13, 'Wukhangele umsebenzi kaThixo; ngokuba ngubani na onokolula into ajikileyo?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 14, 'Vuyani ngomhla wentsikelelo, niqondele imini yobubi;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 15, 'Le nto yonke ndayibona ngemihla yam engamampunge: kubakho ilungisa elitshabalalayo noko linobulungisa, kubekho ongendawo ophila ixesha elide, ngenxa yobungendawo bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 16, 'Musa ukuba lilungisa ngezinto ezininzi; musani ukuqhayisa. Kutheni uzozonakalisa?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 17, 'Musa ukuba ngongendawo ngokukhulu, ungazenzi isidenge; ungafa lingekafiki ixesha lakho?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 18, 'Kulungile ukuba uthe wabubamba; ewe, musa ukusisusa isandla sakho kuyo; ngokuba owoyika uThixo wophuma kuyo yonke.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 19, 'Ubulumko buyasiqinisa isilumko, ngaphezu kweshumi lamagorha esixekweni.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 20, 'Ngokuba akukho mntu ulilungisa ehlabathini, wenza okulungileyo, angoni.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 21, 'Kananjalo, musani ukuwanikela ingqalelo amazwi onke athethwayo; hleze umve umkhonzi wakho etshabhisa.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 22, 'Ngokuba intliziyo yakho ihlala isazi ukuba uyabatshabhisa abanye;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 23, 'Zonke ezo zinto ndizilingile ngobulumko, ndathi, Ndiya kulumka; kodwa bekude kum.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 24, 'Yintoni ekude, enzulu kakhulu, ngubani na onokufikelela kuyo?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 25, 'Intliziyo yam ndayinikela ekwazini nasekuphengululeni nasekufuneni ubulumko nenjongo yezinto, nokwazi ububi bobuyatha, ewe, ubudenge nobuyatha.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 26, 'Ndafumanisa ukuba kukrakra ngaphezu kokufa, inkazana engumgibe intliziyo yakhe, nezandla zingamathambo; Olungileyo emehlweni kaThixo uya kusinda kuye; ke yena umoni uya kubanjiswa nguye.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 27, 'Qaphelani, nantsi into endiyifumeneyo, utsho umshumayeli, njengoko ndifunda nganye nganye, ukuze ndifumane umbhalo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 28, 'Okufunayo umphefumlo wam, ndingakufumani; indoda enye ewakeni ndiyifumene; andifumananga ntokazi phakathi kwabo bonke.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 7, 29, 'Yabona, le nto kuphela ndiyifumene, yokuba uThixo wamenza umntu olilungisa; kodwa babefuna ukuveliswa okungakumbi.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 1, 'Ngubani na onjengesilumko? kwaye ngubani oyaziyo inkcazo yetyala? Ubulumko bomntu bukhanyisa ebusweni bakhe, nokonakala kobuso bakhe kuya kuguqulwa.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 2, 'Ndikucebisa ukuba uwugcine umyalelo kakumkani, yaye oku kuphathelele isifungo sikaThixo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 3, 'Musa ukukungxamela ukumka ebusweni bakhe; ngokuba wenza into ayithandayo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 4, 'Apho ilizwi lokumkani linegunya; ngubani na onokuthi kuye, Wenza ntoni na?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 5, 'Ogcina umthetho akayi kuva ububi; intliziyo yezilumko iyalazi ixesha nesigwebo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 6, 'Ngokuba yonke into inexesha layo nesigwebo;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 7, 'Kuba engayazi into eya kubakho; ngokuba ngubani na onokumxelela ukuba kuya kuba nini na?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 8, 'Akukho bani unagunya phezu komphefumlo ukusindisa umphefumlo; akanamandla ngemini yokufa, akukho luphumlo kwelo dabi; nobugwenxa abuyi kubasindisa abo bunikiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 9, 'Konke oku ndakubonayo, ndaza ndayinikela intliziyo yam kuwo wonke umsebenzi owenziweyo phantsi kwelanga: kukho ixesha laxa umntu elawula omnye ukuze amenzakalisa.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 10, 'Bangcwatywa ke abangendawo, nabaphumayo, nababephumileyo engcweleni, balityalwa kuloo mzi bebewenzela; kwaye ngamampunge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 11, 'Ngenxa enokuba ukugwetywa kwesenzo esibi akukukhawulezisi ukwenza oko, ngenxa yoko intliziyo yoonyana babantu izele kukwenza ububi.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 12, 'Kwanokuba umoni enze okubi izihlandlo ezilikhulu, yolule imihla yakhe, noko ndiyazi ukuba kuya kuba kuhle kwabamoyikayo uThixo, nabamoyikayo kakuhle;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 13, 'Ke yena ongendawo akayi kuhamba kakuhle, akayi kuyolula imihla yakhe njengesithunzi; ngokuba akamoyiki uThixo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 14, 'Kukho amampunge enzekayo ehlabathini; ukuba kukho abantu abalungileyo abachatshazelwa ngumsebenzi wabantu ababi; kananjalo, kukho abantu abangendawo ababonakala ngokokwenza kwamalungisa; Nam ndathi ngamampunge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 15, 'Ndaluncoma ke mna uvuyo, ngokuba akukho nto imlungeleyo umntu phantsi kwelanga, ngaphandle kokuba adle, asele, avuye; ngokuba buya kuba ngumsebenzi wakhe, ngemihla yobomi bakhe amnikayo uThixo phantsi kwelanga.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 16, 'Xa ndandinikela intliziyo yam ekwazini ubulumko nokubona umsebenzi owenziwa ehlabathini; (kuba kukho imini nobusuku, abuboni ubuthongo emehlweni akhe).', 'XHO22'),
(25, 8, 17, 'Ndawubona ke wonke umsebenzi woThixo oyinyaniso, ukuba akukho namnye unako ukuwuqonda umsebenzi owenziwayo phantsi kwelanga; ngaphezulu koko; Nokuba isilumko safuna ukwazi, akasifumani.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 1, 'Ndacinga ke ngentliziyo yonke le nto, ukuba ndiyithethe yonke le nto, yokuba amalungisa, nezilumko, nemisebenzi yabo, isesandleni sikaThixo; akukho bani waziyo uthando nentiyo kuyo yonke into ephambi kwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 2, 'Izinto zonke zibahlela ngokufanayo bonke: esinye isihlo selungisa, esinye sibe sesongendawo; kolungileyo, kwabahlambulukileyo, nabangcolileyo; Kwalowo uhlabayo, nakongahlabiyo; njengoko anjalo olungileyo, unjalo nomoni; ofungayo, makabe njengokoyika isifungo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 3, 'Kubi ke kuzo zonke izinto ezenziwayo phantsi kwelanga, ukuba behlelwa yinto enye bonke, kwanentliziyo yoonyana babantu izele bububi, ibe bubugeza entliziyweni yabo bedla ubomi, bazibulale ke bona yiya kwabafileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 4, 'Kuba kukho ithemba kulowo unamathela kubo bonke abaphilayo, ekubeni inja ephilayo ilunge ngakumbi kunengonyama efileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 5, 'Ngokuba abadla ubomi bayazi ukuba baya kufa; ke bona abafileyo abazi lutho, abanamvuzo; ngokuba balityelwe, abasakhunjulwa nganto.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 6, 'Seluphelile kade uthando lwabo, nentiyo yabo, nekhwele labo; àbanasabelo naphakade ezintweni zonke ezenzekayo phantsi kwelanga.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 7, 'Yiya udle isonka sakho unovuyo, usele iwayini yakho unentliziyo echwayithileyo; ngokuba ngoku ekholisiwe uThixo imisebenzi yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 8, 'Iingubo zakho mazibe mhlophe ngamaxesha onke; nentloko yakho ayifuneki ngamafutha aqholiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 9, 'Hlala kakuhle nomfazi omthandileyo ngemihla yonke yobomi bakho obungamampunge, omnikileyo phantsi kwelanga, ngemihla yakho yonke engamampunge; ngokuba sisabelo sakho eso ebomini, nasemisebenzini yakho oyenzayo phantsi kwelanga.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 10, 'Konke esikufumanayo ukuba sikwenze isandla sakho kwenze ngamandla akho; ngokuba akusekho kwenza, nakucinga, nakwazi, nakulumka kwelabafileyo, apho uya khona wena.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 11, 'Ndabuya ndabona phantsi kwelanga, ukuba ugqatso asilolwabanamendu, nedabi asilolwabanamandla, nesonka asisosezilumko, nobutyebi asibobabuthathaka, nenceba asiyoyabasweleyo ngenxa yezilumko; kodwa wonke umntu uzalwa enexesha nethuba.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 12, 'Kuba naye umntu akalazi ixesha lakhe; njengentlanzi ebanjiswe ngomnatha ombi, nanjengeentaka ezibanjiswe ngomgibe; ngoko abantwana babantu babanjwa ngexesha elinzima xa libafikela ngequbuliso.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 13, 'Ndabuya ndabubona obu bulumko phantsi kwelanga, ndabona ukuba bukhulu;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 14, 'Kwaye kukho umzi omncinane, unamadoda ambalwa; Wafikela ukumkani omkhulu, wawungqinga, wakha udonga olukhulu lokungqinga.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 15, 'Kwafunyanwa kuwo indoda elihlwempu inobulumko, yona yawusiza umzi ngobulumko bayo; noko akubangakho namnye owakhumbulayo loo mntu ulihlwempu.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 16, 'Ndathi ke mna, Bulunge ubulumko ngaphezu kobugorha; ukanti ubulumko besisweli budelekile, namazwi alo akaviwa.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 17, 'Amazwi ezilumko aviwe kwathi cwaka, Ngaphezu kokukhala komlawuli phakathi kwezinyabi.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 9, 18, 'Bulunge ubulumko ngaphezu kweempahla zokulwa; ke yena umoni emnye utshabalalisa izinto ezininzi.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 1, 'Iimpukane ezifileyo zikhupha amafutha aqholiweyo; bunjalo ubudenge obuncinane kowaziwa ngobulumko nozuko.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 2, 'Intliziyo yesilumko isesandleni saso sokunene; kodwa intliziyo emthubi kwicala lasekhohlo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 3, 'Ewe, nasendleleni, xa sihamba endleleni isidenge, siyaphelelwa bubulumko, sixelele wonke umntu ukuba sisidenge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 4, 'Ukuba ukufutha komlawuli kuthe kwenyuka kwakuchasa, musa ukuyishiya indawo yakho; kuba ithomalalisa ubugwenxa obukhulu.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 5, 'Kukho ububi endibubonileyo phantsi kwelanga, obunjengobubi bomlawuli;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 6, 'Ubutyhakala bunikwa isidima esikhulu, yaye izityebi zihleli phantsi emhlabeni.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 7, 'Ndabona abakhonzi bekhwele emahasheni, neenkosana zihamba emhlabeni njengezicaka.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 8, 'Ombe umngxuma uya kweyela kuwo; othe waphula uthango, inyoka iya kumluma.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 9, 'Osusa amatye, uya kwenzakala ngawo; ocanda iinkuni uya kuba sengozini.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 10, 'Ukuba intsimbi ithe yaba buthuntu, akalulola uhlangothi lwayo, woyenza ibe namandla ngakumbi; ke ubulumko buyanceda bulungise.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 11, 'Okunene, inyoka iya kuluma kungekho kukhafula; kwaye uMthetheleli akangcono.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 12, 'Alungile amazwi omlomo wezilumko; ke yona imilebe yomlomo wesidenge iya kusiginya.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 13, 'Ingqalo, yamazwi omlomo waso bubudenge, nengqibo yomlomo waso bubugeza ongendawo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 14, 'Kwanesidenge sithetha amazwi; akukho bani unokuxela okuya kwenzeka; Kuya kubakho ntoni na emva kwakhe, ngubani na onokumxelela?', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 15, 'Umsebenzi wezidenge uyazidinisa zonke ezo, ngokuba aziyazi indlela yokuya emzini.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 16, 'Yeha, wena lizwe likumkani ungumntwana, zidle amatshawe adlayo!', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 17, 'Hayi, uyolo lwehlabathi, xa ukumkani wakho engunyana wabathetheli, Neenkosi zakho zidla ngexesha elifanelekileyo, ukuze zibe namandla, kungekhona ukunxila!', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 18, 'Isakhiwo sitshabalala ngobuvila obukhulu; ngenxa yobuvila bezandla indlu iyawa.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 19, 'Itheko lenziwa yintsini, newayini indenza ndonwabe, kodwa imali iphendula yonk’ into.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 10, 20, 'Musa ukumtshabhisa ukumkani, nasesandleni sakho; Musa ukuqalekisa isityebi egumbini lakho lokulala; ngokuba intaka yezulu yolikhupha ilizwi, kwaye omaphiko wolixela.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 11, 1, 'Siphose isonka sakho phezu kwamanzi, ngokuba wosifumana kwakuba ziintsuku ezininzi.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 11, 2, 'Yahlula izahlulo zibesixhenxe, zibe nesibhozo; ngokuba akuyazi into embi eya kubakho ehlabathini.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 11, 3, 'Xa amafu ezele yimvula, agaleleka emhlabeni; ukuba umthi uthe wawa, wabheka ezantsi, nokuba uthe wabheka entla, kuloo ndawo uwe kuyo umthi lowo, yoba lapho.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 11, 4, 'Okhangela umoya akayi kuhlwayela; nokhangela amafu akayi kuvuna.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 11, 5, 'Kanye njengokuba ungayazi indlela yomphefumlo kwanendlela akhula ngayo amathambo esibelekweni somfazi omithiyo, ngokunjalo akuyazi imisebenzi kaThixo owenza zonke izinto.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 11, 6, 'Yihlwayele imbewu yakho kusasa, ungasiphumzi isandla sakho ngokuhlwa;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 11, 7, 'Ewe, kulungile ukukhanya, kuyathandeka kwamehlo ukulibona ilanga.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 11, 8, 'Ukuba umntu uthe wadla ubomi iminyaka emininzi, wadla ubomi ebantwini bonke; Makakhumbule imihla yobumnyama; ngokuba baya kuba baninzi. Yonke into ezayo ingamampunge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 11, 9, 'Vuya, ndodana, ebutsheni bakho; ikuvuyise intliziyo yakho ngemihla yesijwili sakho, uhambe ngeendlela zentliziyo yakho, nangokukhangela kwamehlo akho; kodwa yazini ukuba uThixo uya kunigweba kuko konke oko.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 11, 10, 'Yisuse ke ingqumbo entliziyweni yakho, ubudlulise ububi enyameni yakho; ngokuba ezintsha, ezintsha, amampunge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 12, 1, 'Mkhumbule uMdali wakho ngemihla yobutsha bakho, xa ingekafiki imihla yobubi, ingekafiki iminyaka, ukuba uthe: “Andiyoliswa yiyo;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 12, 2, 'Xa ilanga, nokukhanya, nenyanga, neenkwenkwezi, azibi mnyama, namafu akabuyi emva kwemvula.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 12, 3, 'Ngaloo mini baye begubha ababoniseli bendlu, bayaguqa abomeleleyo, bayeke abasila ngenxa yokuba betyhafile, nabavelela ngeefestile benza mnyama;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 12, 4, 'ziya kuvalwa iingcango ezitratweni, sakudamba isandi sengxokozelo;', 'XHO22'),
(25, 12, 5, 'Xa bezoyika iziganga, endleleni kunkwantya, umile um-amangile, usuke ube ngumthwalo umqiwu, uphele umnqweno; Ngokuba umntu uya endlwini yakhe ende, bathi abamatsheke basasaze izitalato.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 12, 6, 'Kunjengoko kwaphulwa intambo yesilivere, nokuba kukwaphulwa kwesitya segolide, nokuba sisitya sequla, nokuba kukwaphuke ivili.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 12, 7, 'Luya kubuyela emhlabeni uthuli, njengoko belunjalo, umoya ubuyele kuThixo owawunikayo.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 12, 8, 'Amampunge awo amampunge, itsho iNtshumayeli; yonke into ingamampunge.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 12, 9, 'Ngaphezu koko, ekubeni umshumayeli wayesisilumko, wayesafundisa abantu ukwazi; ewe, wacingisisa kakuhle waphengulula walungisa izivakalisi ezininzi.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 12, 10, 'Umshumayeli wayefuna ukufumana amazwi amkelekileyo, yaye oko kubhaliweyo kwakuchanekile, amazwi enyaniso.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 12, 11, 'Amazwi ezilumko anjengentonga nanjengezikhonkwane ezibethelelwe ziinkokeli zamabandla, ezinikwe ngumalusi omnye.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 12, 12, 'Kwaye kwakhona, ngoku, nyana wam, lumka: akukho siphelo ekudalweni kweencwadi ezininzi; Ukufunda okuninzi kudinisa inyama.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 12, 13, 'Ukuhlanganiswa kwentetho, yakuba ivakele into yonke, nanku: Yoyika uThixo, ugcine imithetho yakhe, ngokuba indawo leyo yimfanelo yoluntu lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(25, 12, 14, 'Kuba wonke umsebenzi uThixo uya kuwuzisa ekugwetyweni kwayo yonke into efihliweyo, enoba ilungile okanye imbi.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 1, 'iNgoma yazo iiNgoma, eyekaSolomon.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 2, 'Makandange ngokwanga komlomo wakhe, Ngokuba izincokoliso zakho zimnandi ngaphezu kwewayini.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 3, 'Ngenxa yevumba elimnandi lesiqhumiso sakho, igama lakho linjengesiqhumiso esithululwayo; yilonto amantombazana ekuthanda.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 4, 'Nditsale, sibaleke emva kwakho; ukumkani wandingenisa ezingontsini zakhe; siya kuvuya, sivuye ngawe, sicinge ngothando lwakho ngaphezu kwewayini; Amalungisa ayakuthanda.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 5, 'Zintombi zaseYerusalem, ndimnyama, kodwa ndimhle, njengeentente zomsedare, nanjengengubo kaSolomon.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 6, 'Musani ukundikhangela ngakuba ndife mnyama, ngokuba nditshe lilanga; Abantwana bam bandiqumbele; bandimisela umveleli wezidiliya; ke sona isidiliya sam asisisindisanga.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 7, 'Wena uwuthandayo umphefumlo wam, ndixelele apho walusela khona, Walusela khona umhlambi wakho emini; kutheni ndifanele ndibe njengalowo waphambukayo emhlambini wabahlobo bakho?', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 8, 'Ukuba akuyazi loo nto, ukuba mhle phakathi kwabafazi, hamba ngomzekelo womhlambi, waluse iibhokhwe zakho ngaseminqubeni yabalusi.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 9, 'Ntanda yam, ndikufanisa neenqwelo zokulwa zikaFaro;', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 10, 'Zinomkhitha izidlele zakho, Umxokelelwane wegolide, Umqala wakho ngamatyathanga.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 11, 'Sokwenzela iintambo zegolide ezineentambo zesilivere.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 12, 'Xa ukumkani ehleli ngasesithebeni sakhe, iindaba zam zikhupha ivumba lazo.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 13, 'Intanda yam sisipha semore kum; uya kulala phakathi kwamabele am ubusuku bonke.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 14, 'Intanda yam kum injengentlabathi yeminquba, ezidiliyeni zase-Engedi.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 15, 'Yabona, umhle, sithandwa sam; yabona, umhle; unamehlo ehobe.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 16, 'Yabona, umhle, sithandwa sam, ewe, unomtsalane; neemandlalo zethu ziluhlaza.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 1, 17, 'Imiqadi yendlu yethu yimisedare, Imiqadi yethu yimisipres.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 1, 'Ndiyintyantyambo yaseSharon, ndiyinyibiba yasezintlangeni.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 2, 'Njengenyibiba phakathi kwemithana, injalo intanda yam phakathi kweentombi.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 3, 'Njengomapile phakathi kwemithi yehlathi, Injalo intanda yam phakathi koonyana. Bendihleli emthunzini wawo ndinovuyo olukhulu, Neziqhamo zawo zibe nencasa ekhuhlangubeni lam.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 4, 'Yandisa endlwini yetheko, nebhanile yayo phezu kwam luthando.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 5, 'Ndibambe ngamaphiko akho, Ndidlise iiapile, Ngokuba ndisifa luthando.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 6, 'Isandla sayo sokhohlo siphantsi kwentloko yam, Esokunene sayo sindiwole.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 7, 'Zintombi zaseYerusalem, ndinifungela amaxhamakazi, nangexhama lelizwe, ukuba aniyi kuluxhokonxa, ningaluvuseleli uthando lwam, nide nibone.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 8, 'Izwi lentanda yam! yabona, isiza, itsiba ezintabeni, isuka imitsi ezindulini.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 9, 'Intanda yam injengexhama, nexhama; nantso imi emva kodonga lwakowethu, ikroba ngeefestile, iphuma imivalo;', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 10, 'Intanda yam yathetha, yathi kum, Vuka, ntanda yam, ntwana yam, uze.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 11, 'Ngokuba, yabonani, ubusika bugqithile, imvula iphelile;', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 12, 'Iintyatyambo ziyavela emhlabeni; ixesha lokuntyiloza kweentaka lifikile, nesandi sokugoba sivakele ezweni lakowethu;', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 13, 'Umkhiwane uvelisa amakhiwane awo aluhlaza, Imidiliya ineediliya ezinevumba elimnandi. Vuka, sithandwa sam, ntombi yam, hamba!', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 14, 'Vukuthu lam, emqhokrweni wamawa, entsithelweni, ndibubone ubuso bakho, ndilive ilizwi lakho; Ngokuba ilizwi lakho limnandi, ubuso bakho buhle.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 15, 'Sithabatheleni iimpungutye, iimpungutye ezincinane ezonakalisa izidiliya, ngokuba izidiliya zethu zineediliya ezilungileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 16, 'Intanda yam yeyam, nam ndingowaso; Ulusela phantsi kweenyibiba.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 2, 17, 'Lide liphume ilanga namathunzi asabe, jika, sithandwa sam, ube njengexhama ezintabeni zaseBhetere.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 3, 1, 'Ndimlindele esililini sam ebusuku, lowo uthandwa ngumphefumlo wam; Ndamkhangela andamfumana.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 3, 2, 'Ndosuka ndime, ndijikajike umzi ezitratweni, nasezitratweni, ndimfuna lowo uthandwa ngumphefumlo wam; Ndamkhangela andamfumana.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 3, 3, 'Bandifumana abalindi abajikeleze umzi; Ndathi kuye, Uyambona na lowo uthandwa ngumphefumlo wam?', 'XHO22'),
(26, 3, 4, 'Ndagqitha kubo kancinane, ndamfumana lowo uthandwa ngumphefumlo wam; Ndambamba andamyeka ndade ndamsa endlini kamama nasegumbini lokulala lalowo undimithisileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 3, 5, 'Zintombi zaseYerusalem, ndinifungela amaxhamakazi, nangexhama lelizwe, ukuba aniyi kuluvuselela uthando lwam, nide niluthande.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 3, 6, 'Ngubani na lo, unyuka evela entlango njengemiqulu yomsi, egalelwe imore nesiqhumiso esimhlophe, kunye nemifuno yonke yomrhwebi?', 'XHO22'),
(26, 3, 7, 'Naso ke isilili sakhe, esisingqengqelo sikaSolomon; kukho amashumi amathandathu amadoda anobukroti phezu kwalo, kumakroti akwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 3, 8, 'Bonke bephela baphethe amakrele, ngenxa yokuba bafundiswe ukulwa; elowo unekrele ethangeni lakhe ngenxa yonkwantyo lwasebusuku.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 3, 9, 'Ukumkani uSolomon wazenzela inqwelo kwihlathi laseLebhanon.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 3, 10, 'Iintsika zayo wazenza ngesilivere, nemiphantsi yazo ngegolide, nesigubungelo sayo ngemisonto emsi nemfusa;', 'XHO22'),
(26, 3, 11, 'Nina zintombi zaseZiyon, phumani nize nibone uKumkani uSolomon enesithsaba awasinikwa ngunina ngomhla womtshato wakhe nangomhla wovuyo lwentliziyo yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 1, 'Yabona, umhle, sithandwa sam; yabona, umhle; unamehlo ehobe engxoweni yakho; iinwele zakho zinjengomhlambi weebhokhwe ezintabeni zaseGiliyadi.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 2, 'Amazinyo akho anjengomhlambi weegusha ezichetyiweyo, Eziphuma ekuhlanjweni; Ngamnye kubo uzala amawele, yaye akukho namnye uludlolo phakathi kwawo.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 3, 'Imilebe yakho injengomsonto omfusa, yaye intetho yakho imnandi; iintlafuno zakho zinjengothanda lwerharnati ezingxoweni zakho.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 4, 'Intamo yakho injengenqaba kaDavide, eyakhiwe ngokweentonga, Ekuxhonywe kuyo iwaka leengweletshetshe, Onke amakhaka amagorha.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 5, 'Amabele akho omabini anjengamantshontsho amabini eebhokhwe adla phakathi kweenyibiba.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 6, 'Lide liphume ilanga namathunzi asabe, ndiya kuya entabeni yemore nasendulini yesiqhumiso.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 7, 'Uyinzwakazi, sithandwa sam sonke; akukho bala kuwe.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 8, 'Hamba nam, ugxa wam, siye eLebhanon, uhambe nam eLebhanon, ukhangele encotsheni yeAmana, encotsheni yeSenire neHermon, emiqolombeni yeengonyama, ezintabeni zamahlosi.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 9, 'Uyizukisa intliziyo yam, dade wethu, mtshakazi; Uyihombisile intliziyo yam ngelinye lamehlo akho, Ngomxokelelwane omnye emqaleni wakho.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 10, 'Hayi, ukuba ntle kwenceba yakho, dade wethu, mtshakazi! Lubeka phi na ke uthando lwakho ngaphezu kwewayini! nevumba leoli yakho elimnandi njengabo bonke ubulawu!', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 11, 'Umlomo wakho uvuza incindi, mlingane wam; Bubusi namasi ngaphantsi kolwimi lwakho; ivumba leengubo zakho linjengevumba leLebhanon.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 12, 'Udade wethu, ummelwane wam, uhleli endle; Gubungela iqula, vala iqula.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 13, 'Amahlumelo akho ngumyezo wemirharnate, kunye neziqhamo ezimnandi; iCamphor, nespikenard;', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 14, 'inareda nesafron; ubulawu, nesinamon, nemithi yonke yesiqhumiso; imore nehaloti, nobulawu bonke;', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 15, 'Umthombo wemiyezo, Ithende lamanzi aphilileyo, Imilambo yaseLebhanon.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 4, 16, 'Vuka, moya wasentla; uze, wena Mzantsi! Vuthela emyezweni wam, ukuze kuphume ubulawu bawo. Isithandwa sam masingene emyezweni waso, sidle isiqhamo saso esimnandi.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 1, 'Ndingenile emyezweni wam, dade wethu, mtshakazi wam; Ndiyithathile imore yam nobulawu bam; Ndilidlile inqatha lam lobusi nobusi bam; Ndiyayisela iwayini yam, namasi am; yityani, oh bahlobo! sela, ewe, sela kakhulu, zintanda.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 2, 'Ndilele, yona intliziyo yam isaphaphile; lilizwi lentanda yam, inkqonkqoza, isithi, Ndivulele, mzalwana wam, ntanda yam, vukuthu lam elingenazinqambi, ngokuba intloko yam izele ngumbethe, neenwele zam zizele ngamathontsi. Ngobusuku.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 3, 'Ndikhulule ingubo yam; Sendizihlambile na iinyawo zam; Ndingazingcolisa njani?', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 4, 'Intanda yam yasifaka isandla elucangweni, saxuxuzela isisu sam ngenxa yaso.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 5, 'Ndavuka ndaya kuyivula intanda yam; izandla zam zivuza imore, neminwe yam ivuza imore enuka kamnandi, ezikrobeni zezitshixo.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 6, 'Ndasivulela mna intanda yam; Ke yona intanda yam yemka, yemka; Wakhathazeka umoya wam ekuthetheni kwakhe; Ndiye ndambiza, akandiphendula.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 7, 'Bandifumana abalindi abajikeleze umzi, bandibetha, bandingcikiva; Abalindi beendonga bandihlutha isigqubuthelo sam.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 8, 'Zintombi zaseYerusalem, ndiyanifungisa, ukuba nithe nafumana ndithandwa, mxeleleni ukuba ndiyathandwa.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 9, 'Yini na ukuba isithandwa sakho sibe ngaphezu kwezinye izithandane, Wena nzwakazindini phakathi kweentokazi? Yintoni eyenza isithandwa sakho sibengcono kunezinye izithandani, ukuba uya kusifunga ngolo hlobo?', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 10, 'Intanda yam imhlophe, ingqombela, Inkulu phakathi kwamawaka alishumi.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 11, 'Intloko yayo iyigolide engcwengiweyo, ecikizekileyo;', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 12, 'Amehlo ayo anjengamehlo amahobe ngasemilanjeni yamanzi, Ehlanjwe ngobisi, ecocekile kunene.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 13, 'Izidlele zayo zinjengemityino yetyeleba, zinjengentyantyambo yokuqhola; Umlomo wayo unjengeenyibiba ezivuza imore evumba limnandi.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 14, 'Izandla zayo ziintonga zegolide, zimibalabala, Isisu sayo sinjengophondo lwendlovu ebenyezelayo, ethiwe wambu ngesafire.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 15, 'Iinyawo zayo ziintsika zemarmore emhlophe, zibekwe phezu kweziseko zegolide engcwengiweyo; ubuso bakhe bunjengeLebhanon, bubuhle njengemisedare.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 5, 16, 'Umlomo wakhe umnandi; ewe, uthandeka ngokupheleleyo. Yiyo leyo intanda yam, nguye lowo uwethu, Zintombi zaseYerusalem.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 6, 1, 'Iye phi na intanda yakho, Wena nzwakazindini phakathi kweentokazi? Isithandwa sakho siye phi? masimkhangele nawe.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 6, 2, 'Intanda yam yehla yaya emyezweni waso, kwiziqholo, ukuze idle emiyezweni ize ivune iinyibiba.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 6, 3, 'Mna ndingowentanda yam, nentanda yam yeyam; Ulusela phantsi kweenyibiba.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 6, 4, 'Uyinzwakazi, sithandwa sam, njengeTire, uyinzwakazi njengeYerusalem, woyikeka njengeenkamba.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 6, 5, 'Wasuse amehlo akho kum, ngokuba endimisile; Iinwele zakho zinjengomhlambi weebhokhwe waseGiliyadi.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 6, 6, 'Amazinyo akho anjengomhlambi weegusha ezisandul’ ukuhlanjwa, ezizala amawele, kungekho nanye kuzo engazaliyo.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 6, 7, 'Njengeqhekeza lerharnati, iintlafuno zakho zisezingxoweni zakho;', 'XHO22'),
(26, 6, 8, 'Kukho ookumkanikazi abamashumi amathandathu, nezithende ezimashumi asibhozo, neentombi ezingenakubalwa.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 6, 9, 'Hobe lam, wena oyinqambi, wedwa; nguye yedwa ovela kunina, nguye onyuliweyo walowo wamzalayo. Zambona iintombi, zamsikelela; Ewe, abatshakazi nabayeni, yaye baguquka.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 6, 10, 'Ngubani na onjengentsasa, emhle njengenyanga, eqaqambileyo njengelanga, eyoyikeka njengemikhosi exhonywe ngebhanile?', 'XHO22'),
(26, 6, 11, 'Ndehla ndaya emyezweni weminoti ukuze ndibone iziqhamo zentlambo yomlambo oqukuqelayo, ukuze ndibone ukuba umdiliya awuphumelelanga na nokuba iirharnati zihlumile na.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 6, 12, 'Bendisazi nje, umphefumlo wam undenze ndanjengenqwelo yokulwa ka-Aminadibhi;', 'XHO22'),
(26, 6, 13, 'Buya, buya, mShulamiti; buya, buya, ukuze sikujonge. Uza kubona ntoni eMoshulame? Iqela lemikhosi emibini, njengokuba kunjalo.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 7, 1, 'Azi kuhle ukunyathela kwakho ngeembadada, ntombi yokumkani! Amalungu amanqe akho anjengamatye anqabileyo, umsebenzi wezandla ezinkulu.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 7, 2, 'Iinkaba zakho zinjengendebe engqukuva, efuna kusezwa; isisu sakho siyimfumba yengqolowa ebiyelwe ngomdiza.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 7, 3, 'Amabele akho omabini anjengamawele amabini.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 7, 4, 'Intamo yakho injengenqaba yophondo lwendlovu; Amehlo akho anjengamachibi eentlanzi aseHeshbhon, esangweni leBharabhim; Impumlo yakho injengenqaba yaseLebhanon ekhangele eDamasko.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 7, 5, 'Intloko yakho injengeKarmele, iinwele zentloko yakho zinjengosinga olubomvu; ukumkani ugcinwe evarandeni.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 7, 6, 'Hayi, ubuhle bakho!', 'XHO22'),
(26, 7, 7, 'Ukumila kwakho kunjengomthi wesundu; Amabele akho anjengeediliya;', 'XHO22'),
(26, 7, 8, 'Ndathi, Ndiya kukhwela emthini wesundu, ndiwanqumle amasebe awo; Ngoku, amabele akho anjengeediliya, nevumba lempumlo yakho libe njengeeapile;', 'XHO22'),
(26, 7, 9, 'Ikhuhlangubo lakho liyathandeka kum njengewayini enencasa, Yehla kamnandi, Ikhuphise umlomo wabaleleyo.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 7, 10, 'Mna ndingowentanda yam, Umnqweno waso ukum.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 7, 11, 'Yiza, sithandwa sam, sihambe siye emaphandleni; sihlala ezidolophini.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 7, 12, 'Masivuke kusasa, siye ezidiliyeni; Makhe sibone ukuba iidiliya zintshula na, ukuba zikhahlela na iidiliya; Ndoninika khona abandithandayo.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 7, 13, 'iMandereake inevumba elimnandi, yaye kwiminyango yethu kukho zonke iintlobo zeziqhamo ezilungileyo, ezitsha nezindala, endizibekele wena, sithandwa sam.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 8, 1, 'Hayi, ubunjengodade wethu Owanyayo amabele kama! ukuba bendikufumene phandle, bendiya kukwanga; ewe, andifanelanga kugxekwa.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 8, 2, 'Bendiya kukuqhuba, ndikuse endlwini kama, andifundise;', 'XHO22'),
(26, 8, 3, 'Isandla sakhe sokhohlo siya kuba phantsi kwentloko yam, Esokunene sakhe siya kundiwola.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 8, 4, 'Zintombi zaseYerusalem, ndiyaniluleka, ndithi, musani ukuluvusa uthando lwam, musani ukuluvusa uthando lwam, nide nizivumele.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 8, 5, 'Ngubani na onyuka evela entlango, aze ayame ngentanda yakhe? Ndakukhulisa phantsi kom-apile; kulapho wazalelwa khona unyoko; Wakuzalela khona owakuthwala.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 8, 6, 'Ndibeke njengomsesane wokutywina entliziyweni yakho, njengomsesane wokutywina esandleni sakho; ngokuba uthando lunamandla njengokufa; Ikhwele libukrakra njengeBhodulabahu; Ukulamba kwalo ngamalahle omlilo.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 8, 7, 'Amanzi amaninzi akanakulucima uthando;', 'XHO22'),
(26, 8, 8, 'Sinodade wethu omncinane, Akakabi namabele; Kufuneka senze ntoni ngodade wethu xa kuthethwa ngaye?', 'XHO22'),
(26, 8, 9, 'Ukuba ludonga, sokwakha ibhotwe lesilivere phezu kwalo; ukuba lucango, solurhangqa ngamaplanga omsedare.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 8, 10, 'Ndiludonga mna, namabele am anjengenqaba; ngoku ndandiliqabane elithandekayo emehlweni akhe.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 8, 11, 'uSolomon ubenesidiliya eBhahali-hamon; Isidiliya wasinikela kubaveleli; yaziishekele eziliwaka zesilivere ngokwesiqhamo saso.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 8, 12, 'Isidiliya sam, esesam, siphambi kwam; Wena Solomon uya kunikwa iwaka, yaye abo bagcina iziqhamo zabo baya kunikwa amakhulu amabini.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 8, 13, 'Wena, bahleli emiyezweni, zizihlobo ilizwi lakho; mandiyive.', 'XHO22'),
(26, 8, 14, 'Khawuleza, sithandwa sam, ube njengexhama nexhamakazi Ezintabeni zobulawu.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 1, 'Umbono kaIsaya unyana ka-Amotsi, awawubonayo ngokusingisele kuYuda neYerusalem, ngemihla ka-Uziya, noYotam, noAhazi, noHezekiya, ookumkani bakwaYuda.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 2, 'Yivani, mazulu, uve, hlabathi, ngokuba uYehova ethethile, esithi, Ndivelele, ndikhulise abantwana, bandizukisa ke bona.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 3, 'Inkomo iyawazi umniniyo, neesile liyawazi umkhumbi womniniyo, ukanti yena uSirayeli akaqondi, abantu bam abakhathali.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 4, 'Luhlanga lonayo, luhlanga luthwaxwa bubugwenxa, sizukulwana samanginingini, esiziinqambi; Bamnikela umva uYehova, bemgculela oyiNgcwele kaSirayeli, bajikile.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 5, 'Yini na ukuba usafuneke ubethwe? yonke intloko iyafa, yonke intliziyo idandathekile.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 6, 'Ukususela entendeni yonyawo kwesa entloko akukho mntu uphila kamnandi kuyo; ibingamanxeba, nemivumbo, namanxeba amatsha;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 7, 'Ilizwe lenu liyinkangala, imizi yenu itshiswe ngomlilo; ilizwe lakho lidliwe ngabasemzini phambi kwakho, ngoku seliyinkangala, njengoko lalingcwatywe ngabasemzini.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 8, 'Isele ke intombi enguZiyon, njengokhula esidiliyeni, njengomandlalo entsimini yeekomkom, njengomzi ongqingiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 9, 'Ukuba uYehova wemikhosi ebengasishiyelanga nje abambalwa, singe saba njengeSodom, sisuke saba njengeGomora.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 10, 'Liveni ilizwi likaYehova, nina bokumkani baseSodom; wubekeleni indlebe umyalelo woThixo wethu, bantu baseGomora.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 11, 'Yeyani na kum le mibingelelo yenu mininzi kangaka? utsho uYehova. Ndanelisekile ngamadini anyukayo eenkunzi zeegusha, namanqatha amathole atyetyisiweyo; kwaye andikholiswanga ligazi leenkunzi zeenkomo, neleemvana, neleenciniba.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 12, 'Ukuba uza kubonakala phambi kwam, ngubani na oyalele ukuba ungene ezintendelezweni zam?', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 13, 'Nize ningabi sazisa izipho ezilambatha; Isiqhumiso silisikizi kum; ukuthwasa kwenyanga, nesabatha, nokukhala kwamabandla, andiyi kukuphelisa; bubungendawo, yitheko.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 14, 'Ukuthwasa kweenyanga zenu namatheko enu awawuthiyile umphefumlo wam; ilishwa kum; Ndidiniwe kukunxiba.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 15, 'Ukuba nithe nazolula izandla zenu, ndiya kuwafihla amehlo am kuni; ewe, ukuba nithandaza ngamandla, andiyi kuva; izandla zakho zizele ligazi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 16, 'Zihlambe, uhlambuluke; susani ububi beentlondi zenu phambi kwamehlo am; yekani ukwenza ububi;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 17, 'fundani ukwenza okulungileyo; gwebani ityala, gwebani ityala lenkedama; lindelani umhlolokazi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 18, 'Khanize siyigwebe le nto, utsho uYehova; nokuba izono zenu zide zavela zayingqombela njengengqombela, zoba mhlophe njengekhephu; nokuba zide zayingqombela njengebala elibomvu, zovela zinjengoboya begusha.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 19, 'Ukuba nithe nathanda naphulaphula, nodla izinto ezilungileyo zelizwe;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 20, 'Ukuba nithe anavuma, naqhayisa, nobhujiswa likrele, kuba umlomo kaYehova uthethile.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 21, 'Utheni na ukuba lihenyukazi umzi lo, ubunyanisile; ubuzele kukugweba; bekuhlala ubulungisa khona; kodwa ngoku ingababulali.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 22, 'Isilivere yakho isuke yaba ligwebu, iwayini yakho entle ingxengelelwe ngamanzi;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 23, 'Abathetheli bakho ngabakreqi, ngamadlelana namasela; wonke umntu uyazithanda izipho kwaye usukela imivuzo; abaligwebi inkedama, ityala lomhlolokazi alifiki kubo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 24, 'Ngako oko, itsho iNkosi, uYehova wemikhosi, imbalasane yakwaSirayeli, ukuthi, Ndiya kuzisindisa ezintshabeni zam, ndiphindezele impindezelo ezintshabeni zam.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 25, 'Ndiya kusibuyisela phezu kwakho isandla sam, ndikuhlambe ukungcola kwakho, ndisuse zonke izinqe zakho.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 26, 'Ndobabuyisa abagwebi bakho njengokwasekuqaleni, namaphakathi akho njengokwamatanci; emva koko uya kubizwa ngokuba ngumzi wobulungisa, umzi othembekileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 27, 'iZiyon iya kukhululwa ngokusesikweni, nabaguquki bayo ngokusesikweni;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 28, 'Ukutshatyalaliswa kwabakreqi naboni kuya kuba kunye, nabo bamshiyileyo uYehova baya kutshabalala.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 29, 'Ngokuba baya kudana ngenxa yemioki ebeniyinqwenela, nibe neentloni yimiyezo eniyinyulileyo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 30, 'ngenxa yokuba niya kuba njengomthi wom-oki omagqabi omileyo, nanjengomyezo ongenamanzi;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 1, 31, 'nenjengele ibe njengentambo, nomenzi wayo ube yintlantsi, kutshe kuphele kokubini kunye, kungabikho ucimayo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 1, 'Ilizwi awalibonayo uIsaya unyana ka-Amotsi, ngokusingisele kuYuda neYerusalem.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 2, 'Ekupheleni kwemihla, intaba yendlu kaYehova iya kuma encotsheni yazo iintaba, izongamele iinduli; zonke izizwe ziya kuthontelana khona.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 3, 'Kwaye abantu abaninzi baya kuhamba kwaye bathi: Yizani, masinyuke siye entabeni yeNkosi, endlwini yoThixo kaYakobi; asiyalele iindlela zakhe, sihambe ngeendlela zakhe; ngenxa yokuba umthetho nelizwi likaYehova liya kuphuma eZiyon liye eYerusalem.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 4, 'Uya kugweba phakathi kweentlanga, ohlwaye iintlanga ezininzi, ziwakhande amakrele azo abe ngamarhengqa, nezikhali zazo zibe zizikere zokuthena imithi;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 5, 'Nina bendlu kaYakobi, yizani sihambe ekukhanyeni kukaYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 6, 'Ngenxa yoko ubanikele umva abantu bakho, indlu kaYakobi; ngokuba beze empumalanga, besenza amatola njengamaFilisti, betsaleleke koonyana bezinye iintlanga.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 7, 'Ilizwe labo lizele yisilivere negolide, nobuncwane babo buyiphela; ilizwe labo lizele ngamahashe, neenqwelo zokulwa zabo azinasiphelo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 8, 'Kwaye ihlabathi labo lizele zizithixo; baqubuda kumsebenzi wezandla zabo, owenziwe yiminwe yabo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 9, 'Kwaye indoda encinci yaqubuda, kwaye indoda enkulu yazithoba; ke ngoko, musani ukubaxolela.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 10, 'Ngena eliweni uze uzifihle eluthulini ngenxa yokoyika uYehova nangenxa yobukhulu bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 11, 'Amehlo aphakamileyo abantu aya kuthotywa, neqhayiya labantu liya kuthotywa, yaye ngaloo mini nguYehova yedwa oya kuphakanyiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 12, 'Kuba imini kaYehova wemikhosi iya kuba phezu kwabo bonke abanekratshi, abaziphakamisayo, nabo bonke abaziphakamisayo; kwaye uya kuthotywa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 13, 'Nemisedare yonke emide, emide yaseLebhanon, nemioki yonke yaseBhashan;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 14, 'nasezindulini zonke ezinde, nasezindulini zonke eziphakamileyo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 15, 'naphezu kweenqaba zonke ezinde, nasezindongeni zonke ezakhiweyo iindonga;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 16, 'nakwiinqanawa zonke zaseTarshishe, nakuyo yonke imifanekiso eqingqiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 17, 'Ukuphakama kwendoda kuya kuthotywa, nokuphakama kwabantu kuthotywe; yaye nguYehova yedwa oya kuba mkhulu ngaloo mini.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 18, 'Yaye uya kuzitshabalalisa ngokupheleleyo izithixo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 19, 'Kwaye baya kungena emaphandleni nakwimingxuma yomhlaba ngenxa yokoyika uYehova nangenxa yozuko lobungangamsha bakhe, ekuphakameni kwakhe ukuze ashukumise umhlaba.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 20, 'Ngaloo mini umntu uya kuyiphosa ezinambuzaneni naselulwaneni imifanekiso yakhe yesilivere, nemifanekiso yakhe yegolide, abayenzele ukuyinqula;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 21, 'ukuba bangene ezimfanteni zeengxondorha nomkhenkce weengxondorha, ngenxa yokoyika uYehova, nangenxa yozuko lobukhulu bakhe, ekumeni kwakhe ukuba alinyikimise ihlabathi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 2, 22, 'Myeke umntu omphefumlo usemathatheni akhe, ngokuba uya kufundelwa ntoni na?', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 1, 'Ngokuba, yabonani, iNkosi, uYehova wemikhosi, ithabatha iYerusalem neYerusalem, ingumsimelelo, nomsimelelo, nomsimelelo wonke, nomsimelelo wamanzi;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 2, 'igorha negorha, umgwebi nomprofeti, indoda elumkileyo, eqolileyo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 3, 'yingqwayi-ngqwayi yamashumi amahlanu, nobekekileyo, nongumcebisi, nesifundiswa esisisilumko, nothetha olulumkileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 4, 'Ndobanika oonyana babe ngabathetheli babo, nabantwana babalawule;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 5, 'Ziya kucinezelana iintlanga, elowo engowakowabo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 6, 'Kwathi, xa omnye wamthabathayo umzalwana wakhe endlwini kayise, wathi, Nina ninengubo, sikhonzeni;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 7, 'Wofunga ngaloo mini, athi, Andiyi kuba ngugqirha; ngokuba endlwini yam akukho sonka nangubo; musa ukundenza umlawuli wesizwe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 8, 'Kuba iYerusalem iphangiwe noYuda uwile, ngenxa yokuba iilwimi zabo nezenzo zabo zinxamnye noYehova ukuze bawacaphukise amehlo ozuko lwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 9, 'Imbonakalo yobuso babo iyangqina ngabo; bayaxela izono zabo njengeSodom, abakhanyeli. Yeha imiphefumlo yabo! ngokuba baziphindezelele ngobubi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 10, 'Yithi kumalungisa, izinto ziya kumhambela kakuhle, ngokuba aya kudla iziqhamo zezenzo zawo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 11, 'Yeha, ongendawo! kuya kuba kubi kuye, ngokuba uya kunikwa umvuzo wezandla zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 12, 'Ke bona abantu bam, ngabacinezeli babo, balawulwa ngabafazi. Bantu bam, abo banilahlekisayo, bawonakalisayo umendo weendlela zenu.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 13, 'uYehova umi ukuze abalamlele, yaye umi ukuze agwebe uhlanga.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 14, 'uYehova uya kungena ematyaleni namadoda amakhulu abantu bakhe, nabathetheli bakhe, ngenxa yokuba nisidlile isidiliya; amaxhoba eentsizana asezindlwini zenu.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 15, 'Nithini na xa nibatyumza abantu bam naxa nisila ubuso babaxhwalekileyo? itsho iNkosi, uYehova wemikhosi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 16, 'Ngaphezu koko, utsho uYehova ukuthi: “Kungenxa yokuba iintombi zaseZiyon zikhukhumele, zihamba ngeentamo namehlo etyeketyeke, zihamba zigila, zihexa ngeenyawo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 17, 'Ngako oko, iNkosi iya kuzibetha ngesando iintloko zeentombi zaseZiyon, uYehova azihlube iindawo zazo zokusithela.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 18, 'Ngaloo mini uYehova uya kuzisusa izivatho zabo eziduma ezinyaweni zabo, nezidanga zabo nezibopho zabo njengenyanga.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 19, 'Amakhamandi nezacholo nenkunkuma;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 20, 'neminqwazi, nezidanga, nezithsaba, neetafile, namajikazi;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 21, 'Amakhonkco nezacholo zempumlo,', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 22, 'iingubo, iingubo, iingubo, iingubo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 23, 'iiglasi, nelinen ecikizekileyo, neminqwazi, namalaphu.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 24, 'Endaweni yevumba elimnandi kuya kubakho ivumba; kwibhanti yamagxa; nangenxa yenkqayi elungiswe kakuhle; nasendaweni yesicakazana nesinqe setyala; nokutshisa ngenxa yobuhle.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 25, 'Amadoda akho aya kuwa likrele, namagorha akho emfazweni;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 3, 26, 'Kwaye amasango ayo aya kukhala, akhale; ke yena otshabalalayo uya kudla ubomi ehlabathini.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 4, 1, 'Ngaloo mini abafazi abasixhenxe bobambelela ndodeni-nye, besithi, Sodla isonka sethu, sambathe iingubo zethu; masibhenele egameni lakho, ukuba sikususe ukucukucezwa kwethu.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 4, 2, 'Ngaloo mini iqashiso likaYehova liya kuba lihle, liqaqambe, nesiqhamo somhlaba sibe sihle size sibe nomtsalane kwabasindileyo bakwaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 4, 3, 'Wothi oseleyo eZiyon, noseleyo eYerusalem, kuthiwe ungcwele, bonke ababhaliweyo phakathi kwabadla ubomi eYerusalem;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 4, 4, 'ekuhlambeni kukaYehova ukungcola kweentombi zaseZiyon, yalihlambulula igazi leYerusalem kuyo ngomoya wogwebo, nangomoya womlilo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 4, 5, 'uYehova uya kudala phezu kwayo yonke indawo yokuhlala yeNtaba yeZiyon naphezu kwamabandla ayo ilifu elingumsi emini nokukhanya komlilo ovuthayo ebusuku, kuba kuya kubakho indawo yokusithela phezu ‘kozuko lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 4, 6, 'Kuya kubakho umnquba njengomthunzi emini ekubaleleni kwelanga, nendawo yokusabela, neyokusithela esiphangweni nasemvuleni.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 1, 'Intanda yam makhe ndiyivumele ingoma yentanda yam, ngesidiliya sayo. Intanda yam inesidiliya endulini echumayo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 2, 'Wasakha ngothango, wakhupha amatye aso, watyala owona mdiliya ubalaseleyo, wakha inyango phakathi kwaso, wenza nesixovulelo kuso; wayelindele ukuba sivelise iidiliya, sivelise iidiliya zelizwe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 3, 'Kaloku ke, bemi baseYerusalem, nani madoda akwaYuda, gwebani phakathi kwam nesidiliya sam;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 4, 'Kunokwenziwa ntoni na esidiliyeni sam, endingayenzanga ke kuso? Yini na ukuba ndilinde ukuba sivelise iidiliya, sisuke sivelise iidiliya zomhlaba?', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 5, 'Yiyani ngoku; Ke kaloku makhe ndinazise into endiya kusenza yona isidiliya sam ndiludilizile udonga lwaso, ibe siya kunyhashwa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 6, 'Ndolitshabalalisa ke, aliyi kugawulwa, aliyi kumbiwa; kodwa imithana enameva iya kuhluma ndiya kuwawisela umthetho amafu ukuba anganisi mvula.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 7, 'Kuba isidiliya sikaYehova wemikhosi yindlu kaSirayeli, namadoda akwaYuda sisityalo sokumyolisa; funa ubulungisa, nanku ikhala.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 8, 'Yeha, abahlomela indlu kwindlu, abasondeza intsimi kwindima eyiekile, kude kungabikho ndawo, nihlale nedwa phakathi kwelizwe!', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 9, 'uYehova wemikhosi uthethe ezindlebeni zam, wathi, Inene, izindlu ezininzi ziya kuba ngamanxuwa, ezinkulu, ezintle, zingabi namhlali.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 10, 'Kuba ishumi leendima zesidiliya liya kuvelisa ibhete enye, nembewu yehomere yenze iefa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 11, 'Yeha, abavuka kusasa belandela isiselo esinxilisayo; balala kude kube sebusuku, ide ibatshise iwayini.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 12, 'Ugwali, nogwali, neqebengwana, nogwali, newayini, emgidini wabo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 13, 'Kungenxa yoko le nto abantu bam bathinjwa bengazi;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 14, 'Ngeso sizathu, izihogo zawukhulisa, zaza zawuvula umlomo wawo ngokungenamlinganiselo, nozuko lwazo, nesihlwele sazo, nozuko lwazo, ezigcobayo, ziya kuhla phezu kwalo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 15, 'Ke yena umncinane uya kuthotywa, neqhawe lithotywe, athotywe amehlo abaphakamileyo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 16, 'Ke yena uYehova wemikhosi uya kuziphakamisa ngogwebo, azingcwalise uThixo oyiNgcwele ngobulungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 17, 'Kuya kwandula ke amatakane adle ngendlela yawo, yaye okuseleyo kwezityebileyo kuya kudla abasemzini.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 18, 'Yeha, abatsala ubugwenxa ngeentsontelo zenkohlakalo, nesono njengentsontelo yenqwelo!', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 19, 'abathi, Makawukhawulezise umsebenzi wakhe, siwubone; malisondele, lize icebo loyiNgcwele kaSirayeli, ukuze silazi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 20, 'Yeha, abathi okubi kulungile, okulungileyo kubi; into eyenza ubumnyama bube kukukhanya, ukukhanya kube bubumnyama; obeka ubukrakra endaweni yobumnandi nencasa endaweni yobukrakra!', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 21, 'Yeha, abazibona belumkile, banengqondo kwawabo amehlo!', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 22, 'Yeha ke izigantsontso ezisela iwayini, namadoda anamandla aphithikeza isiselo esinxilisayo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 23, 'othi ongendawo ulilungisa ngenxa yomvuzo, abushenxise kuye ubulungisa belungisa!', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 24, 'Ngako oko, njengokuba umlilo uzitshisa iindiza, nelangatye liwudla umququ, ingcambu yabo iya kuba njengokubola, nentyantyambo yabo inyuke njengothuli; ngokuba bewucekisile umyalelo kaYehova wemikhosi, balicekisile ilizwi labo yeenkundla. Oyingcwele kaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 25, 'Wavutha ke umsindo kaYehova kubantu bakhe, usolula phezu kwabo isandla sakhe, waboyisa; Ngenxa yoko awubuyanga umsindo wakhe, kodwa isandla sakhe sisasolulile.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 26, 'Uya kuziphakamisela ibhanile iintlanga ezikude, azivuthele isigodlo kuzo, zivela eziphelweni zehlabathi; kwaye yabona, baya kuza kamsinya.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 27, 'Akukho utyhafileyo, akayi kukhubeka kuzo; akuyi kulala, akuyi kulala mntu; umbhinqo wamanqe azo awusayi kuthukuluka, nomtya weembadada zazo awusayi kunqunyulwa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 28, 'Iintolo zazo zitsolile, nezaphetha zazo zonke zityediwe; neempuphu zamahashe abo zibalelwa njengelitye elinqabileyo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 29, 'Ukugquma kwabo kuya kuba njengengonyama, bagqume njengengonyama; ewe, baya kubharhula, bahluthe okuphangiweyo, balithabathe benoxolo, kungabikho ulihlangulayo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 5, 30, 'Zogquma phezu kwabo ngaloo mini, njengokugquma kolwandle; yaye xa ubani ekhangela ehlabathini, khangela, kukho ubumnyama nosizi, nokukhanya nobumnyama emazulwini alo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 6, 1, 'Ngomnyaka wokufa kuka-Osiya ukumkani, ndambona uYehova ehleli etroneni ende, ephakamileyo, isambatho sakhe sizalise itempile.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 6, 2, 'Kumi iipiramidi phezu kwayo, iyileyo inamaphiko amathandathu; ngamabini ifihle ubuso bayo, ngamabini ifihle iinyawo zayo, ngamabini iphaphazela.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 6, 3, 'Waza omnye wabiza omnye wathi, Ulilungisa, ulilungisa, ulilungisa, unguKumkani waseMasomomo; ihlabathi lizele bubuqaqawuli bakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 6, 4, 'Zashukuma iiplanga lilizwi lodandulukayo, nendlu yazala ngumsi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 6, 5, 'Ndaza ndathi: “Yeha ke mna! ngokuba nditshatyalalisiwe; kuba ndiyindoda enemilebe emdaka, kwaye ndihlala phakathi kwabantu abanemilebe emdaka; ngokuba amehlo am abone iNkosi, uYehova wemikhosi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 6, 6, 'Yaphaphazela yeza kum enye iserafi, iphethe ilahle elivuthayo ngesandla sayo, eyalithabatha ngesandla sayo esibingelelweni;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 6, 7, 'yazibeka emlonyeni wam, yathi, Khangela, uchukumise izandla zakho; bususiwe ubugwenxa bakho, sihlanjululwe isono sakho.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 6, 8, 'Kananjalo ndeva izwi likaYehova, lisithi, Ndothuma bani na? Ngubani na owosiyela? Ndathi ke, Ndikho; ndithumelele.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 6, 9, 'Wathi, Yiya, uthi kwaba bantu, Yivani, nive, ningaqondi; uyabona, kodwa akuboni.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 6, 10, 'Yityebise intliziyo yaba bantu, wenze lukhuni iindlebe zabo, uwavale amehlo abo; hleze babone ngamehlo, beve ngeendlebe zabo, baqonde ngeentliziyo zabo, baguquke, baze baphiliswe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 6, 11, 'Ndathi ke, Nkosi, koda kube nini na? Saphendula sathi, Ide yonakale imizi, ingabi nabemi, ingabi nabemi, litshabalale ilizwe;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 6, 12, 'uYehova wabafudusela kude abantu, kwabakho ukuphanziswa okukhulu ezweni.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 6, 13, 'Kusaya kubakho isahlulo seshumi sawo, sibuye sidliwe; ngaloo ndlela imbewu engcwele iya kuba bubutyebi bayo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 1, 'Ngemihla ka-Ahazi, unyana kaYotam, unyana ka-Uziya, ukumkani wakwaYuda, wayifikela iYerusalem uRetsin, ukumkani wakwa-Aram, noPeka, unyana kaRemaliya, ukumkani wakwaSirayeli kodwa akazange akwazi ukoyisa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 2, 'Kwaxelwa kwindlu kaDavide, kwathiwa, Ama-Aram enze umnqophiso noEfrayim. Yadidizela intliziyo yakhe, nentliziyo yabantu bakhe, njengokudidizela kwemithi yehlathi phambi komoya.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 3, 'Wathi uYehova kuIsaya, Hamba uye kumkhawulela ngoku uAhazi, wena noShehare-yasub unyana wakho, ekupheleni komjelo wechibi eliphezulu, emendweni ongasentsimini yomxovuli weengubo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 4, 'Wathi kuye, Zikhangele, uthi cwaka; Musa ukoyika, ungaqhiphuki umbilini ngenxa yaloo misila mibini iqhumayo, ngenxa yomsindo kaRetsine kuma-Aram nonyana kaRemaliya.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 5, 'Ngenxa enokuba ama-Aram, uEfrayim, nonyana kaRemaliya, becebe ngawe, besithi,', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 6, 'Masimhlasele uYuda size simdinise, yaye masimenze abe nekhwele, simisele ukumkani phakathi kwakhe, unyana kaTabhehali.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 7, 'Itsho iNkosi uYehova ukuthi, Loo mbambano ayiyi kubakho, ingabikho.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 8, 'Ngokuba intloko yama-Aram yiDamasko, intloko yeDamasko nguRetsin; phambi kweminyaka engamashumi amathandathu anesihlanu uEfrayim uya kwaphulwa, angabi luhlanga.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 9, 'Intloko yamaEfrayim kukwaSamari, intloko yakwaSamari ngunyana kaRemaliya. Ukuba awukholwa, awuyi kuqinisekiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 10, 'Waphinda uYehova wathetha kuAhazi, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 11, 'Zicelele umqondiso kuYehova uThixo wakho; intle, nokuba unzulu, nokuba uphezulu.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 12, 'Wathi uAhazi, Andiyi kucela, andiyi kumlinga uYehova.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 13, 'Wathi, Phulaphulani, nina bendlu kaDavide! Yinto encinane le kuni ukuba nihlisele ishwangusha, nimbandezele uThixo wam?', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 14, 'Ke ngoko, iNkosi ngokuqinisekileyo iya kuninika umqondiso; Uyabona, intombi le iya kumitha, izale unyana, imthiye igama elinguEmanuweli.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 15, 'Uya kudla ubusi nobusi, ukuze alahle ububi, anyule okulungileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 16, 'Kuba ngaphambi kokuba loo nkwenkwe ikwazi ukugatya okubi nokukhetha okulungileyo, ilizwe olithiyileyo liya kushiywa ngookumkani balo ababini.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 17, 'uYehova wozisa wena nabantu bakho, nendlu kayihlo, imihla ekungazanga kubekho ingangayo, kususela koko wemkayo uEfrayim kwaYuda; nokumkani waseAsiriya.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 18, 'Ngaloo mini uYehova uya kubetha ikhwelo phezu kwempukane esesiphelweni semilambo yaseYiputa naphezu kwenyosi esezweni laseAsiriya.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 19, 'Kwaye ziya kufika ziphumle zonke emingxunyeni nasengxondorheni nakuwo onke ameva nakuwo onke ameva.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 20, 'Ngaloo mini uYehova uya kuyicheba intloko noboya bemilenze ngesitshetshe esiqeshiweyo sokumkani waseAsiriya phesheya koMnayile, uzidle iindevu.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 21, 'Ngaloo mini umntu uya kwalusa inkuku neegusha ezimbini;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 22, 'Ngenxa yobutyebi bobisi bazo, niya kudla ibhotolo; ngokuba bonke abaseleyo belizwe baya kudla incindi nobusi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 23, 'Ngaloo mini zonke iindawo ezazinewaka lemidiliya enewaka leesilivere, ziya kuba yimithana enameva neenkunzane.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 24, 'Kuya kufika abantu khona bephethe izaphetha neentolo; ngokuba lonke ilizwe liya kuba yimithana enameva neenkunzane.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 7, 25, 'Kuzo zonke iintaba eziya kombiwa ngentonga, akuyi koyikwa yimithana enameva namakhakakhaka, kodwa iya kuba yindawo yokugxotha iinkomo nokunyathela amathole.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 1, 'Wathi uYehova kum, Thabatha incwadi esongwayo enkulu, ubhale kuyo ngosiba lomntu, uthi, Mahersal-hasbhas;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 2, 'Ndathabatha amangqina am athembekileyo ukuze ndiwabhale, umbingeleli u-Uriya noZekariya unyana kaYeberekiya.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 3, 'Ndafika kumprofetikazi; wakhawula, wazala unyana. Wathi uYehova kum, Mbize ngokuba nguMahersal-hasbhas.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 4, 'Kuba ngaphambi kokuba umntwana akwazi ukubiza ngokuthi: “Tata noMama, ubutyebi baseDamasko namaxhoba aseSamariya aya kuthwalelwa phambi kokumkani waseAsiriya.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 5, 'Waphinda uYehova wathetha kum, esithi:', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 6, 'Kuthiwa abantu bala kuwo amanzi aseSilowa awawa ngobunono kwaye bagcoba ngoRetsin nonyana kaRemaliya;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 7, 'Ngako oko, yabonani, iNkosi iwazisela amanzi omlambo, ukuba ngamandla, maninzi, ukuze awafikele, ukumkani waseAsiriya nobuqaqawuli bakhe bonke; uya kunyuka aye emideni yayo yonke, aludlule lonke unxweme lwalo,', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 8, 'liya kucanda kwaYuda; uya kuvula, adlule, afike entanyeni; ukunaba kwamaphiko akhe kuya kuzalisa ububanzi belizwe lakho, Emanuweli!', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 9, 'Yibani mnandi, nityunyuzwe; niphulaphule, nonke mazwe akude; zibopheni, niqotywe; zibopheni, niqotywe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 10, 'Cebani icebo, lotshitsha; Thethani ilizwi, aliyi kubakho; ngokuba uThixo unathi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 11, 'Kuba wenjenje uYehova ukuthetha kum ngesandla esomeleleyo waza wandiyalela ukuba ndingahambi ngendlela yolu hlanga, wathi:', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 12, 'Musa ukuthi, Ngumnqophiso wabo bonke abathi abo bantu, Ngumnqophiso; musani ukoyika ukunkwantya kwabo, musani ukoyika.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 13, 'Mbongeni uYehova wemikhosi; kwaye makabe luloyiko kuni, kwaye makabe nguye uloyiko kuni.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 14, 'Yoba yingcwele; ke kuzo zombini izindlu zakwaSirayeli iya kuba yisikhubekiso, nesikhubekiso, nomgibe nomgibe kubemi baseYerusalem.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 15, 'Abaninzi kubo baya kukhubeka bawe, baphuke, batshiswe, babanjiswe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 16, 'Bopha ubungqina, uwuqinise umthetho phakathi kwabafundi bam.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 17, 'Ndiya kulindela kuYehova obufihlayo ubuso bakhe kwindlu kaYakobi, ndize ndimfune.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 18, 'Yabona, mna nabantwana andinikileyo uYehova, singabemiqondiso nezimanga kwaSirayeli, ezivela kuYehova wemikhosi, ulohlala entabeni yaseZiyon.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 19, 'Xa bathe kuni, Quqelani kwimimoya yabafileyo, nabakhafuli abalalelayo, abaxokozelayo, abantu abayi kumquqela na uThixo wabo? ngabaphilayo kwabafileyo?', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 20, 'Kuwo umyalelo nakubungqina, Ukuba abathanga bathethe eli lizwi, boba abanasifingo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 21, 'Baya kucanda kulo, bengaginywanga, belambile; kwaye xa belambile, baya kuba nomsindo, baqalekise ukumkani wabo noThixo wabo, baze bajonge phezulu.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 8, 22, 'Kwaye baya kuya ehlabathini; nanko kukho imbandezelo nobumnyama; kwaye baya kuqhutywa ebumnyameni.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 1, 'Ke yena ubumnyama abuyi kuba njengomsindo wakhe, ekulitshutshiseni kwakhe ilizwe lakwaZebhulon nelizwe lakwaNafetali umzuzwana, wabatshutshisa kakubi endleleni eya elwandle, phesheya kweYordan, iGalili yeentlanga.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 2, 'Ke abo bahamba ebumnyameni babone ukukhanya okukhulu; abo bahleli ethunzini lokufa bakhanyiselwa kukukhanya.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 3, 'Ubandisile abantu, akwandise luvuyo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 4, 'Ngokuba uyaphule idyokhwe yomthwalo wabo, umsimelelo osemagxeni abo, nomsimelelo womxinzeleli wabo, njengoko kwakunjalo ngemihla yakwaMidiyan.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 5, 'Kuba yonke imfazwe yegorha inesandi esididekileyo, neengubo zizele ligazi; kodwa kuya kuba kumlilo nakukudla.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 6, 'Kuba sizalelwe umntwana, sinikwe unyana; ukuthethela kusegxalabeni lakhe, ukubizwa kwakhe kuthiwe nguMmangaliso, nguMcebisi, uThixo oligorha, nguSonini-nanini, nguMthetheli woxolo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 7, 'Akuyi kubakho ukwanda kolongamo noxolo ukusa kwixesha elingenammiselo etroneni kaDavide nasebukumkanini bakhe ukuze abuqinise buqinise ngobulungisa nangokusesikweni ukususela ngoku kuse kwixesha elingenammiselo. Ubukhwele bukaYehova wemikhosi buya kukwenza oko.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 8, 'uYehova wathumela ilizwi kuYakobi, lamndulula ke uSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 9, 'Kwaye bonke abantu baya kwazi, oko kukuthi, uEfrayim nabemi bakwaSamari, abathetha ngekratshi nangentliziyo eqinileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 10, 'Izitena ziwile, siya kwakha ngamatye aqingqiweyo; imithombe igawulwe, siya kuyitshintsha ibe yimisedare.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 11, 'Ngako oko uYehova uya kubavelisela abachasi bakaRetsine, azihlanganisele ndawonye iintshaba zakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 12, 'Ama-Aram engaphambili, amaFilisti ngasemva; kwaye ziya kudla uSirayeli ngomlomo ovulekileyo. Ngenxa yoko awubuyanga umsindo wakhe, kodwa isandla sakhe sisasolulile.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 13, 'Kuba uhlanga alubuyelanga kuLowo ulohlwayayo, yaye alukhange lufune uYehova wemikhosi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 14, 'Kungenxa yoko le nto uYehova eya kumnqumla uSirayeli intloko nomsila, isebe nerhengqa ngamini-nye.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 15, 'Indoda enkulu nebekekileyo, yintloko ke leyo; yaye umprofeti ofundisa ubuxoki ngumsila.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 16, 'Ngokuba abathetheli baba bantu babandwendwisa; nabo bakhokelwa zizo bayatshabalala.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 17, 'Ke ngoko, iNkosi ayiyi kukholiswa ngabo bafana babo, kwaye ayiyi kuba namfesane kubo nabahlolokazi, ngenxa yokuba bonke bangabahanahanisi nabakhohlisayo, kwaye yonke imilomo ithetha ubudenge. Ngenxa yoko awubuyanga umsindo wakhe, kodwa isandla sakhe sisasolulile.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 18, 'Kuba okungendawo kuvutha njengomlilo, kutshisa imithana enameva neenkunzane, liwatshise amatyholo, linyuke njengomsi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 19, 'Ngokuvutha komsindo kaYehova wemikhosi umhlaba wenziwa mnyama, neentlanga ziya kuba njengamalahle avuthayo; Akukho bani uya kumconga umzalwana wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 20, 'Uya kusikrazula isandla sakhe sokunene, walambe; ngasekhohlo uya kudla, bangahluthi; elowo adle inyama yesandla sakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 9, 21, 'uManase, uEfrayim; noEfrayim noManase, bona kunye baya kuba nxamnye noYuda. Ngenxa yoko awubuyanga umsindo wakhe, kodwa isandla sakhe sisasolulile.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 1, 'Yeha, abamisa umthetho, nababhala phantsi imizekeliso;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 2, 'Ukuphambukisa osweleyo koko kulungileyo nokuhlutha okusesikweni kwabasweleyo bohlanga lwam, ukuze abahlolokazi babe lixhoba labo, neenkedama ziphangwe!', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 3, 'Niya kuthini na ke ngomhla wokuvelelwa kwenu, nivela kude? Uya kubalekela kubani na ukuba akuncede? ulushiye phi na uzuko lwakho?', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 4, 'Ngaphandle kwam baya kuguqa phakathi kwabathinjwa, bawe phakathi kwababuleweyo. Ngenxa yoko awubuyanga umsindo wakhe, kodwa isandla sakhe sisasolulile.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 5, 'uAsiriya, luswazi lomsindo wam, luswazi olusesandleni sabo ngumsindo wam.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 6, 'Ndiza kumthumela kuhlanga lwabahanahanisi, yaye ndiya kumyalela nxamnye nabantu bomsindo wam ukuba athabathe okuthinjiweyo aze athabathe into ethinjiweyo aze abanyathele njengodaka ezitratweni.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 7, 'Ke akenjinjalo; intliziyo yakhe ayiyicingi loo nto; kodwa kusentliziyweni yakhe ukutshabalalisa nokutshabalalisa iintlanga ezimbalwa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 8, 'Kuba uthi, Abathetheli bam asingookumkani ngokupheleleyo na?', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 9, 'iKalno ayifane na neKarkemishe? Xa ndithi, iHamati ayinjengeArpadi? iSamariya ayinjengeDamasko na?', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 10, 'Njengoko isandla sam sazifumanayo izikumkani zemifanekiso eqingqiweyo, ezinemifanekiso yazo eqingqiweyo yadlula kuyo, iYerusalem neSamariya;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 11, 'andiyi kuthi na ke ndiyenze kwiYerusalem nezithixo zayo, njengoko ndenza ngako kowakwaSamari nezithixo zawo ezingeni?', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 12, 'Ngako oko, xa ithe iNkosi yawugqiba wonke umsebenzi wayo entabeni yeZiyon naseYerusalem, ndozivelela iziqhamo zentliziyo eqinileyo yokumkani waseAsiriya, nesihombo sozuko lwakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 13, 'Ngokuba wathi, Ndenza ngamandla esandla sam, nangobulumko bam; ngenxa enokuba ndilumkile, ndayishenxisa imida yezizwe, ndabuthabatha ubuncwane babo, ndabaphanzisa abantu njengendoda enobukroti.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 14, 'Sabufumana isandla sam ubutyebi bezizwe njengendlu yentaka, ndalibutha mna lonke ihlabathi, njengokubutha amaqanda; akwabakho namnye oshukumisa iphiko, evula umlomo, akakroba.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 15, 'Izembe lingamqhayisela na umnqunquli walo? Okanye isarha iya kuziphakamisela kulowo uyishukumisayo? kube ngathi iphiko livuthelwa ngabasithwaliyo, okanye kube ngathi lithwalwa intshontsho ngokungathi alikho esigodoni.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 16, 'Ngako oko uYehova, uYehova wemikhosi, uya kuwathumela iintlungu phakathi kwamanqatha akhe; phantsi kokukhanya kwakhe uya kuphemba umlilo njengomlilo ovuthayo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 17, 'Ukhanyiso lukaSirayeli luya kuba ngumlilo, oyiNgcwele wakhe abe lilangatye; kwaye ngenye imini liya kutshisa, litshise ameva alo nameva;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 18, 'yaye uya kulutshabalalisa uzuko lwehlathi lakhe nolwelizwe lakhe elinemveliso, umphefumlo nomzimba, yaye ziya kuba njengokufa komthwali-mthetho.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 19, 'Imithi eseleyo yehlathi lakhe iya kuba buthathaka, ukuze inkwenkwe ibhale phantsi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 20, 'Kuya kuthi ngaloo mini, angabi sahlala amasalela akwaSirayeli, nabasindileyo bendlu kaYakobi, nabawaxabelayo; kodwa mna ngokuqinisekileyo ndiya kuma phambi koYehova, Lowo Ungcwele kaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 21, 'Amasalela aya kubuya, amasalela akwaYakobi, abuyele kuThixo oligorha.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 22, 'Kuba nangona uhlanga lwakho, Sirayeli, belunjengentlabathi yaselwandle, obuya kubuya amasalela alo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 23, 'Kuba iNkosi enguMongami uYehova wemikhosi iza kuzisa intshabalalo, ewe, izaliseke kulo lonke ilizwe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 24, 'Ngako oko, itsho iNkosi uYehova wemikhosi ukuthi, Bantu bam, bemi eZiyon, musani ukuyoyika uAsiriya;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 25, 'Ngokuba lisaya kuba lifutshane ixesha, ukuba iphele ingqumbo, nomsindo wam ubatshabalalise.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 26, 'Yaye uYehova wesaqhwithi uya kumqwenga, njengoko amaMidiyan awoyiswa kwiliwa likaOrebhe; kwanjengokuba ibinjalo intonga yakhe phezu kolwandle, uya kuyiphakamisa ngokohlobo lwaseYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 27, 'Kuya kuthi ngaloo mini, ususwe umthwalo wakhe esixhantini sakho, nedyokhwe yakhe esandleni sakho, idake idyokhwe ngenxa yokuthanjiswa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 28, 'Ekufikeni kwakhe eAyati wawela, waya eMigron; eMigmas wazibeka iinqwelo zakhe zokulwa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 29, 'Badlula ngendlela; ayakha iGebha; iRama iyoyika; iGibheha yasaba ngenxa kaSawule.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 30, 'Liphakamise ilizwi lakho, Owu ntombi yaseGalim;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 31, 'iMadmena isusiwe; abantu baseGebhim bahlanganisana ukuba basabe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 32, 'Uya kuhlala eNobhi ngaloo mini; uya kubeka isandla sakhe entabeni yentombi enguZiyon, endulini yaseYerusalem.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 33, 'Yabona, iNkosi, uYehova wemikhosi, iya kuwavikiva amagatya ngokunkwantyisa, aphakamileyo nophakamileyo agawulwe, abaziphakamisayo bathotywe;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 10, 34, 'Uya kuwagawula amatyholo ehlathi ngesixengxe, iwe iLebhanon ngekrele.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 1, 'Kuya kuphuma intonga kwindlu kaYese, kuhlume ihlumelo ezingcanjini zakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 2, 'Wohlala phezu kwakhe uMoya kaYehova, umoya wobulumko nowokuqonda, umoya womnqweno nowamandla, umoya wokwazi nowokoyika uYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 3, 'Womdlisa ubomi ngentliziyo ephilileyo, esoyika uYehova; angagwebi ngokubona kwamehlo akhe, engayi kukhalimela ngokuva kweendlebe zakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 4, 'Uya kuligweba ityala lehlwempu ngobulungisa, abakhalimele abalulamileyo behlabathi ngokuthe tye; uya kuwubetha umhlaba ngentonga yomlomo wakhe, ababulale ongendawo ngomoya womlomo wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 5, 'Ubulungisa buya kuba ngumbhinqo esinqeni sakhe, nokuthembeka kube ngumbhinqo wamanqe akhe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 6, 'Ingcuka iya kuhlala nemvana, ingwe netakane lebhokhwe; laye ithole, nethole, nenkomo, yatyetyiswa kunye; nomntwana uya kuzikhokela.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 7, 'Ithokazi lenkomo nebhere ziya kudla utyani; amathole azo abuthe ndaweni-nye, ingonyama idle utyani njengenkomo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 8, 'Kwaye umama oncancisayo uya kudlala emanzini benyoka, nomntwana olunyulweyo afake isandla sakhe kuloo nto imanzi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 9, 'Aziyi kwenzakalisa okanye ziyonakalisa intaba yam engcwele iphela, ngenxa yokuba umhlaba uya kuzala kukwazi uYehova njengamanzi egubungele ulwandle.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 10, 'Ngaloo mini kuya kubakho indoda yakwaYese, eya kuma njengoqhwithela lwabantu; Emveni koko ziya kufuna iintlanga, yaye ukuphumla kwakhe kuya kuba nobuqaqawuli.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 11, 'Ngaloo mini uYehova uya kuphinda esolule isandla sakhe isihlandlo sesibini kumasalela abantu bakhe abaseleyo, eAsiriya naseYiputa, ePatrosi, eKushe, eElam, naseShinare naseShinare. iHamati neziqithi zolwandle.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 12, 'Uya kuziphakamisela ibhanile iintlanga, ahlanganise abagxothiweyo bakwaSirayeli, abahlanganisele abasabileyo bakwaYuda kwiimbombo zone zomhlaba.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 13, 'Kwaye ikhwele likaEfrayim liya kumka, kwaye iintshaba zikaYuda ziya kutshabalala; uEfrayim akayi kumkhweletela uYuda, noYuda akayi kumqumbela uEfrayim.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 14, 'Wophaphazela egxalabeni lamaFilisti, aye ngasentshonalanga; baya kuyiphanga iMpuma kunye; baya kusolula isandla sabo phezu koEdom noMowabhi; oonyana baka-Amon baya kubaphulaphula.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 15, 'uYehova uya kulubetha ngesiqalekiso ulwimi lolwandle lwaseYiputa; Woyishukumisa ngesandla sakhe phezu komlambo ngomoya wakhe onamandla, awubethe imilambo esixhenxe, abakhwelise abantu ngeembadada ezomileyo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 11, 16, 'Kuya kubakho umendo wamasalela abantu bakhe, abaseleyo eAsiriya; njengoko kwakunjalo kuSirayeli, ngemini yokunyuka kwawo evela ezweni laseYiputa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 12, 1, 'Ngaloo mini uya kuthi, Yehova, ndiya kubulela kuwe; nangona ubundiqumbele, wabuya umsindo wakho, wandithuthuzela.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 12, 2, 'Yabona, uThixo ulusindiso lwam; Ndiya kukholosa, andiyi koyika; ngokuba uYehova ungamandla am nendumiso yam; waba lusindiso kum.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 12, 3, 'Ke ngoko, niya kukha amanzi ngovuyo emithonjeni yosindiso.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 12, 4, 'Niya kuthi ngaloo mini, Dumisani uYehova, libizeni igama lakhe, zivakaliseni ezintlangeni izenzo zakhe, nivakalise ukuba liyingxonde igama lakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 12, 5, 'Memelelani uzuko lukaYehova; ngokuba wenze imisebenzi ebalulekileyo, eyaziwa ehlabathini lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 12, 6, 'Dumani nivuye, nina bemi baseZiyon, ngokuba mkhulu phakathi kwenu oyiNgcwele kaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 1, 'Isihlabo saseBhabheli, awasibonayo uIsaya, unyana ka-Amos.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 2, 'Phakamisa ibhanile entabeni ephakamileyo, uphakamise ilizwi lakho kubo, phakamisa isandla sakho, bangene ngeengcango zamanene.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 3, 'Mna ndibawisele umthetho abenceba bam, ndabiza iingxilimbela zam ngenxa yomsindo wam, abaqhayisa ngobude bam.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 4, 'Kuvakala isandi sengxokolo ezintabeni, ngathi sesezizwe ezininzi; Kuhlanganiselwe ndawonye ukudubadubeka kwezizwe; uYehova wemikhosi uhlanganisa imikhosi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 5, 'Bavela ezweni elikude, ekupheleni kwamazulu, uYehova nezixhobo zomsindo wakhe, ukuba alonakalise ihlabathi lonke.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 6, 'Lilani; ngokuba ikufuphi imini kaYehova; liya kuza njengenkangala evela kuSomandla.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 7, 'Ngako oko, zonke izandla ziya kubethwa, neentliziyo zabantu bonke ziya kuthamba.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 8, 'Baya kunkwantya; baya kufikelwa bububi naziimbandezelo; baya kuva ubunzima njengozalayo; ziyangqubana; ubuso babo buya kuba njengamalangatye.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 9, 'Yabona, imini kaYehova iyeza, inobujorha, ishushu, ishushu, ukuze iliguqule ilizwe libe yintlango; abatshabalalise aboni bakhe kulo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 10, 'Kuba iinkwenkwezi zezulu neenkwenkwezi zazo aziyi kukhanyisa kukhanya kwazo; liya kuba mnyama ilanga ekuphumeni kwalo, nenyanga ingakhanyisi ukukhanya kwayo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 11, 'Kwaye ndiya kuwuvelela umhlaba ngenxa yenkohlakalo yawo nabakhohlakeleyo ngenxa yenkohlakalo yabo; yaye ndiya kulibangela lithotywe ikratshi labakhukhumeleyo neqhayiya labangcangcazelisayo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 12, 'Umntu ndiwenze athandeke ngaphezu kwegolide engcwengiweyo; nendoda enjengentonga yegolide yakwaOfire.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 13, 'Ngoko ke ndiya kuwanyikimisa amazulu, nomhlaba uya kunyikima endaweni yawo ngomsindo kaYehova wemikhosi nangemini yomsindo wakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 14, 'Kuya kuba njengeenciniba ezisukelwayo, nanjengegusha engayichomiyo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 15, 'Bonke abafunyenweyo baya kutyunyuzwa; yaye wonke ubani othe wawumanya nawo uya kuwa likrele.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 16, 'Yaye abantwana babo baya kutyunyuzwa phambi kwamehlo abo; izindlu zabo ziya kuphangwa, nabafazi babo baya kuhlaziswa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 17, 'Yabona, ndixhoxha amaMedi angayikhathaleleyo isilivere; yona igolide, abayi kukholiswa yiyo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 18, 'Izaphetha zawo zowaphula amadodana; nesiqhamo sesizalo sikanina abayi kuba namfesane; amehlo abo akayi kubaconga abantwana.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 19, 'Yaye iBhabhiloni, iqhayiya lookumkani, iqhayiya lamaKhaledi, iya kuba njengokubhukuqa kukaThixo iSodom neGomora.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 20, 'Aliyi kuba sanabemi, yaye ukususela kwesinye isizukulwana ukuya kwesinye liya kuba sanabemi; nomArabhu akanako ukumisa intente khona; yaye abalusi abayi kwenza nawuphi na umhlambi apho.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 21, 'Kodwa amarhamncwa asendle aya kuba yindle; nezindlu zabo ziya kuzaliswa zizidalwa; kuya kuhlala khona izikhova, kuphaphazele khona iintaka.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 13, 22, 'Kwaye amarhamncwa eziqithi aya kubhomboloza ezindlwini zabo ezishiyiweyo, neempungutye ezindlwini zabo zobukumkani ezithandekayo; ixesha lakhe lisondele, nemihla yakhe ayiyi kolulwa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 1, 'Ngokuba uYehova uya kuba nemfesane kuYakobi, angawanyuli amaSirayeli, awashiye emhlabeni wawo; nabasemzini baya kuzimanya nabo, banamathele kwindlu kaYakobi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 2, 'Abantu baya kubathabatha, babase endaweni yabo; kwaye abendlu kaSirayeli baya kuwadla ilifa ezweni likaYehova, babe ngabakhonzi nezicakakazi; kwaye baya kubalawula abacinezeli babo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 3, 'Kuya kuthi, xa athe uYehova waniphumza ebubini benu, nasekunkwantyiseni kwenu, nasekukhonzeni kwakho nzima,', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 4, 'nize nithethe le mizekeliso nxamnye nokumkani waseBhabhiloni nithi, ‘Hayi indlela ehambe ngayo lo zwilakhe! Umzi wegolide umile!', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 5, 'uYehova uwaphule umsimelelo wabangendawo, nentonga yobukhosi yabalawuli.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 6, 'Lowo wohlwaya iintlanga ngomsindo wakhe, engenasiphelo; lowo ulawula iintlanga ngomsindo, uyatshutshiswa, akukho unqandayo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 7, 'Liphumle, lizolile ihlabathi lonke; bagqabhuka yimincili.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 8, 'Kananjalo imisipres ikuvuyele, nemisedare yaseLebhanon, isithi, Ulele nje, akuyi kusihlasela impungutye.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 9, 'Izihogo ezisuka ezantsi zinyathele ukukuhlangabeza ekuzeni kwakho; wabaphakamisa ezitroneni zabo bonke ookumkani beentlanga.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 10, 'Baya kuthetha bonke, bathi kuni, Nani wenziwe ofayo njengathi na? uyafana nathi?', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 11, 'Buhlile uzuko lwakho kwelabafileyo, nesandi seehadi zakho;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 12, 'Utheni na ukuwa emazulwini, Lusifa, nyana wesifingo! Ukuphoswa phantsi kwakho, mngquli weentlanga!', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 13, 'Ngenxa enokuba uthe entliziyweni yakho, Ndiya kunyukela emazulwini, ndiyinyuse itrone yam ibe ngaphezu kweenkwenkwezi zikaThixo; Ndiya kuhlala ke entabeni yebandla, kweleembombo zasentla.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 14, 'Ndiya kunyuka ndiye ezindaweni eziphakamileyo zamafu; ndiya kuba njengoPhezukonke.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 15, 'Noko ke, uya kuhliselwa kwelabafileyo, emacaleni omhadi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 16, 'Abakubonayo baya kukukhangela, bakukhangele, bathi, Yilaa yini na le indoda eyayilinyikimisa elimiweyo, ebizinyikimisa izikumkani?', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 17, 'owalenza ilizwe njengenkqantosi, ebezigungxula imizi yalo; ongayivulanga indlu yamabanjwa akhe?', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 18, 'Bonke ookumkani beentlanga, bonke bephela, balele benozuko, ngamnye endlwini yakhe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 19, 'Ke wena, ulahliwe esizalweni sakho, njengamadlavu namadlavu, nanjengeengubo zababuleweyo, abahlatywe ngekrele, abehla baye emangcwabeni; inyathelwe njengesidumbu.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 20, 'Musa ukuzibandakanya nabo kwelabafileyo, ngokokuba walonakalisayo ilizwe lakho, wababulala abantu bakho; abayi kukwaziwa naphakade abantwana benkohliso.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 21, 'Balungiseleleni ukusikwa ngoonyana bakhe, ngenxa yobungendawo booyise; hleze bavuke, balidle ilifa ilizwe, bazalise ubuso behlabathi ngemizi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 22, 'Ndiya kusukela phezulu kubo, utsho uYehova wemikhosi, ndilitshabalalise igama leBhabheli, namasalela, nonyana, nomzukulwana, utsho uYehova;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 23, 'Ndiya kuyenza indawo yamaxolo akrakra, nezamachibi amanzi; yaye ndiza kuyidiliza ngerhamncwa elitshabalalisayo,” utsho uYehova wemikhosi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 24, 'Ufungile uYehova wemikhosi wathi, Inyaniso, njengoko ndakhumbulayo, koba njalo; njengoko ndicebe ngako, koba njalo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 25, 'Ndiya kumaphula uAsiriya ezweni lam, ndimnyathelele phantsi ezintabeni zam; iya kumka idyokhwe yakhe kubo, nomthwalo wakhe esixhantini sabo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 26, 'Lilo elo icebo elicetyiweyo ngehlabathi lonke; siso eso isandla esolukileyo phezu kweentlanga zonke.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 27, 'Kuba uYehova wemikhosi wenze icebo, ngubani na oya kuliphelisa? isandla sakhe esokile, ngubani na ongasibuyisayo?', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 28, 'Ngomnyaka wokufa kokumkani uAhazi, yaba ngumthwalo onzima.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 29, 'Musa ukuvuya, Palestina, lonke, ngakuba yaphukile intonga ebikubetha; kuba engcanjini yenyoka kuya kuphuma umthi, isiqhamo sawo sibe yinyoka yomlilo, ephaphazelayo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 30, 'Baya kudla abazizisweli, abasweleyo balale bekholosile; kwaye ndiya kuyibulala ingcambu yakho ngendlala, kwaye uya kuwabulala intsalela yakho.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 31, 'Bhomboloza, wena sango! biza, sixekondini! wena, lonke elasePalestina, ubhuqiwe; kuba kuya kunyuka umsi entla, kungabikho mntu ngamaxesha akhe amisiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 14, 32, 'Bathini na ukuphendula abathunywa beentlanga? Ukuba uYehova uyizinzisile iZiyon, yaye amahlwempu abantu bakhe baya kukholosa ngayo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 15, 1, 'Isihlabo sikaMowabhi. Ngokuba iphanzisiwe ebusuku iAri yakwaMowabhi; kuba ngobusuku ibhuqiwe iKire yakwaMowabhi, yathi shwaka;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 15, 2, 'Wenyuka waya eBhayiti naseDibhon, kummandla weentaba, ukuya kulila; uMowabhi uya kuzilela ngenxa yeNebho neMedebha; zonke iintloko zabo ziya kuba ziinkqayi, zonke iindevu zabo ziya kuchetywa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 15, 3, 'Baya kunxiba ezimnyama ezitalatweni zabo;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 15, 4, 'Iya kubiza iHeshbhon, ne-Elehali; ilizwi labo liya kuvakala naseYatsa; ke ngoko amagorha axhobileyo akwaMowabhi aya kuduma; ubomi bakhe buya kuba nzima kuye.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 15, 5, 'Intliziyo yam iyakhala ngenxa kaMowabhi; abasabayo bakhe baya kusabela eTsohare, ithokazi lenkomo eliminyaka mithathu; kuba endleleni yaseHoronayim baya kuduma ngentshabalalo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 15, 6, 'Ngenxa yokuba amanzi aseNimrim aya kuba yintlango, ngenxa yokuba ingca yomile, ingca iwile, ayibikho luhlaza.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 15, 7, 'Ke ngoko, baya kuthabatha intabalala abayifumeneyo, abayibeke kwiqula lemingcunube.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 15, 8, 'Isikhalo sajikeleza emdeni wakwaMowabhi; ukukhala kwakhe kufik’ e-Eglayim, ukukhala kwakhe kufike eBhelim.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 15, 9, 'Kuba amanzi aseDimon aya kuzala ligazi, yaye ndiya kuzisa okungakumbi phezu kweDimon, ndizisa iingonyama phezu kwabasindileyo bakwaMowabhi nakwabaseleyo belizwe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 16, 1, 'Thumani umangaleli wehlabathi ephuma eSela, aye entlango, entabeni yentombi enguZiyon.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 16, 2, 'Kuba njengentaka ephaphazelayo eshiywe kwindlwane yayo, zinjalo iintombi zakwaMowabhi kwimilambo yaseArnon.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 16, 3, 'Cebani icebo, zigwebeni; senza isithunzi sakho sibe njengobusuku emva kwemini; fihla abagxothiweyo; Sukuzenza ngathi uyabhadula.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 16, 4, 'Mabahlale nawe abathinjwa, uMowabhi; Yiba lihlathi kubo ebusweni bombhuqi; ngokuba abaphangi abasekho, umbhuqi uphelile, abacinezeli abasekho ehlabathini.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 16, 5, 'Yaye itrone iya kumiselwa ngokuqinileyo ngenceba, yaye uya kuhlala phezu kwayo enenyaniso ententeni kaDavide, ngoxa elindele umgwebo nokusesikweni nokukhawulezisa ubulungisa.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 16, 6, 'Silivile ikratshi likaMowabhi; unekratshi kakhulu, ewe, nekratshi lakhe, nekratshi lakhe, nomsindo wakhe;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 16, 7, 'Ngako oko uMowabhi uya kukhalela uMowabhi, akhale uMowabhi; uya kulilela iziseko zeKir-haresheti; ngenene babethwe.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 16, 8, 'Kuba amasimi aseHeshbhon abunile, neediliya zaseSibhema; Abathetheli beentlanga baziqhekeza iziseko zabo, beza eYazere, babhadula entlango; amasebe awo anaba phezu kolwandle.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 16, 9, 'Ngako oko ndiya kuwulila ngokulila kukaYashere, womdiliya waseSibhema; ndikunyakamisa ngeenyembezi zam, Heshbhon, nawe Elale, ngenxa yokuba ukukhala kwakho kuye kwafika ngenxa yeziqhamo zakho zasehlotyeni nangenxa yokuvuna kwakho.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 16, 10, 'Kwaye uvuyo nemigcobo isusiwe entsimini etyebileyo; kodwa ezidiliyeni akuyi kubakho kuvuma nakukuvuya; Ndayeka ukukhala kwabo kwakudala.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 16, 11, 'Ngako oko izibilini zam ziya kukhala njengezembe kwaMowabhi, izibilini zam zikhala eKir-hares.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 16, 12, 'Xa kubonakala ukuba uMowabhi udiniwe, uya kuthandaza engcweleni yakhe; kodwa akayi kuphumelela.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 16, 13, 'Lilo elo ilizwi awalithethayo uYehova ngoMowabhi ukususela ngelo xesha ukuya phambili.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 16, 14, 'Wathetha uYehova, wathi, Kungekadluli iminyaka emithathu, njengeminyaka yomqeshwa, buya kudeleka uzuko lukaMowabhi, kunye nenani elikhulu labantu; kwaye intsalela iya kuba ncinane kakhulu, ibe buthathaka.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 17, 1, 'Umyalezo waseDamasko. Yabona, ifudusiwe iDamasko, ayisayi kuba saba ngumzi, ibe yimiwewe;', 'XHO22'),
(27, 17, 2, 'Ibhuqiwe imizi yaseArohere; ziya kuba ziinkomo, kungabikho uwothusayo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 17, 3, 'Kuya kuma inqaba kwaEfrayim nobukumkani baseDamasko, namasalela akwa-Aram; baya kuba njengobuqaqawuli boonyana bakaSirayeli; utsho uYehova wemikhosi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 17, 4, 'Kuya kuthi ke ngaloo mini ubungcwele bukaYakobi bube buthathaka nokutyeba kwenyama yakhe kuya kuncipha.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 17, 5, 'Kuya kuba njengomvuni ebutha ingqolowa, ewunqumla ukhula ngesandla sakhe; yaye kuya kuba njengalowo uhlanganisa ukhula entlanjeni yakwaFaro.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 17, 6, 'Kuya kusala iidiliya ezingekavunwa, njengokuvuthulwa komnquma, zibe zibini, zibe ntathu iziqhamo entloko, zibe zine, zibe zintlanu emasebeni akhe angaphandle; utsho uYehova, uThixo kaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 17, 7, 'Ngaloo mini umntu uya kukhangela kuMenzi wakhe, namehlo akhe akhangele koyiNgcwele kaSirayeli.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 17, 8, 'Akayi kukhangela ezibingelelweni, umsebenzi wezandla zakhe, angayikhangeli into eyenziwa yiminwe yakhe, izikhondo zemithi engcwele nemifanekiso eqingqiweyo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 17, 9, 'Ngelo xesha imizi yakhe enqabileyo iya kuba njengegatsha elishiyiweyo, elisikelelweyo, abalishiyileyo ngenxa yoonyana bakaSirayeli, libe senkangala.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 17, 10, 'Ngenxa enokuba umlibele uThixo, umsindisi wakho, akwalikhumbula neliwa lokunqaba kwakho, ngenxa yoko uya kutyala izityalo ezintle, uzimilisele emagqabini olwandle.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 17, 11, 'Woyihluma isityalo sakho ngaloo mini, kusasa uya kuyintshulisa imbewu yakho; kodwa ukuvuna kuya kuba lithemba ngemini yembandezelo nembandezelo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 17, 12, 'Yeha, ingxokolo yeentlanga ehlokoma njengolwandle! nesandi sezizwe ezingxolayo njengamanzi!', 'XHO22'),
(27, 17, 13, 'Iintlanga ziya kugquma njengesandi samanzi amaninzi, kodwa uThixo uya kuzikhalimela, yaye ziya kusabela kude ziphetshethwe njengomququ ezintabeni phambi komoya nanjengomoya ovuthuza phambi kwesaqhwithi.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 17, 14, 'Kwathi, ngokuhlwa, kukho iliza lembandezelo; kungekafi, akakho. Siso eso isabelo sabasiphangayo, sisiphelo sabasiphangayo.', 'XHO22'),
(27, 18, 1, 'Yeha ilizwe elizaliswe ngamaphiko, phesheya kwemilambo yakwaKushi!', 'XHO22'),
(27, 18, 2, 'owathuma abathunywa elwandle, beneengqayi zengcongolo phezu kwamanzi, besithi, Hambani, bathunywa banamendu, niye kubantu abathe saa, abahlukene phakathi, kubantu aboyikekayo abangapha nangapha; luhlanga olulinganiselweyo, olunyathelweyo, olulizwe lilonakaliswe yimilambo.', 'XHO22');
